(52, 26873, '', 20, 'If I love you, what business is it of yours?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:12:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:04'),
(53, 66324, '', 20, 'A business absolutely devoted to service will have only one worry about profits. They will be embarrassingly large.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:12:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:04'),
(54, 4222, '', 20, 'In the business world, the rearview mirror is always clearer than the windshield.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:12:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:04'),
(55, 3265, '', 20, 'I have never once regretted missing a business opportunity so that I could be with my children and grandchildren.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:12:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:04'),
(56, 14987, '', 20, 'We don\'t seem to be able to check crime, so why not legalize it and then tax it out of business?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:12:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:04'),
