(92, 52279, '', 20, 'To me, business isn\'t about wearing suits or pleasing stockholders. It\'s about being true to yourself, your ideas and focusing on the essentials.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:12:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:04'),
(93, 62555, '', 20, 'Employers and business leaders need people who can think for themselves - who can take initiative and be the solution to problems.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:12:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:04'),
(94, 31391, '', 20, 'No matter what business you\'re in, you can\'t run in place or someone will pass you by. It doesn\'t matter how many games you\'ve won.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:12:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:04'),
(95, 11369, '', 20, 'Business has only two functions - marketing and innovation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:12:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:04'),
