(97, 57807, '', 20, 'A grocer is attracted to his business by a magnetic force as great as the repulsion which renders it odious to artists.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:12:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:04'),
(98, 6567, '', 20, 'Money is a strange business. People who haven\'t got it aim it strongly. People who have are full of troubles.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:12:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:04'),
(99, 13546, '', 20, 'The only business of the head in the world is to bow a ceaseless obeisance to the heart.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:12:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:04'),
