(1134, 34340, '', 18, 'One is loved because one is loved. No reason is needed for loving.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1135, 84336, '', 18, 'Love is being stupid together.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1136, 67113, '', 18, 'Love is when you meet someone who tells you something new about yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1137, 53620, '', 18, 'It is difficult to know at what moment love begins it is less difficult to know that it has begun.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1138, 42031, '', 18, 'How absurd and delicious it is to be in love with somebody younger than yourself. Everybody should try it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1139, 11077, '', 18, 'In love the paradox occurs that two beings become one and yet remain two.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1140, 91553, '', 18, 'When love is not madness, it is not love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1141, 70197, '', 18, 'The love we give away is the only love we keep.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1142, 40763, '', 18, 'Love is an act of endless forgiveness, a tender look which becomes a habit.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1143, 57829, '', 18, 'Blessed is the influence of one true, loving human soul on another.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1144, 37374, '', 18, 'A kiss is a rosy dot over the \'i\' of loving.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1145, 14992, '', 18, 'Love is the only sane and satisfactory answer to the problem of human existence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1146, 53612, '', 18, 'Absence - that common cure of love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1147, 20534, '', 18, 'Life is the flower for which love is the honey.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1148, 47174, '', 18, 'The only abnormality is the incapacity to love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1149, 42038, '', 18, 'There is no disguise which can hide love for long where it exists, or simulate it where it does not.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1150, 50723, '', 18, 'Love consists in this, that two solitudes protect and touch and greet each other.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1151, 49670, '', 18, 'Be of love a little more careful than of anything.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1152, 85059, '', 18, 'Whatever our souls are made of, his and mine are the same.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1153, 87600, '', 18, 'Love takes off masks that we fear we cannot live without and know we cannot live within.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1154, 55314, '', 18, 'A new command I give you: Love one another. As I have loved you, so you must love one another.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1155, 57875, '', 18, 'Love is supreme and unconditional like is nice but limited.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1156, 45157, '', 18, 'Looking back, I have this to regret, that too often when I loved, I did not say so.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1157, 39898, '', 18, 'I love that feeling of being in love, the effect of having butterflies when you wake up in the morning. That is special.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1158, 89944, '', 18, 'Lord, grant that I might not so much seek to be loved as to love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1159, 15843, '', 18, 'Sometimes it\'s a form of love just to talk to somebody that you have nothing in common with and still be fascinated by their presence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1160, 38821, '', 18, 'There is a woman at the begining of all great things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1161, 35018, '', 18, 'Love knows not distance it hath no continent its eyes are for the stars.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:15'),
(1162, 24466, '', 18, 'The sweetest of all sounds is that of the voice of the woman we love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1163, 27738, '', 18, 'The degree of loving is measured by the degree of giving.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1164, 63533, '', 18, 'People think love is an emotion. Love is good sense.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1165, 12268, '', 18, 'Love is the only reality and it is not a mere sentiment. It is the ultimate truth that lies at the heart of creation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1166, 82774, '', 18, 'Love is the greatest refreshment in life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1167, 98437, '', 18, 'There is only one kind of love, but there are a thousand imitations.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1168, 20521, '', 18, 'Love is the delusion that one woman differs from another.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1169, 60258, '', 18, 'If you wished to be loved, love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1170, 37691, '', 18, 'Love is my religion - I could die for it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1171, 58917, '', 18, 'Tell me who admires and loves you, and I will tell you who you are.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1172, 32277, '', 18, 'Love shall be our token love be yours and love be mine.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1173, 7992, '', 18, 'He is not a lover who does not love forever.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1174, 7990, '', 18, 'Love is the hardest habit to break, and the most difficult to satisfy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1175, 27477, '', 18, 'When we are in love we seem to ourselves quite different from what we were before.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1176, 29274, '', 18, 'The most powerful weapon on earth is the human soul on fire.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1177, 55554, '', 18, 'Love is all we have, the only way that each can help the other.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1178, 66700, '', 18, 'Choose your love, Love your choice.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1179, 89887, '', 18, 'Falling in love consists merely in uncorking the imagination and bottling the common sense.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1180, 34054, '', 18, 'Love is an emotion experienced by the many and enjoyed by the few.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1181, 77135, '', 18, 'If you could only love enough, you could be the most powerful person in the world.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1182, 58021, '', 18, 'Love means to commit yourself without guarantee.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1183, 21767, '', 18, 'Follow love and it will flee, flee love and it will follow thee.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1184, 51866, '', 18, 'The way to know life is to love many things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1185, 87647, '', 18, 'Your words are my food, your breath my wine. You are everything to me.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1186, 18681, '', 18, 'Love is only a dirty trick played on us to achieve continuation of the species.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1187, 81673, '', 18, 'Down on your knees, and thank heaven, fasting, for a good man\'s love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16');
INSERT INTO `quotes` (`id`, `order`, `entry_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `author`, `has_notif`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1188, 40777, '', 18, 'Love takes up where knowledge leaves off.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1189, 71601, '', 18, 'Fortune and love favor the brave.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1190, 51156, '', 18, 'Each moment of a happy lover\'s hour is worth an age of dull and common life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1191, 62962, '', 18, 'Love is suffering. One side always loves more.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1192, 62526, '', 18, 'Love is what you\'ve been through with somebody.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1193, 81163, '', 18, 'Love looks through a telescope envy, through a microscope.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1194, 28910, '', 18, 'Love in its essence is spiritual fire.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1195, 19618, '', 18, 'There are never enough I Love You\'s.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1196, 29872, '', 18, 'Love is always being given where it is not required.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1197, 59819, '', 18, 'Friendship is Love without his wings!', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1198, 60013, '', 18, 'Come live with me and be my love, And we will all the pleasures prove, That valleys, groves, hills, and fields, Woods, or steepy mountain yields.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1199, 36147, '', 18, 'We are all born for love. It is the principle of existence, and its only end.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1200, 16189, '', 18, 'Love is the poetry of the senses.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1201, 15854, '', 18, 'There is always something left to love. And if you ain\'t learned that, you ain\'t learned nothing.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1202, 73933, '', 18, 'Love means to love that which is unlovable or it is no virtue at all.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1203, 24976, '', 18, 'People who throw kisses are hopelessly lazy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1204, 43345, '', 18, 'Love is not only something you feel, it is something you do.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1205, 50061, '', 18, 'Love is the great miracle cure. Loving ourselves works miracles in our lives.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1206, 68386, '', 18, 'In every living thing there is the desire for love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1207, 60513, '', 18, 'Love is but the discovery of ourselves in others, and the delight in the recognition.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1208, 49759, '', 18, 'For love is immortality.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1209, 62237, '', 18, 'We may give without loving, but we cannot love without giving.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1210, 19553, '', 18, 'Love conquers all.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1211, 96220, '', 18, 'Sometimes it\'s hard to be a woman giving all your love to just one man.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1212, 49245, '', 18, 'To love abundantly is to live abundantly, and to love forever is to live forever.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1213, 36245, '', 18, 'Love is that splendid triggering of human vitality the supreme activity which nature affords anyone for going out of himself toward someone else.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1214, 37979, '', 18, 'If you can learn to love yourself and all the flaws, you can love other people so much better. And that makes you so happy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1215, 92960, '', 18, 'Say what you will, \'tis better to be left than never to have been loved.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1216, 87778, '', 18, 'Sympathy constitutes friendship but in love there is a sort of antipathy, or opposing passion. Each strives to be the other, and both together make up one whole.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1217, 24308, '', 18, 'Love is the power to see similarity in the dissimilar.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1218, 59986, '', 18, 'If thou must love me, let it be for naught except for love\'s sake only.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1219, 8290, '', 18, 'Take away love and our earth is a tomb.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1220, 13627, '', 18, 'Love is the child of illusion and the parent of disillusion.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1221, 95866, '', 18, 'Do you have to have a reason for loving?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1222, 99474, '', 18, 'The first magic of love is our ignorance that it can ever end.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1223, 36675, '', 18, 'Love\'s greatest gift is its ability to make everything it touches sacred.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1224, 17958, '', 18, 'The quarrels of lovers are the renewal of love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1225, 53006, '', 18, 'What the world really needs is more love and less paper work.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1226, 89315, '', 18, 'Woe to the man whose heart has not learned while young to hope, to love - and to put its trust in life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1227, 89811, '', 18, 'Let no one who loves be unhappy, even love unreturned has its rainbow.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1228, 2315, '', 18, 'I don\'t know that love changes. People change. Circumstances change.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1229, 82568, '', 18, 'No one has ever loved anyone the way everyone wants to be loved.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1230, 84169, '', 18, 'He who loves, flies, runs, and rejoices he is free and nothing holds him back.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1231, 86443, '', 18, 'Love is the only gold.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1232, 77188, '', 18, 'To love and be loved is to feel the sun from both sides.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1233, 54949, '', 18, 'It is easier to love humanity as a whole than to love one\'s neighbor.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1234, 39513, '', 18, 'Though lovers be lost love shall not.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1235, 83755, '', 18, 'Nobody has ever measured, not even poets, how much the heart can hold.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1236, 94783, '', 18, 'When you love someone all your saved up wishes start coming out.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1237, 4304, '', 18, 'Love means not ever having to say you\'re sorry.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1238, 19735, '', 18, 'There is no limit to the power of loving.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1239, 55747, '', 18, 'Love you will find only where you may show yourself weak without provoking strength.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1240, 6464, '', 18, 'Love is a springtime plant that perfumes everything with its hope, even the ruins to which it clings.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1241, 44858, '', 18, 'O, thou art fairer than the evening air clad in the beauty of a thousand stars.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1242, 87820, '', 18, 'Love is a mutual self-giving which ends in self-recovery.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1243, 35693, '', 18, 'To love for the sake of being loved is human, but to love for the sake of loving is angelic.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1244, 50564, '', 18, 'There is more pleasure in loving than in being beloved.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1245, 94727, '', 18, 'When love is at its best, one loves so much that he cannot forget.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1246, 47840, '', 18, 'Love is like a faucet, it turns off and on.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1247, 78153, '', 18, 'More than kisses, letters mingle souls.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1248, 99141, '', 18, 'Stand by your man. Give him two arms to cling to and something warm to come to.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1249, 4077, '', 18, 'Love is metaphysical gravity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1250, 96176, '', 18, 'There is room in the smallest cottage for a happy loving pair.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1251, 7321, '', 18, 'Who loves, raves.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1252, 19192, '', 18, 'With our love, we could save the world.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1253, 68877, '', 18, 'Pains of love be sweeter far than all other pleasures are.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1254, 71888, '', 18, 'To good and true love fear is forever affixed.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1255, 53218, '', 18, 'What is love? It is the morning and the evening star.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1256, 49140, '', 18, 'Ultimately love is everything.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1257, 44468, '', 18, 'True love is quiescent, except in the nascent moments of true humility.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1258, 36176, '', 18, 'Only love interests me, and I am only in contact with things that revolve around love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1259, 74099, '', 18, 'You don\'t have to go looking for love when it\'s where you come from.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1260, 14104, '', 18, 'It is very easy to love alone.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1261, 42621, '', 18, 'Who so loves believes the impossible.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1262, 80043, '', 18, 'Only divine love bestows the keys of knowledge.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1263, 59266, '', 18, 'The richest love is that which submits to the arbitration of time.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:16'),
(1264, 79607, '', 18, 'We perceive when love begins and when it declines by our embarrassment when alone together.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1265, 36967, '', 18, 'Love ceases to be a pleasure when it ceases to be a secret.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1266, 16654, '', 18, 'All love is vanquished by a succeeding love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1267, 91427, '', 18, 'We can only learn to love by loving.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1268, 23592, '', 18, 'We are most alive when we\'re in love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1269, 42497, '', 18, 'Who ever loved that loved not at first sight?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1270, 1825, '', 18, 'Love is when he gives you a piece of your soul, that you never knew was missing.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1271, 30746, '', 18, 'Love is an energy which exists of itself. It is its own value.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
