(1283, 39760, '', 18, 'Love is the magician that pulls man out of his own hat.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1284, 62378, '', 18, 'In our life there is a single color, as on an artist\'s palette, which provides the meaning of life and art. It is the color of love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1285, 40660, '', 18, 'To enlarge or illustrate this power and effect of love is to set a candle in the sun.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1286, 83387, '', 18, 'One must not trifle with love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1287, 88140, '', 18, 'Darkness cannot drive out darkness only light can do that. Hate cannot drive out hate only love can do that.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1288, 37901, '', 18, 'Life is a song - sing it. Life is a game - play it. Life is a challenge - meet it. Life is a dream - realize it. Life is a sacrifice - offer it. Life is love - enjoy it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1289, 63892, '', 18, 'Love all, trust a few, do wrong to none.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1290, 28920, '', 18, 'When the power of love overcomes the love of power the world will know peace.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1291, 43072, '', 18, 'Choose a job you love, and you will never have to work a day in your life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1292, 42996, '', 18, 'A successful marriage requires falling in love many times, always with the same person.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1293, 88193, '', 18, 'Spread love everywhere you go. Let no one ever come to you without leaving happier.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1294, 63247, '', 18, 'I believe that unarmed truth and unconditional love will have the final word in reality. This is why right, temporarily defeated, is stronger than evil triumphant.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1295, 46564, '', 18, 'To love beauty is to see light.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1296, 91721, '', 18, 'My great hope is to laugh as much as I cry to get my work done and try to love somebody and have the courage to accept the love in return.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1297, 86101, '', 18, 'It is not a lack of love, but a lack of friendship that makes unhappy marriages.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1298, 3613, '', 18, 'Love and compassion are necessities, not luxuries. Without them humanity cannot survive.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1299, 20869, '', 18, 'Don\'t aim for success if you want it just do what you love and believe in, and it will come naturally.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1300, 48829, '', 18, 'I love people who make me laugh. I honestly think it\'s the thing I like most, to laugh. It cures a multitude of ills. It\'s probably the most important thing in a person.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1301, 55038, '', 18, 'When you arise in the morning, think of what a precious privilege it is to be alive - to breathe, to think, to enjoy, to love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1302, 80711, '', 18, 'The love of family and the admiration of friends is much more important than wealth and privilege.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1303, 48460, '', 18, 'Man must evolve for all human conflict a method which rejects revenge, aggression and retaliation. The foundation of such a method is love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1304, 63903, '', 18, 'There can be no deep disappointment where there is not deep love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1305, 56208, '', 18, 'Love begins by taking care of the closest ones - the ones at home.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1306, 57295, '', 18, 'If music be the food of love, play on.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1307, 21219, '', 18, 'If you have only one smile in you give it to the people you love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1308, 37043, '', 18, 'Love is the only force capable of transforming an enemy into friend.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
