(1311, 25003, '', 18, 'If you love life, don\'t waste time, for time is what life is made up of.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1312, 80439, '', 18, 'At the center of non-violence stands the principle of love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
