(1324, 6878, '', 18, 'People love chopping wood. In this activity one immediately sees results.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1325, 22799, '', 18, 'If you want a love message to be heard, it has got to be sent out. To keep a lamp burning, we have to keep putting oil in it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
