(1334, 96202, '', 18, 'Love of beauty is taste. The creation of beauty is art.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1335, 94813, '', 18, 'I honestly think it is better to be a failure at something you love than to be a success at something you hate.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
