(1347, 49145, '', 18, 'If someone thinks that love and peace is a cliche that must have been left behind in the Sixties, that\'s his problem. Love and peace are eternal.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1348, 67120, '', 18, 'The first duty of love is to listen.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1349, 55428, '', 18, 'I see when men love women. They give them but a little of their lives. But women when they love give everything.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1350, 47863, '', 18, 'Rare as is true love, true friendship is rarer.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1351, 69187, '', 18, 'We are not the same persons this year as last nor are those we love. It is a happy chance if we, changing, continue to love a changed person.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1352, 33805, '', 18, 'Falling in love and having a relationship are two different things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1353, 36612, '', 18, 'Accept the things to which fate binds you, and love the people with whom fate brings you together, but do so with all your heart.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1354, 16069, '', 11, 'Nothing gives one person so much advantage over another as to remain always cool and unruffled under all circumstances.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1355, 20117, '', 11, 'Rather be dead than cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1356, 30306, '', 11, 'Let your soul stand cool and composed before a million universes.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1357, 25086, '', 11, 'I never cut class. I loved getting A\'s, I liked being smart. I liked being on time. I thought being smart is cooler than anything in the world.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1358, 33225, '', 11, 'Being cool is being your own self, not doing something that someone else is telling you to do.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1359, 66796, '', 11, 'I\'m not the kind of person who tries to be cool or trendy, I\'m definitely an individual.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1360, 85091, '', 11, 'He who keeps his cool best wins.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1361, 80747, '', 11, 'It seems like once people grow up, they have no idea what\'s cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1362, 27678, '', 11, 'So there\'s nothing more provocative than taking a genre that everybody who\'s cool hates - and then making it cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1363, 95469, '', 11, 'All of my favorite people - people I really trust - none of them were cool in their younger years.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:17'),
(1364, 96363, '', 11, 'I can take it. The tougher it gets, the cooler I get.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1365, 69299, '', 11, 'You don\'t have to carry a designer bag that costs more than a car to look cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1366, 97559, '', 11, 'One cool judgment is worth a thousand hasty counsels. The thing to do is to supply light and not heat.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1367, 76845, '', 11, 'My perfect guy wears converse, is totally laid back, and doesn\'t worry about being cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1368, 43137, '', 11, 'To act coolly, intelligently and prudently in perilous circumstances is the test of a man - and also a nation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1369, 10049, '', 11, 'I\'ve never done anything because I thought it would look cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1370, 92653, '', 11, 'Summer bachelors, like summer breezes, are never as cool as they pretend to be.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
