(1382, 58618, '', 11, 'If at any moment of the day I ever think I\'m remotely cool at all, which is hardly ever, I have two daughters who make sure that never happens.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
