(1396, 43195, '', 11, 'Keep cool anger is not an argument.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1397, 84164, '', 11, 'The high-spirited man may indeed die, but he will not stoop to meanness. Fire, though it may be quenched, will not become cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1398, 38717, '', 11, 'If your stomach disputes you, lie down and pacify it with cool thoughts.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1399, 78969, '', 11, 'Aristotle taught that the brain exists merely to cool the blood and is not involved in the process of thinking. This is true only of certain persons.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1400, 38487, '', 11, 'I don\'t go to the cool, trendy restaurants. I go to either the holes in the wall or the super-fancy restaurants where there are no cool people.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1401, 95561, '', 11, 'I have a cycle that is not particularly cool, but it\'s a cycle: trash myself to reward myself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1402, 66758, '', 11, 'That\'s one of the cool things about fame. You have an affect on society and where it goes.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1403, 69230, '', 11, 'Competition is great. And as long as it\'s friendly and not a malicious thing, then I think it\'s cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1404, 6677, '', 11, 'Someone who doesn\'t take herself too seriously and can be a goofball. Because everyone\'s a nerd inside, I don\'t care how cool you are.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1405, 41015, '', 11, 'I grew up not really having anything, so the idea that I can take care of my family and my friends now is a really cool bonus.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1406, 49253, '', 11, 'I\'ve been in fights, but that doesn\'t make me cool or like a tough guy or more interesting actor, I\'m not proud of it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1407, 64505, '', 11, 'What\'s cool is when you\'re able to give your audience imagination and you don\'t have to cage them in like animals.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1408, 13734, '', 11, 'I\'m a video game fan, and I always thought it would be cool to be able to control a character.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1409, 55830, '', 11, 'It\'s cool now to play golf.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1410, 55808, '', 11, 'The nerds are the ones that make the films and do loads of other really cool stuff in their life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1411, 78295, '', 11, 'Keep cool my babies.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1412, 90440, '', 11, 'There are people out there who are older who are cool. I want that.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1413, 54574, '', 11, 'I was trying to be this person who is cool, eternally rocking.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1414, 90532, '', 11, 'Parenthood and family come first for me, and when I\'m not working I\'m cool with the Teletubbies.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1415, 69141, '', 11, 'I\'m going to let people know that it\'s cool to have a child and be young and still be a good mom. It\'s really tough, but I\'m doing it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1416, 9535, '', 11, 'It\'s really cool to see glowsticks at the show, to see dance music culture infiltrating and becoming one with the metal community.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1417, 49924, '', 11, 'It\'s cool to go places where working people are happy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1418, 1299, '', 11, 'As a young boy, I was taught in high school that hacking was cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1419, 17747, '', 11, 'If you want to go to the mall, you have to take security. But it\'s always cool. The kids are amazing.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1420, 57133, '', 11, 'I have, I admit, a low tolerance for detached chronicling and cool analysis.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1421, 56941, '', 11, 'The cool kindliness of sheets, that soon smooth away trouble and the rough male kiss of blankets.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1422, 61654, '', 11, 'An orange on the table, your dress on the rug, and you in my bed, sweet present of the present, cool of night, warmth of my life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1423, 80682, '', 11, 'My parents are the coolest of the cool on every single level, and it\'s because they have a deep appreciation for every moment of their lives.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1424, 72484, '', 11, 'A lot of pop people out there are cool, but they overdo it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1425, 44998, '', 11, 'I could do without \'cool\' publications calling me \'mom jazz.\' But I laughed all the way to the bank, baby.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1426, 75499, '', 11, 'I\'m a sappy mom now. I didn\'t think I would be. I thought I\'d be a cool mom who keeps everything in perspective.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1427, 757, '', 11, 'My uncle\'s a lawyer and I remember going to see him in court and thinking, \'That\'s cool, too bad I could never be a lawyer.\'', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1428, 99272, '', 11, 'I used to be a cool chick but I\'m not anymore.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1429, 99091, '', 11, 'Long intros are cool because there\'s a little bit of anticipation, you know?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1430, 63698, '', 11, 'There aren\'t many poster children for cool angst. Everybody thinks it\'s cool if you\'re the bad girl.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1431, 21313, '', 11, 'For the last few years, it\'s been so chic for everybody to be miserable. Like if you\'re in with the cool crowd, you can\'t be happy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1432, 76000, '', 11, 'I haven\'t took no punishment. There\'s nothing cool about taking punishment.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1433, 68172, '', 11, 'The problem to me is violence. It\'s not cool to kill somebody or hurt people.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1434, 21058, '', 11, 'Tweeting is like sending out cool telegrams to your friends once a week.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1435, 66595, '', 11, 'I have a kind of boring personal life, to the paparazzi anyway, and I don\'t hang with the cool crowd.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1436, 17255, '', 11, 'Survival, in the cool economics of biology, means simply the persistence of one\'s own genes in the generations to follow.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1437, 22593, '', 11, 'I wondered how they would top the Pirates and skeletons and moonlight, because that\'s a pretty cool concept.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1438, 88760, '', 11, 'Hip-hop is still cool at a party. But to me, hip-hop has never been strictly a party it is also there to elevate consciousness.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1439, 51635, '', 11, 'I\'d love to date somebody cool, fun, funny.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1440, 27731, '', 11, 'Being cool, having a \'cool\' energy is just not attractive to me.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1441, 84076, '', 11, 'The ballplayer who loses his head, who can\'t keep his cool, is worse than no ballplayer at all.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1442, 78936, '', 11, 'I know what it feels like to have the door slammed firmly in my face, so I\'m cool with that.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1443, 78188, '', 11, 'In my teens, I was never part of the cool crowd.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1444, 30491, '', 11, 'For most of my life, I\'ve thought of myself as pretty cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1445, 17255, '', 11, 'Personally, I was never the cool kid. I was always sort of a bookworm. I would just like to be more like Troy, because he\'s so cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1446, 12297, '', 11, 'When you get to play a character that\'s in love, it\'s cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1447, 42846, '', 11, 'Everything that\'s cool that happens, I look at my wife and I say, \'We need to enjoy this moment right here! This is really special!\'', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1448, 1846, '', 11, 'I\'m blessed to have cool roles in these big movies.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1449, 53807, '', 11, 'That was excellent! I mean, it didn\'t do anything, but it looked really cool!', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1450, 65733, '', 11, 'I love Poseidon. His trident - his weapon - is really cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1451, 93563, '', 11, 'I think you have to be cool to be a good flirt, and I don\'t think I\'m very cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1452, 3779, '', 11, 'Music is music, ultimately. If it makes you feel good, cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1453, 70953, '', 11, 'Well, a sort of epiphany: I was in a great band. And it\'s very cool to be at 53 and realise that when you were a kid you were in a great band.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1454, 20058, '', 11, 'We aren\'t cool and never will be.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1455, 43487, '', 11, 'It\'s always cool to meet people who can do things that you have no capacity to do.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1456, 93207, '', 11, 'I\'d like to see a world free of strife, stress, pain, hunger, war - a cool place where everyone could live.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1457, 25641, '', 11, 'It\'s cool to play a sinister bad guy who also has a human side.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:18'),
(1458, 42400, '', 11, 'It\'s cool to go to a place that has posters up and it\'s one night only. It feels more special.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1459, 43612, '', 11, 'I don\'t count on the boy who waits till October, when it\'s cool and fun, then decides he wants to play.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1460, 93893, '', 11, 'That was cool and that sucked all at the same time.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1461, 88391, '', 11, 'I wasn\'t one of the cool kids by any stretch. I just bumbled along really.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1462, 94552, '', 11, 'I\'m thought of as a cool, unemotional dancer, but inside I\'m not.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1463, 67280, '', 11, 'But live shows are cool. I just got back into the idea of enjoying it live.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1464, 46816, '', 11, 'I\'d like to have the flying car, I think that\'d be really cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1465, 20581, '', 11, 'I want you to see that I\'m looking. Look at me look at you. I\'m cool with that.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1466, 92240, '', 11, 'You actually don\'t want people thinking your product is cool, because then you\'re a fad.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1467, 43177, '', 11, 'People connect with me just as a cool, around-the-way type of guy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1468, 90053, '', 11, 'And in a world without heroes, as the movie trailer voice-over guy might say, the slightly awkward can be slightly cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1469, 84699, '', 11, 'I shall go the way of the open sea, to the lands I knew before you came, and the cool ocean breezes shall blow from me the memory of your name.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1470, 75292, '', 11, 'It\'s cool to be recognised by your peers.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1471, 77540, '', 11, 'The idea of recognising your strengths and using them in as versatile a way as you can is cool to me.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1472, 29308, '', 11, 'What I do doesn\'t sit well in the world of hipsterville. I don\'t have a cool card, but I also don\'t have thin skin.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1473, 85646, '', 11, 'The cool thing about music is no one can take music away from you, writing wise.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1474, 46343, '', 11, 'I\'m not really cool, or dashing, or any of those things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1475, 35052, '', 11, 'There\'s no point in swanning through and being cool as a breeze in every scene. It\'s not really that interesting. Even if you\'re a superhero.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1476, 91761, '', 11, 'All I know is that I\'ve ruled out wearing fairy wings. When I was nine I wanted to get married in fairy wings, and now I realize that\'s not cool anymore.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1477, 85071, '', 11, 'If you meet a girl, you meet a girl. It\'s normal, so if you exchange numbers, whatevs, it\'s cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1478, 10361, '', 11, 'In my school, people liked the gym teachers because they were the football or soccer coaches. But look, if they\'re cool, they get respect.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1479, 66295, '', 11, 'For years I have been going to the South of France to cool out.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1480, 41376, '', 11, 'It\'s cool to have instruments lying around because they give you different ideas.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1481, 76988, '', 11, 'I was labeled at a young age - Miss Unemotional, Miss Cool, and that would carry over to my press conferences.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1482, 64135, '', 11, 'I never felt cool growing up. I was a bit of an outsider, but I discovered theatre very early on, which got me through.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1483, 7894, '', 11, 'Most people are really cool and I really don\'t mind talking to them and answering their questions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1484, 92364, '', 11, 'I won\'t go into detail but this animated one, the story line is very cool and the kids seem to love it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1485, 11113, '', 11, 'Now there is so much expertise and brainpower it\'s hard to be at the cutting edge of what\'s cool and not do something that\'s totally geeky.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1486, 63429, '', 11, 'Arizona is really cool but I couldn\'t stay there for too long.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1487, 96154, '', 11, 'I thought that would be kind of cool, to make a bad guy look sympathetic.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1488, 78062, '', 11, 'This wired generation is kind of cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1489, 3130, '', 11, 'It was cool for a couple of weeks, but how much bad golf can you play?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1490, 5556, '', 11, 'A lot of those little things that I really like doing are just moments of cool articulation, just little moments of phrasing that probably go over everybody\'s head.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1491, 55573, '', 11, 'The worst thing I could be thinking is how could I be a cool bass player.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1492, 79460, '', 11, 'I think trying to be cool is the worst possible ambition - and I have never suffered from it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1493, 28649, '', 11, 'It\'s pretty cool to see how far music can take you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1494, 62807, '', 11, 'I was training more learning how to scuba dive which I\'d never done which was really, really, really cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1495, 17036, '', 11, 'Punk\'s influence on music, movies, art, design and fashion is no longer in doubt. It is used as the measurement for what is cool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19'),
(1496, 15081, '', 11, 'I\'ve been such an oddball my whole life, but I\'ve always been cool and I\'ve always dressed fairly smartly.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:14:55', '2023-01-27 00:30:19');
