(2037, 96425, '', 12, 'The point of power is always in the present moment.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:24', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2038, 30237, '', 30, 'Age is an issue of mind over matter. If you don\'t mind, it doesn\'t matter.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2039, 92261, '', 30, 'Wrinkles should merely indicate where smiles have been.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2040, 47484, '', 30, 'A diplomat is a man who always remembers a woman\'s birthday but never remembers her age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2041, 35001, '', 30, 'As I grow older, I pay less attention to what men say. I just watch what they do.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2042, 42647, '', 30, 'How incessant and great are the ills with which a prolonged old age is replete.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2043, 87175, '', 30, 'Old age has deformities enough of its own. It should never add to them the deformity of vice.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2044, 6038, '', 30, 'An archaeologist is the best husband a woman can have. The older she gets the more interested he is in her.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2045, 65641, '', 30, 'All diseases run into one, old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2046, 87699, '', 30, 'Bashfulness is an ornament to youth, but a reproach to old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2047, 58109, '', 30, 'Like everyone else who makes the mistake of getting older, I begin each day with coffee and obituaries.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2048, 29801, '', 30, 'Age appears to be best in four things old wood best to burn, old wine to drink, old friends to trust, and old authors to read.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2049, 24217, '', 30, 'None are so old as those who have outlived enthusiasm.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2050, 93055, '', 30, 'Every man over forty is a scoundrel.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2051, 60818, '', 30, 'Forty is the old age of youth fifty the youth of old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2052, 8945, '', 30, 'You can\'t help getting older, but you don\'t have to get old.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2053, 67875, '', 30, 'Alas, after a certain age every man is responsible for his face.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2054, 60839, '', 30, 'Youth is when you\'re allowed to stay up late on New Year\'s Eve. Middle age is when you\'re forced to.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2055, 65042, '', 30, 'Old age is like everything else. To make a success of it, you\'ve got to start young.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2056, 38677, '', 30, 'A man growing old becomes a child again.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2057, 8575, '', 30, 'I will never be an old man. To me, old age is always 15 years older than I am.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2058, 81707, '', 30, 'Age considers youth ventures.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2059, 50966, '', 30, 'What most persons consider as virtue, after the age of 40 is simply a loss of energy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2060, 9700, '', 30, 'Age is a very high price to pay for maturity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2061, 72690, '', 30, 'Old age is no place for sissies.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2062, 55224, '', 30, 'I don\'t feel old. I don\'t feel anything till noon. That\'s when it\'s time for my nap.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2063, 21788, '', 30, 'I don\'t believe one grows older. I think that what happens early on in life is that at a certain age one stands still and stagnates.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2064, 14307, '', 30, 'Advice in old age is foolish for what can be more absurd than to increase our provisions for the road the nearer we approach to our journey\'s end.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2065, 50322, '', 30, 'When grace is joined with wrinkles, it is adorable. There is an unspeakable dawn in happy old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2066, 81293, '', 30, 'It takes a long time to become young.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2067, 10654, '', 30, 'After thirty, a body has a mind of its own.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2068, 70775, '', 30, 'Age is not a particularly interesting subject. Anyone can get old. All you have to do is live long enough.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2069, 63833, '', 30, 'Old minds are like old horses you must exercise them if you wish to keep them in working order.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2070, 70013, '', 30, 'Forty is the old age of youth, fifty is the youth of old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2071, 26220, '', 30, 'Youth is the gift of nature, but age is a work of art.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:24'),
(2072, 20808, '', 30, 'Preparation for old age should begin not later than one\'s teens. A life which is empty of purpose until 65 will not suddenly become filled on retirement.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2073, 87749, '', 30, 'There is always some specific moment when we become aware that our youth is gone but, years after, we know it was much later.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2074, 44024, '', 30, 'Growing old is no more than a bad habit which a busy person has no time to form.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2075, 15400, '', 30, 'Old age is fifteen years older than I am.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2076, 99645, '', 30, 'Aging is not lost youth but a new stage of opportunity and strength.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2077, 47934, '', 30, 'The trick is growing up without growing old.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2078, 77962, '', 30, 'Old age comes on suddenly, and not gradually as is thought.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2079, 86410, '', 30, 'I think your whole life shows in your face and you should be proud of that.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2080, 17863, '', 30, 'I\'m happy to report that my inner child is still ageless.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2081, 34077, '', 30, 'Youth is the best time to be rich, and the best time to be poor.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2082, 72328, '', 30, 'It is sad to grow old but nice to ripen.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2083, 2569, '', 30, 'One of the many things nobody ever tells you about middle age is that it\'s such a nice change from being young.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2084, 17227, '', 30, 'After you\'re older, two things are possibly more important than any others: health and money.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2085, 80737, '', 30, 'You end up as you deserve. In old age you must put up with the face, the friends, the health, and the children you have earned.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2086, 42687, '', 30, 'I\'m not interested in age. People who tell me their age are silly. You\'re as old as you feel.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2087, 15142, '', 30, 'Inflation is when you pay fifteen dollars for the ten-dollar haircut you used to get for five dollars when you had hair.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2088, 43186, '', 30, 'My notion of a wife at 40 is that a man should be able to change her, like a bank note, for two 20s.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2089, 82339, '', 30, 'As you age naturally, your family shows more and more on your face. If you deny that, you deny your heritage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2090, 99814, '', 30, 'Old age is like a plane flying through a storm. Once you\'re aboard, there\'s nothing you can do.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2091, 75945, '', 30, 'In youth the days are short and the years are long. In old age the years are short and day\'s long.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2092, 59640, '', 30, 'The aging process has you firmly in its grasp if you never get the urge to throw a snowball.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2093, 30379, '', 30, 'Age is how we determine how valuable you are.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2094, 33128, '', 30, 'Middle age is when your age starts to show around your middle.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2095, 247, '', 30, 'Aging seems to be the only available way to live a long life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(2096, 63356, '', 30, 'I think when the full horror of being fifty hits you, you should stay home and have a good cry.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2097, 69162, '', 30, 'To keep the heart unwrinkled, to be hopeful, kindly, cheerful, reverent that is to triumph over old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2098, 57067, '', 30, 'If you\'re old, don\'t try to change yourself, change your environment.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2099, 47947, '', 30, 'Old age is an excellent time for outrage. My goal is to say or do at least one outrageous thing every week.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2100, 67924, '', 30, 'I want to get old gracefully. I want to have good posture, I want to be healthy and be an example to my children.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2101, 48548, '', 30, 'What makes old age so sad is not that our joys but our hopes cease.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2102, 81145, '', 30, 'While one finds company in himself and his pursuits, he cannot feel old, no matter what his years may be.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2103, 29057, '', 30, 'To resist the frigidity of old age, one must combine the body, the mind, and the heart. And to keep these in parallel vigor one must exercise, study, and love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2104, 83154, '', 30, 'Old age is the most unexpected of all the things that can happen to a man.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2105, 63921, '', 30, 'No one can avoid aging, but aging productively is something else.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2106, 94502, '', 30, 'If you haven\'t turned rebel by twenty you\'ve got no heart if you haven\'t turned establishment by thirty you\'ve got no brains!', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2107, 91461, '', 30, 'Oh rage! Oh despair! Oh age, my enemy!', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2108, 15426, '', 30, 'I don\'t want to fight aging I want to take good care of myself, but plastic surgery and all that? I\'m not interested.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2109, 56942, '', 30, 'Middle age is the time when a man is always thinking that in a week or two he will feel as good as ever.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2110, 63846, '', 30, 'Middle age is the awkward period when Father Time starts catching up with Mother Nature.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2111, 73494, '', 30, 'Middle age is youth without levity, and age without decay.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2112, 58312, '', 30, 'No man is ever old enough to know better.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2113, 48073, '', 30, 'The denunciation of the young is a necessary part of the hygiene of older people, and greatly assists the circulation of the blood.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2114, 21543, '', 30, 'In youth we run into difficulties. In old age difficulties run into us.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2115, 3277, '', 30, 'We pay when old for the excesses of youth.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2116, 8351, '', 30, 'We\'ve put more effort into helping folks reach old age than into helping them enjoy it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2117, 14878, '', 30, 'The real sadness of fifty is not that you change so much but that you change so little.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2118, 12497, '', 30, 'I\'m not afraid of aging.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2119, 67724, '', 30, 'He has a profound respect for old age. Especially when it\'s bottled.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2120, 46435, '', 30, 'Whatever poet, orator or sage may say of it, old age is still old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2121, 6981, '', 30, 'To keep the heart unwrinkled, to be hopeful, kindly, cheerful, reverent - that is to triumph over old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2122, 44005, '', 30, 'In old age we are like a batch of letters that someone has sent. We are no longer in the past, we have arrived.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2123, 27715, '', 30, 'There\'s no such thing as old age, there is only sorrow.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2124, 98041, '', 30, 'Those who love deeply never grow old they may die of old age, but they die young.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2125, 37688, '', 30, 'The really frightening thing about middle age is the knowledge that you\'ll grow out of it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2126, 14650, '', 30, 'There is an anti-aging possibility, but it has to come from within.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2127, 85825, '', 30, 'The lovely thing about being forty is that you can appreciate twenty-five-year-old men more.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2128, 47836, '', 30, 'When a noble life has prepared old age, it is not decline that it reveals, but the first days of immortality.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2129, 44612, '', 30, 'The whole business of marshaling one\'s energies becomes more and more important as one grows older.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2130, 98895, '', 30, 'Old age adds to the respect due to virtue, but it takes nothing from the contempt inspired by vice it whitens only the hair.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2131, 65705, '', 30, 'As men get older, the toys get more expensive.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2132, 70141, '', 30, 'I find that a man is as old as his work. If his work keeps him from moving forward, he will look forward with the work.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2133, 78162, '', 30, 'Common sense is the collection of prejudices acquired by age eighteen.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2134, 64536, '', 30, 'Confusion of goals and perfection of means seems, in my opinion, to characterize our age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2135, 25810, '', 30, 'Perfection of means and confusion of ends seem to characterize our age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2136, 10644, '', 30, 'The age of a woman doesn\'t mean a thing. The best tunes are played on the oldest fiddles.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2137, 48062, '', 30, 'Life would be infinitely happier if we could only be born at the age of eighty and gradually approach eighteen.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2138, 75240, '', 30, 'Age is whatever you think it is. You are as old as you think you are.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2139, 34165, '', 30, 'In every country and every age, the priest had been hostile to Liberty.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2140, 75137, '', 30, 'The heresy of one age becomes the orthodoxy of the next.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2141, 95575, '', 30, 'The golden age is before us, not behind us.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2142, 98122, '', 30, 'Every formula of every religion has in this age of reason, to submit to the acid test of reason and universal assent.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2143, 46983, '', 30, 'No woman should ever be quite accurate about her age. It looks so calculating.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2144, 13634, '', 30, 'At twenty years of age the will reigns at thirty, the wit and at forty, the judgment.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2145, 58499, '', 30, 'Age does not protect you from love. But love, to some extent, protects you from age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2146, 62795, '', 30, 'Information is the oxygen of the modern age. It seeps through the walls topped by barbed wire, it wafts across the electrified borders.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2147, 44828, '', 30, 'Old age is just a record of one\'s whole life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2148, 88002, '', 30, 'We prefer world law in the age of self-determination to world war in the age of mass extermination.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2149, 60436, '', 30, 'Each age, it is found, must write its own books or rather, each generation for the next succeeding.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2150, 3445, '', 30, 'Education is the best provision for old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2151, 20374, '', 30, 'The secret of staying young is to live honestly, eat slowly, and lie about your age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2152, 35275, '', 30, 'Sometimes I think it would be easier to avoid old age, to die young, but then you\'d never complete your life, would you? You\'d never wholly know you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2153, 16686, '', 30, 'He who is of calm and happy nature will hardly feel the pressure of age, but to him who is of an opposite disposition youth and age are equally a burden.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2154, 91495, '', 30, 'Why should society feel responsible only for the education of children, and not for the education of all adults of every age?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2155, 76319, '', 30, 'I\'ve got volumes on how not to behave. I\'ve got more information now than a guy should have at my age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2156, 257, '', 30, 'Age is something that doesn\'t matter, unless you are a cheese.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(2157, 9218, '', 30, 'Hesitation increases in relation to risk in equal proportion to age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2158, 49642, '', 30, 'I must confess, I was born at a very early age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2159, 99558, '', 30, 'The secret of genius is to carry the spirit of the child into old age, which mean never losing your enthusiasm.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2160, 88014, '', 30, 'It is utterly false and cruelly arbitrary to put all the play and learning into childhood, all the work into middle age, and all the regrets into old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2161, 76125, '', 30, 'We aren\'t in an information age, we are in an entertainment age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2162, 82680, '', 30, 'To me - old age is always ten years older than I am.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2163, 47108, '', 30, 'Age is not important unless you\'re a cheese.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2164, 47837, '', 30, 'A woman has the age she deserves.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2165, 61681, '', 30, 'The older I grow the more I distrust the familiar doctrine that age brings wisdom.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:25'),
(2166, 79975, '', 30, 'Youngsters of the age of two and three are endowed with extraordinary strength. They can lift a dog twice their own weight and dump him into the bathtub.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2167, 63612, '', 30, 'He who has not the spirit of this age, has all the misery of it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2168, 51990, '', 30, 'I think being able to age gracefully is a very important talent. It is too late for me.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2169, 10043, '', 30, 'Error is acceptable as long as we are young but one must not drag it along into old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2170, 24179, '', 30, 'Age wrinkles the body. Quitting wrinkles the soul.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2171, 77764, '', 30, 'I don\'t need you to remind me of my age. I have a bladder to do that for me.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2172, 85759, '', 30, 'Better pass boldly into that other world, in the full glory of some passion, than fade and wither dismally with age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2173, 23876, '', 30, 'Age merely shows what children we remain.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2174, 18400, '', 30, 'Each moment of a happy lover\'s hour is worth an age of dull and common life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2175, 31979, '', 30, 'The credit of advancing science has always been due to individuals and never to the age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2176, 49630, '', 30, 'A woman telling her true age is like a buyer confiding his final price to an Armenian rug dealer.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2177, 33054, '', 30, 'How young can you die of old age?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2178, 88076, '', 30, 'Legend: A lie that has attained the dignity of age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2179, 73978, '', 30, 'Age does not protect you from love. But love, to some extent, protects you from age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2180, 11209, '', 30, 'Every great architect is - necessarily - a great poet. He must be a great original interpreter of his time, his day, his age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2181, 36180, '', 30, 'At the age of six I wanted to be a cook. At seven I wanted to be Napoleon. And my ambition has been growing steadily ever since.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2182, 16259, '', 30, 'Middle age is when you\'re sitting at home on a Saturday night and the telephone rings and you hope it isn\'t for you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2183, 67869, '', 30, 'If youth knew if age could.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2184, 93148, '', 30, 'The charm of history and its enigmatic lesson consist in the fact that, from age to age, nothing changes and yet everything is completely different.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2185, 26676, '', 30, 'Men are like wine - some turn to vinegar, but the best improve with age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2186, 9856, '', 30, 'We are all geniuses up to the age of ten.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2187, 13011, '', 30, 'It is well for the world that in most of us, by the age of thirty, the character has set like plaster, and will never soften again.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2188, 81047, '', 30, 'Old age is not a matter for sorrow. It is matter for thanks if we have left our work done behind us.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2189, 72296, '', 30, 'I suppose when they reach a certain age some men are afraid to grow up. It seems the older the men get, the younger their new wives get.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2190, 70555, '', 30, 'Publishing is in a kind of Jurassic age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2191, 27316, '', 30, 'Age is just a number. It\'s totally irrelevant unless, of course, you happen to be a bottle of wine.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2192, 77402, '', 30, 'Whatever you may look like, marry a man your own age - as your beauty fades, so will his eyesight.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2193, 92887, '', 30, 'Youth has no age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2194, 5677, '', 30, 'Youth is a blunder Manhood a struggle, Old Age a regret.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2195, 63783, '', 30, 'Nobody expects to trust his body overmuch after the age of fifty.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2196, 237, '', 30, 'In youth we learn in age we understand.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(2197, 1463, '', 30, 'Believe me, that was a happy age, before the days of architects, before the days of builders.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2198, 9717, '', 30, 'I have the problems of, I must confess, old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2199, 25061, '', 30, 'Bad news isn\'t wine. It doesn\'t improve with age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2200, 89238, '', 30, 'People who refuse to rest honorably on their laurels when they reach retirement age seem very admirable to me.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2201, 46869, '', 30, 'Not to expose your true feelings to an adult seems to be instinctive from the age of seven or eight onwards.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2202, 3784, '', 30, 'Age is a case of mind over matter. If you don\'t mind, it don\'t matter.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2203, 60699, '', 30, 'Experience is a revelation in the light of which we renounce our errors of youth for those of age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2204, 52453, '', 30, 'My view is that at a younger age your optimism is more and you have more imagination etc. You have less bias.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2205, 59281, '', 30, 'The ruling ideas of each age have ever been the ideas of its ruling class.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2206, 9615, '', 30, 'In the information age, you don\'t teach philosophy as they did after feudalism. You perform it. If Aristotle were alive today he\'d have a talk show.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2207, 43011, '', 30, 'Once I planned to write a book of poems entirely about the things in my pocket. But I found it would be too long and the age of the great epics is past.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2208, 74227, '', 30, 'The harvest of old age is the recollection and abundance of blessing previously secured.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2209, 36980, '', 30, 'It is the spirit of the age to believe that any fact, no matter how suspect, is superior to any imaginative exercise, no matter how true.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2210, 95670, '', 30, 'The arrogance of age must submit to be taught by youth.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2211, 91937, '', 30, 'The biggest disease this day and age is that of people feeling unloved.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2212, 2827, '', 30, 'Old age: the crown of life, our play\'s last act.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2213, 60307, '', 30, 'Few women, I fear, have had such reason as I have to think the long sad years of youth were worth living for the sake of middle age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2214, 89845, '', 30, 'One crowded hour of glorious life is worth an age without a name.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2215, 84242, '', 30, 'Wives are young men\'s mistresses, companions for middle age, and old men\'s nurses.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2216, 45244, '', 30, 'Wisdom doesn\'t necessarily come with age. Sometimes age just shows up all by itself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2217, 59554, '', 30, 'It is a blessed thing that in every age some one has had the individuality enough and courage enough to stand by his own convictions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2218, 55058, '', 30, 'A man does not die of love or his liver or even of old age he dies of being a man.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2219, 9326, '', 30, 'It is with an old love as it is with old age a man lives to all the miseries, but is dead to all the pleasures.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2220, 13441, '', 30, 'I cried on my 18th birthday. I thought 17 was such a nice age. You\'re young enough to get away with things, but you\'re old enough, too.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2221, 9186, '', 30, 'Rashness belongs to youth prudence to old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2222, 42231, '', 30, 'Old age is a tyrant, who forbids, under pain of death, the pleasures of youth.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2223, 78100, '', 30, 'The defects of the mind, like those of the face, grow worse with age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2224, 67304, '', 30, 'The enemy of society is middle class and the enemy of life is middle age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2225, 46382, '', 30, 'This is the patent age of new inventions for killing bodies, and for saving souls. All propagated with the best intentions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2226, 28466, '', 30, 'The mind that is wise mourns less for what age takes away than what it leaves behind.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2227, 79632, '', 30, 'The age of chivalry is past. Bores have succeeded to dragons.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2228, 36866, '', 30, 'Life, an age to the miserable, and a moment to the happy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2229, 74560, '', 30, 'We are always the same age inside.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2230, 21993, '', 30, 'I am, as I\'ve said, merely competent. But in an age of incompetence, that makes me extraordinary.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2231, 69406, '', 30, 'If you live to be one hundred, you\'ve got it made. Very few people die past that age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2232, 33554, '', 30, 'Old age has its pleasures, which, though different, are not less than the pleasures of youth.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2233, 72387, '', 30, 'Old age is when the liver spots show through your gloves.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2234, 83580, '', 30, 'What is an adult? A child blown up by age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2235, 67695, '', 30, 'Intelligent life on a planet comes of age when it first works out the reason for its own existence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2236, 97405, '', 30, 'I am of a healthy long lived race, and our minds improve with age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2237, 267, '', 30, 'The wisdom of age: don\'t stop walking.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(2238, 38174, '', 30, 'Age is strictly a case of mind over matter. If you don\'t mind, it doesn\'t matter.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2239, 13850, '', 30, 'I believe we should encourage children to sing and play instruments from an early age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2240, 43323, '', 30, 'You should not consider a man\'s age but his acts.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2241, 58602, '', 30, 'At my age flowers scare me.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2242, 83964, '', 30, 'I would go out with women my age, but there are no women my age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26');
INSERT INTO `quotes` (`id`, `order`, `entry_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `author`, `has_notif`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(2243, 62022, '', 30, 'It is not well to make great changes in old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2244, 75963, '', 30, 'Setting a good example for your children takes all the fun out of middle age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2245, 81699, '', 30, 'Young men soon give, and soon forget, affronts old age is slow in both.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2246, 46772, '', 30, 'To be happy, we must be true to nature and carry our age along with us.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2247, 63300, '', 30, 'Youth cannot know how age thinks and feels. But old men are guilty if they forget what it was to be young.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2248, 29090, '', 30, 'It is the malady of our age that the young are so busy teaching us that they have no time left to learn.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2249, 52102, '', 30, 'Marriage is not about age it\'s about finding the right person.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2250, 13364, '', 30, 'Old age is the verdict of life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2251, 46345, '', 30, 'The passions grafted on wounded pride are the most inveterate they are green and vigorous in old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2252, 1442, '', 30, 'Every age can be enchanting, provided you live within it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2253, 52920, '', 30, 'There must be a day or two in a man\'s life when he is the precise age for something important.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2254, 64922, '', 30, 'I don\'t care about age very much.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2255, 25534, '', 30, 'Old age and the passage of time teach all things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2256, 51655, '', 30, 'I think age is a very high price to pay for maturity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2257, 93911, '', 30, 'Children rarely want to know who their parents were before they were parents, and when age finally stirs their curiosity, there is no parent left to tell them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2258, 63818, '', 30, 'Middle age occurs when you are too young to take up golf and too old to rush up to the net.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2259, 76005, '', 30, 'Old age: I fall asleep during the funerals of my friends.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2260, 92924, '', 30, 'Staid middle age loves the hurricane passions of opera.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2261, 92695, '', 30, 'Middle age went by while I was mourning for my lost youth.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2262, 8330, '', 30, 'In passing, we should note this curious mark of our own age: the only absolute allowed is the absolute insistence that there is no absolute.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2263, 73081, '', 30, 'Not even old age knows how to love death.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2264, 44289, '', 30, 'I think that a man should not live beyond the age when he begins to deteriorate, when the flame that lighted the brightest moment of his life has weakened.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:26'),
(2265, 17939, '', 30, 'Temper never mellows with age, and a sharp tongue is the only edged tool that grows keener with constant use.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2266, 6093, '', 30, 'It is not by the gray of the hair that one knows the age of the heart.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2267, 19115, '', 30, 'Another belief of mine that everyone else my age is an adult, whereas I am merely in disguise.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2268, 80307, '', 30, 'Age carries all things away, even the mind.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2269, 55706, '', 30, 'Age steals away all things, even the mind.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2270, 99408, '', 30, 'In fact, my courage and my bravery at a young age was the thing I was bullied for, a kind of \'Who do you think you are?\'', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2271, 17556, '', 30, 'As technology advances, it reverses the characteristics of every situation again and again. The age of automation is going to be the age of \'do it yourself.\'', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2272, 11698, '', 30, 'The excess of our youth are checks written against our age and they are payable with interest thirty years later.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2273, 99769, '', 30, 'I smoke ten to fifteen cigars a day. At my age I have to hold on to something.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2274, 19942, '', 30, 'I\'m at the age now where just putting my cigar in its holder is a thrill.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2275, 20362, '', 30, 'No man was ever so completely skilled in the conduct of life, as not to receive new information from age and experience.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2276, 64919, '', 30, 'Interest is the spur of the people, but glory that of great souls. Invention is the talent of youth, and judgment of age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2277, 38227, '', 30, 'Invention is the talent of youth, as judgment is of age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2278, 24773, '', 30, 'I\'m very pleased to be here. Let\'s face it, at my age I\'m very pleased to be anywhere.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2279, 1429, '', 30, 'I must be more sensible and realize that at my age, illusions are hardly permitted and they will always destroy me.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2280, 630, '', 30, 'My age and health will never allow me to realize the dream of art I\'ve been pursuing all my life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2281, 46398, '', 30, 'O love, if I regret the age when one savors you, it is not for the hour of pleasure, but for the one that follows it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2282, 80486, '', 30, 'Age does not matter if the matter does not age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2283, 96057, '', 30, 'Ours is essentially a tragic age, so we refuse to take it tragically.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2284, 32153, '', 30, 'Ours is an excessively conscious age. We know so much, we feel so little.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2285, 77283, '', 30, 'Everybody past a certain age, regardless of how they look on the outside, pretty much constantly dreams of being able to escape from their lives.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2286, 22884, '', 30, 'One keeps forgetting old age up to the very brink of the grave.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2287, 77392, '', 30, 'In the age of the individual\'s liquidation, the question of individuality must be raised anew.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2288, 55359, '', 30, 'Women lie about their age men lie about their income.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2289, 75476, '', 30, 'A major advantage of age is learning to accept people without passing judgment.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2290, 60323, '', 30, 'The people who live in a golden age usually go around complaining how yellow everything looks.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2291, 69084, '', 30, 'There was no respect for youth when I was young, and now that I am old, there is no respect for age, I missed it coming and going.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2292, 13490, '', 30, 'Save your money. You\'re going to need twice as much money in your old age as you think.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2293, 90992, '', 30, 'Middle age is when your old classmates are so grey and wrinkled and bald they don\'t recognize you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2294, 7068, '', 30, 'You can judge your age by the amount of pain you feel when you come in contact with a new idea.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2295, 58053, '', 30, 'Middle age is when you\'ve met so many people that every new person you meet reminds you of someone else.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2296, 39939, '', 30, 'There are people whose watch stops at a certain hour and who remain permanently at that age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2297, 23086, '', 30, 'They that have lived a single day have lived an age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2298, 2322, '', 30, 'Old age, calm, expanded, broad with the haughty breadth of the universe, old age flowing free with the delicious near-by freedom of death.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2299, 16716, '', 30, 'At a certain age it just became apparent to me that this was probably the work that I would have to do.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2300, 89284, '', 30, 'Every age needs men who will redeem the time by living with a vision of the things that are to be.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2301, 75328, '', 30, 'I shall not grow conservative with age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2302, 89473, '', 30, 'When you get to my age life seems little more than one long march to and from the lavatory.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2303, 25991, '', 30, 'I think, if you put a camera in anyone\'s life and document it daily from the age of 21 to 27, there are going to be things that aren\'t always pretty.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2304, 45758, '', 30, 'Where children are, there is the golden age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2305, 71320, '', 30, 'In an age of incompetence, I\'ve been able to last in this crazy business. I actually know how to play my ax and write a song. That\'s my job.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2306, 28494, '', 30, 'In this age of media and Internet access, we are much more talkative than ever before.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2307, 38248, '', 30, 'Every time I see something terrible, it\'s like I see it at age 19. I keep a freshness that way.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2308, 29015, '', 30, 'I hate to mention age, but I come from an era when we weren\'t consumed by technology and television.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2309, 31884, '', 30, 'Morality comes with the sad wisdom of age, when the sense of curiosity has withered.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2310, 24837, '', 30, 'Every age yearns for a more beautiful world. The deeper the desperation and the depression about the confusing present, the more intense that yearning.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2311, 93289, '', 30, 'Does age matter? Time doesn\'t matter.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2312, 64731, '', 30, 'I figured out it was a social thing, what women were allowed to do. At a very young age, I decided I was not going to follow women\'s rules.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2313, 72304, '', 30, 'We were really grown up for our age and it was an incredible special band.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2314, 62345, '', 30, 'Age is the first limitation on roles that I\'ve ever had to encounter, and I hit that awhile ago.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2315, 27796, '', 30, 'I can\'t hit on women in public any more. I didn\'t decide this it just doesn\'t feel right at my age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2316, 15543, '', 30, 'This is the first age that\'s ever paid much attention to the future, which is a little ironic since we may not have one.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2317, 50884, '', 30, 'The secret of long life is double careers. One to about age sixty, then another for the next thirty years.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2318, 92425, '', 30, 'We all know now that people can look good for their age. It isn\'t so extraordinary, I don\'t know why people go on about it so much.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2319, 36191, '', 30, 'I\'ve gotten crankier in my old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2320, 78492, '', 30, 'I\'ve been very competitive by nature from a young age, whether it was eating a bowl of pasta faster than somebody else, or always wanting to be the first one in line.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2321, 18035, '', 30, 'Death comes not to the living soul, nor age to the loving heart.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2322, 33329, '', 30, 'Not by age but by capacity is wisdom acquired.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2323, 32158, '', 30, 'Whoever marries the spirit of this age will find himself a widower in the next.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2324, 85793, '', 30, 'Of middle age the best that can be said is that a middle-aged person has likely learned how to have a little fun in spite of his troubles.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2325, 3365, '', 30, 'Old age is always wakeful as if, the longer linked with life, the less man has to do with aught that looks like death.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2326, 41576, '', 30, 'Even from a very early age, I knew I didn\'t want to miss out on anything life had to offer just because it might be considered dangerous.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2327, 71398, '', 30, 'We live in an age where anonymity is growing in magnitude like a bomb going off.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2328, 72006, '', 30, 'We tried not to age, but time had its rage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2329, 58450, '', 30, 'Bring a wife home to your house when you are of the right age, not far short of 30 years, nor much above this is the right time for marriage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2330, 43791, '', 30, 'There are only two things a child will share willingly communicable diseases and its mother\'s age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2331, 91754, '', 30, 'Although it is generally known, I think it\'s about time to announce that I was born at a very early age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2332, 21558, '', 30, 'Your body actually reminds you about your age and your injuries - the body has a stronger memory than your mind.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2333, 78117, '', 30, 'People dance at any age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2334, 45038, '', 30, 'I\'ve never worried about age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2335, 13561, '', 30, 'If you\'re extremely, painfully frightened of age, it shows.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2336, 32106, '', 30, 'Let age, not envy, draw wrinkles on thy cheeks.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2337, 63576, '', 30, 'Everyone talks about age, but it\'s not about age. It\'s about work ethic. Winning never gets old.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2338, 65127, '', 30, 'I came of age believing that, no matter what happened, I would always be able to support myself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2339, 46094, '', 30, 'People tend to become more emotionally intelligent as they age and mature.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2340, 5891, '', 30, 'With age, you get to a place where you don\'t want to knock people out. You just want to give people a hug.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2341, 72301, '', 30, 'Age is no barrier. It\'s a limitation you put on your mind.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2342, 98259, '', 30, 'Whoever, fleeing marriage and the sorrows that women cause, does not wish to wed comes to a deadly old age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2343, 52599, '', 30, 'Age has been the perfect fire extinguisher for flaming youth.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2344, 69859, '', 30, 'I prefer younger men. In some ways, they are much more open to a woman being stronger and independent then some of the men my age.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2345, 65043, '', 30, 'At my age, no one is married, no one has kids, no one has a career.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2346, 61857, '', 30, 'One of the many pleasures of old age is giving things up.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2347, 73526, '', 30, 'We virtually never feel our age, but thinking that we should can lead to disaster.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2348, 87170, '', 30, 'There\'s a vintage which comes with age and experience.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2349, 73046, '', 30, 'Every age develops its own peculiar forms of pathology, which express in exaggerated form its underlying character structure.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:15:51', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2350, 88418, '', 21, 'I learned that courage was not the absence of fear, but the triumph over it. The brave man is not he who does not feel afraid, but he who conquers that fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2351, 27614, '', 21, 'Courage is what it takes to stand up and speak courage is also what it takes to sit down and listen.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2352, 33206, '', 21, 'There are no easy answers\' but there are simple answers. We must have the courage to do what we know is morally right.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2353, 79096, '', 21, 'Courage is grace under pressure.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2354, 93794, '', 21, 'We must build dikes of courage to hold back the flood of fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2355, 83136, '', 21, 'Courage is resistance to fear, mastery of fear, not absence of fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2356, 63027, '', 21, 'He who is not courageous enough to take risks will accomplish nothing in life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2357, 90729, '', 21, 'Courage is not simply one of the virtues, but the form of every virtue at the testing point.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2358, 47072, '', 21, 'Courage is being scared to death... and saddling up anyway.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2359, 81923, '', 21, 'You will never do anything in this world without courage. It is the greatest quality of the mind next to honor.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2360, 56029, '', 21, 'Efforts and courage are not enough without purpose and direction.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2361, 74553, '', 21, 'One man with courage is a majority.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2362, 65100, '', 21, 'Have the courage to say no. Have the courage to face the truth. Do the right thing because it is right. These are the magic keys to living your life with integrity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2363, 96884, '', 21, 'Faced with what is right, to leave it undone shows a lack of courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2364, 66532, '', 21, 'How few there are who have courage enough to own their faults, or resolution enough to mend them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2365, 23347, '', 21, 'Who could refrain that had a heart to love and in that heart courage to make love known?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:27'),
(2366, 8882, '', 21, 'Inaction breeds doubt and fear. Action breeds confidence and courage. If you want to conquer fear, do not sit home and think about it. Go out and get busy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2367, 6090, '', 21, 'A great part of courage is the courage of having done the thing before.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2368, 67971, '', 21, 'Have courage for the great sorrows of life and patience for the small ones and when you have laboriously accomplished your daily task, go to sleep in peace.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2369, 78137, '', 21, 'He is a man of courage who does not run away, but remains at his post and fights against the enemy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2370, 78429, '', 21, 'From caring comes courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2371, 42766, '', 21, 'Life shrinks or expands in proportion to one\'s courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2372, 31039, '', 21, 'The only service a friend can really render is to keep up your courage by holding up to you a mirror in which you can see a noble image of yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2373, 94178, '', 21, 'Failure is unimportant. It takes courage to make a fool of yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2374, 2354, '', 21, 'The most courageous act is still to think for yourself. Aloud.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2375, 9482, '', 21, 'Those who lack the courage will always find a philosophy to justify it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2376, 74550, '', 21, 'Success is never final, failure is never fatal. It\'s courage that counts.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2377, 95731, '', 21, 'Courage is contagious. When a brave man takes a stand, the spines of others are often stiffened.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2378, 29967, '', 21, 'Courage is a kind of salvation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2379, 84538, '', 21, 'Courage is fear holding on a minute longer.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2380, 39042, '', 21, 'Man cannot discover new oceans unless he has the courage to lose sight of the shore.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2381, 31247, '', 21, 'Creativity requires the courage to let go of certainties.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2382, 5485, '', 21, 'What would life be if we had no courage to attempt anything?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2383, 79355, '', 21, 'Courage is fire, and bullying is smoke.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2384, 69077, '', 21, 'It requires more courage to suffer than to die.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2385, 75655, '', 21, 'Courage is found in unlikely places.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2386, 60869, '', 21, 'Courage is the greatest of all virtues, because if you haven\'t courage, you may not have an opportunity to use any of the others.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2387, 61339, '', 21, 'To have courage for whatever comes in life - everything lies in that.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2388, 17054, '', 21, 'Any intelligent fool can make things bigger and more complex... It takes a touch of genius - and a lot of courage to move in the opposite direction.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2389, 86120, '', 21, 'The opposite for courage is not cowardice, it is conformity. Even a dead fish can go with the flow.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2390, 25860, '', 21, 'One man with courage makes a majority.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2391, 6895, '', 21, 'Real courage is when you know you\'re licked before you begin, but you begin anyway and see it through no matter what.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2392, 61010, '', 21, 'The secret to happiness is freedom... And the secret to freedom is courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2393, 38309, '', 21, 'A lot of people do not muster the courage to live their dreams because they are afraid to die.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2394, 31694, '', 21, 'We must have courage to bet on our ideas, to take the calculated risk, and to act. Everyday living requires courage if life is to be effective and bring happiness.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2395, 41504, '', 21, 'The courage to be is the courage to accept oneself, in spite of being unacceptable.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2396, 71392, '', 21, 'It is only necessary to have courage, for strength without self-confidence is useless.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2397, 58945, '', 21, 'We have a powerful potential in out youth, and we must have the courage to change old ideas and practices so that we may direct their power toward good ends.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2398, 67384, '', 21, 'Courage - a perfect sensibility of the measure of danger, and a mental willingness to endure it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2399, 35744, '', 21, 'If you are lucky enough to find a way of life you love, you have to find the courage to live it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2400, 1190, '', 21, 'Courage is not the absence of despair it is, rather, the capacity to move ahead in spite of despair.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2401, 37273, '', 21, 'Courage is being afraid but going on anyhow.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2402, 53570, '', 21, 'Clear thinking requires courage rather than intelligence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2403, 95522, '', 21, 'People with courage and character always seem sinister to the rest.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2404, 56137, '', 21, 'Do not lose courage in considering your own imperfections.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2405, 56449, '', 21, 'The best protection any woman can have... is courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2406, 86396, '', 21, 'The trials on the road to world harmony are no greater than the courage of those who accept the challenge.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2407, 93071, '', 21, 'Being deeply loved by someone gives you strength, while loving someone deeply gives you courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2408, 36014, '', 21, 'Success is not final, failure is not fatal: it is the courage to continue that counts.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2409, 62371, '', 21, 'We gain strength, and courage, and confidence by each experience in which we really stop to look fear in the face... we must do that which we think we cannot.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2410, 43539, '', 21, 'All our dreams can come true, if we have the courage to pursue them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2411, 57708, '', 21, 'Mistakes are always forgivable, if one has the courage to admit them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2412, 25921, '', 21, 'My great hope is to laugh as much as I cry to get my work done and try to love somebody and have the courage to accept the love in return.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2413, 88539, '', 21, 'You have to accept whatever comes and the only important thing is that you meet it with courage and with the best that you have to give.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2414, 4888, '', 21, 'Courage means to keep working a relationship, to continue seeking solutions to difficult problems, and to stay focused during stressful periods.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2415, 43310, '', 21, 'History, despite its wrenching pain, cannot be unlived, but if faced with courage, need not be lived again.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2416, 4003, '', 21, 'You don\'t develop courage by being happy in your relationships everyday. You develop it by surviving difficult times and challenging adversity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2417, 8602, '', 21, 'It is curious that physical courage should be so common in the world and moral courage so rare.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2418, 46064, '', 21, 'Wisdom, compassion, and courage are the three universally recognized moral qualities of men.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2419, 60471, '', 21, 'Courage is rightly esteemed the first of human qualities... because it is the quality which guarantees all others.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2420, 96134, '', 21, 'It takes courage to grow up and become who you really are.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2421, 1462, '', 21, 'The courage of life is often a less dramatic spectacle than the courage of a final moment but it is no less a magnificent mixture of triumph and tragedy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2422, 41646, '', 21, 'Courage is the first of human qualities because it is the quality which guarantees the others.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2423, 71309, '', 21, 'The greatest test of courage on earth is to bear defeat without losing heart.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2424, 43393, '', 21, 'Every man has his own courage, and is betrayed because he seeks in himself the courage of other persons.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2425, 73572, '', 21, 'The principles of living greatly include the capacity to face trouble with courage, disappointment with cheerfulness, and trial with humility.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2426, 48573, '', 21, 'Courage is a mean with regard to fear and confidence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2427, 39139, '', 21, 'I want to grow old without facelifts. I want to have the courage to be loyal to the face I have made.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2428, 91177, '', 21, 'A man of great common sense and good taste - meaning thereby a man without originality or moral courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2429, 78220, '', 21, 'It is only through labor and painful effort, by grim energy and resolute courage, that we move on to better things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2430, 35710, '', 21, 'I never thought much of the courage of a lion tamer. Inside the cage he is at least safe from people.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2431, 74726, '', 21, 'True courage is being afraid, and going ahead and doing your job anyhow, that\'s what courage is.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2432, 86889, '', 21, 'Courtesy is as much a mark of a gentleman as courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2433, 68950, '', 21, 'He\'s a man of great common sense and good taste - meaning thereby a man without originality or moral courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2434, 68735, '', 21, 'Courage is like love it must have hope for nourishment.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2435, 89879, '', 21, 'Courage is knowing what not to fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2436, 52109, '', 21, 'Real nobility is based on scorn, courage, and profound indifference.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2437, 26492, '', 21, 'It takes a lot of courage to show your dreams to someone else.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2438, 69847, '', 21, 'Believers, look up - take courage. The angels are nearer than you think.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2439, 61582, '', 21, 'All of us have moments in our lives that test our courage. Taking children into a house with a white carpet is one of them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2440, 3535, '', 21, 'Change will never happen when people lack the ability and courage to see themselves for who they are.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2441, 15775, '', 21, 'A mode of conduct, a standard of courage, discipline, fortitude and integrity can do a great deal to make a woman beautiful.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2442, 54726, '', 21, 'Give us grace and strength to forbear and to persevere. Give us courage and gaiety and the quiet mind, spare to us our friends, soften to us our enemies.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2443, 79956, '', 21, 'Keep your fears to yourself, but share your courage with others.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2444, 71587, '', 21, 'Most of us have far more courage than we ever dreamed we possessed.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2445, 62886, '', 21, 'Life is to be entered upon with courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2446, 65877, '', 21, 'I\'ve been through it all, baby, I\'m mother courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2447, 38917, '', 21, 'We need to find the courage to say no to the things and people that are not serving us if we want to rediscover ourselves and live our lives with authenticity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2448, 3739, '', 21, 'Untutored courage is useless in the face of educated bullets.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2449, 22655, '', 21, 'Courage is almost a contradiction in terms. It means a strong desire to live taking the form of readiness to die.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2450, 93309, '', 21, 'The first virtue in a soldier is endurance of fatigue courage is only the second virtue.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2451, 19430, '', 21, 'There can be no failure to a man who has not lost his courage, his character, his self respect, or his self-confidence. He is still a King.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2452, 4267, '', 21, 'Sometimes even to live is an act of courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2453, 12262, '', 21, 'Healing takes courage, and we all have courage, even if we have to dig a little to find it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2454, 38451, '', 21, 'If human beings had genuine courage, they\'d wear their costumes every day of the year, not just on Halloween.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2455, 98586, '', 21, 'There is nothing in the world so much admired as a man who knows how to bear unhappiness with courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2456, 3555, '', 21, 'Courage and grace are a formidable mixture. The only place to see it is in the bullring.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2457, 29562, '', 21, 'The courage we desire and prize is not the courage to die decently, but to live manfully.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2458, 67303, '', 21, 'The paradox of courage is that a man must be a little careless of his life even in order to keep it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2459, 82607, '', 21, 'Just as courage imperils life, fear protects it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2460, 8505, '', 21, 'There can be no great courage where there is no confidence or assurance, and half the battle is in the conviction that we can do what we undertake.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2461, 45945, '', 21, 'We need men with moral courage to speak and write their real thoughts, and to stand by their convictions, even to the very death.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2462, 73122, '', 21, 'The weak in courage is strong in cunning.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2463, 5343, '', 21, 'Freedom is the sure possession of those alone who have the courage to defend it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:28'),
(2464, 28863, '', 21, 'You will find as you grow older that courage is the rarest of all qualities to be found in public life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2465, 60685, '', 21, 'Every day begins with an act of courage and hope: getting out of bed.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2466, 25983, '', 21, 'A team is where a boy can prove his courage on his own. A gang is where a coward goes to hide.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2467, 72473, '', 21, 'It is a blessed thing that in every age some one has had the individuality enough and courage enough to stand by his own convictions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2468, 71579, '', 21, 'The opposite of courage in our society is not cowardice, it is conformity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2469, 21422, '', 21, 'Perfect courage is to do without witnesses what one would be capable of doing with the world looking on.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2470, 24994, '', 21, 'Courage can\'t see around corners but goes around them anyway.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2471, 22432, '', 21, 'The only courage that matters is the kind that gets you from one moment to the next.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2472, 53015, '', 21, 'Courage and perseverance have a magical talisman, before which difficulties disappear and obstacles vanish into air.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2473, 18344, '', 21, 'Courage without conscience is a wild beast.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2474, 9213, '', 21, 'Why should we honour those that die upon the field of battle? A man may show as reckless a courage in entering into the abyss of himself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2475, 65463, '', 21, 'To dare to live alone is the rarest courage since there are many who had rather meet their bitterest enemy in the field, than their own hearts in their closet.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2476, 33991, '', 21, 'Traits like humility, courage, and empathy are easily overlooked - but it\'s immensely important to find them in your closest relationships.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2477, 5622, '', 21, 'Valor is stability, not of legs and arms, but of courage and the soul.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2478, 36595, '', 21, 'It is courage, courage, courage, that raises the blood of life to crimson splendor. Live bravely and present a brave front to adversity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2479, 4068, '', 21, 'All you need is the plan, the road map, and the courage to press on to your destination.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2480, 7314, '', 21, 'Courage consists not in hazarding without fear but being resolutely minded in a just cause.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2481, 13677, '', 21, 'To create one\'s world in any of the arts takes courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2482, 19191, '', 21, 'The kind of beauty I want most is the hard-to-get kind that comes from within - strength, courage, dignity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2483, 84801, '', 21, 'Genius is talent set on fire by courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2484, 84289, '', 21, 'We\'ve begun to raise daughters more like sons... but few have the courage to raise our sons more like our daughters.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2485, 42073, '', 21, 'Despair gives courage to a coward.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2486, 30237, '', 21, 'He that fails in his endeavors after wealth or power will not long retain either honesty or courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2487, 43580, '', 21, 'Either life entails courage, or it ceases to be life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2488, 63770, '', 21, 'Courage stands halfway between cowardice and rashness, one of which is a lack, the other an excess of courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2489, 62921, '', 21, 'Everyone has talent. What is rare is the courage to follow the talent to the dark place where it leads.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2490, 50052, '', 21, 'To persevere, trusting in what hopes he has, is courage in a man.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2491, 14856, '', 21, 'Political courage is not political suicide.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2492, 4722, '', 21, 'Unless a reviewer has the courage to give you unqualified praise, I say ignore the bastard.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2493, 62568, '', 21, 'The strangest, most generous, and proudest of all virtues is true courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2494, 30646, '', 21, 'Courage, above all things, is the first quality of a warrior.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2495, 54894, '', 21, 'I beg you take courage the brave soul can mend even disaster.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2496, 66258, '', 21, 'The more wit the less courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2497, 56956, '', 21, 'One man scorned and covered with scars still strove with his last ounce of courage to reach the unreachable stars and the world will be better for this.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2498, 48592, '', 21, 'Take chances, make mistakes. That\'s how you grow. Pain nourishes your courage. You have to fail in order to practice being brave.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2499, 87214, '', 21, 'Determination, energy, and courage appear spontaneously when we care deeply about something. We take risks that are unimaginable in any other context.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2500, 7903, '', 21, 'Way down deep, we\'re all motivated by the same urges. Cats have the courage to live by them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2501, 42669, '', 21, 'Suffering! We owe to it all that is good in us, all that gives value to life we owe to it pity, we owe to it courage, we owe to it all the virtues.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2502, 79205, '', 21, 'Failure is only postponed success as long as courage \'coaches\' ambition. The habit of persistence is the habit of victory.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2503, 19396, '', 21, 'It takes as much courage to have tried and failed as it does to have tried and succeeded.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2504, 82020, '', 21, 'Courage consists not in blindly overlooking danger, but in seeing it, and conquering it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2505, 42242, '', 21, 'Creativity takes courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2506, 28972, '', 21, 'Courage enlarges, cowardice diminishes resources. In desperate straits the fears of the timid aggravate the dangers that imperil the brave.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2507, 23878, '', 21, 'If we survive danger it steels our courage more than anything else.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2508, 78162, '', 21, 'There are pretenders to piety as well as to courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2509, 65449, '', 21, 'Religion in its humility restores man to his only dignity, the courage to live by grace.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2510, 50044, '', 21, 'Courage that grows from constitution often forsakes a man when he has occasion for it courage which arises from a sense of duty acts in a uniform manner.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2511, 89809, '', 21, 'We are very much what others think of us. The reception our observations meet with gives us courage to proceed, or damps our efforts.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2512, 78878, '', 21, 'It takes someone with a vision of the possibilities to attain new levels of experience. Someone with the courage to live his dreams.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2513, 31119, '', 21, 'The principal act of courage is to endure and withstand dangers doggedly rather than to attack them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2514, 26068, '', 21, 'Have the courage to act instead of react.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2515, 20605, '', 21, 'Time is neutral and does not change things. With courage and initiative, leaders change things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2516, 7573, '', 21, 'In strife who inquires whether stratagem or courage was used?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2517, 55433, '', 21, 'In fact, my courage and my bravery at a young age was the thing I was bullied for, a kind of \'Who do you think you are?\'', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2518, 32270, '', 21, 'There is in true beauty, as in courage, something which narrow souls cannot dare to admire.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2519, 37611, '', 21, 'Physical courage, which despises all danger, will make a man brave in one way and moral courage, which despises all opinion, will make a man brave in another.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2520, 86973, '', 21, 'I\'m sick of not having the courage to be an absolute nobody.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2521, 85872, '', 21, 'Courage conquers all things: it even gives strength to the body.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2522, 37882, '', 21, 'Courage is the price that life exacts for granting peace.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2523, 18826, '', 21, 'Courage, my friends \'tis not too late to build a better world.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2524, 53162, '', 21, 'Courage is doing what you are afraid to do. There can be no courage unless you are scared.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2525, 73809, '', 21, 'Courage is what preserves our liberty, safety, life, and our homes and parents, our country and children. Courage comprises all things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2526, 83936, '', 21, 'Courage is often lack of insight, whereas cowardice in many cases is based on good information.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2527, 95269, '', 21, 'Courage is simply the willingness to be afraid and act anyway.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2528, 4170, '', 21, 'Whether you be man or woman you will never do anything in this world without courage. It is the greatest quality of the mind next to honor.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2529, 46989, '', 21, 'Without courage, wisdom bears no fruit.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2530, 65681, '', 21, 'He who loses wealth loses much he who loses a friend loses more but he that loses his courage loses all.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2531, 20399, '', 21, 'True courage is not the brutal force of vulgar heroes, but the firm resolve of virtue and reason.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2532, 68572, '', 21, 'Physical bravery is an animal instinct moral bravery is much higher and truer courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2533, 3159, '', 21, 'Hope lies in dreams, in imagination, and in the courage of those who dare to make dreams into reality.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29');
INSERT INTO `quotes` (`id`, `order`, `entry_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `author`, `has_notif`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(2534, 37559, '', 21, 'Success is that old ABC - ability, breaks, and courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2535, 31482, '', 21, 'Audacity augments courage hesitation, fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2536, 17177, '', 21, 'The courage of very ordinary people is all that stands between us and the dark.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2537, 46028, '', 21, 'To live we must conquer incessantly, we must have the courage to be happy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2538, 31516, '', 21, 'I have the courage of my convictions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2539, 31031, '', 21, 'In all realms of life it takes courage to stretch your limits, express your power, and fulfill your potential... it\'s no different in the financial realm.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2540, 4766, '', 21, 'A wise woman knows how to summon her courage and do what is right, rather than what is easy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2541, 49285, '', 21, 'Decision is a risk rooted in the courage of being free.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2542, 74847, '', 21, 'I think there\'s a difference between ditzy and dumb. Dumb is just not knowing. Ditzy is having the courage to ask!', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2543, 15224, '', 21, 'The test of courage comes when we are in the minority. The test of tolerance comes when we are in the majority.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2544, 45334, '', 21, 'I have no physical courage, I\'ve asked for a double.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2545, 34500, '', 21, 'Courage is the ladder on which all the other virtues mount.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:29'),
(2546, 7519, '', 21, 'Courage is the capacity to confront what can be imagined.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2547, 22792, '', 21, 'Patience, that blending of moral courage with physical timidity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2548, 91195, '', 21, 'The last thing a woman will consent to discover in a man whom she loves, or on whom she simply depends, is want of courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2549, 16866, '', 21, 'Courage in danger is half the battle.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2550, 66635, '', 21, 'Courage easily finds its own eloquence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2551, 67305, '', 21, 'Good courage in a bad affair is half of the evil overcome.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2552, 31109, '', 21, 'The courage of a soldier is found to be the cheapest and most common quality of human nature.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2553, 66926, '', 21, 'Courage is a special kind of knowledge: the knowledge of how to fear what ought to be feared and how not to fear what ought not to be feared.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2554, 34587, '', 21, 'My mother taught me that we all have the power to achieve our dreams. What I lacked was the courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2555, 10556, '', 21, 'Every man of courage is a man of his word.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2556, 75726, '', 21, 'A man of courage never needs weapons, but he may need bail.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2557, 17975, '', 21, 'But courage which goes against military expediency is stupidity, or, if it is insisted upon by a commander, irresponsibility.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2558, 39618, '', 21, 'Cowardice and courage are never without a measure of affectation. Nor is love. Feelings are never true. They play with their mirrors.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2559, 39207, '', 21, 'Let us go forth with fear and courage and rage to save the world.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2560, 48093, '', 21, 'Fashion should not be expected to serve in the stead of courage or character.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2561, 12142, '', 21, 'It takes a lot of courage to face up to things you can\'t do because we feed ourselves so much denial.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2562, 66033, '', 21, 'Never undertake anything for which you wouldn\'t have the courage to ask the blessings of heaven.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2563, 39758, '', 21, 'The courage to imagine the otherwise is our greatest resource, adding color and suspense to all our life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2564, 2588, '', 21, 'Discouragement is not the absence of adequacy but the absence of courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2565, 46392, '', 21, 'Conscience is the root of all true courage if a man would be brave let him obey his conscience.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2566, 78362, '', 21, 'I always disliked dogs, those protectors of cowards who lack the courage to fight an assailant themselves.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2567, 48721, '', 21, 'You cannot build character and courage by destroying men\'s initiative and independence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2568, 18189, '', 21, 'Courage is the art of being the only one who knows you\'re scared to death.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2569, 87040, '', 21, 'If you could get up the courage to begin, you have the courage to succeed.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2570, 16436, '', 21, 'Nothing gives us courage more readily than the desire to avoid looking like a damn fool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2571, 8756, '', 21, 'What is more mortifying than to feel that you have missed the plum for want of courage to shake the tree?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2572, 63771, '', 21, 'Courage is always rewarded.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2573, 87135, '', 21, 'The enchanting charms of this sublime science reveal only to those who have the courage to go deeply into it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2574, 56475, '', 21, 'With enough courage, you can do without a reputation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2575, 11933, '', 21, 'I have reached the conclusion that those who have physical courage also have moral courage. Physical courage is a great test.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2576, 21241, '', 21, 'It takes a good deal of physical courage to ride a horse. This, however, I have. I get it at about forty cents a flask, and take it as required.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2577, 50845, '', 21, 'Success means having the courage, the determination, and the will to become the person you believe you were meant to be.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2578, 9221, '', 21, 'It is easy enough to praise men for the courage of their convictions. I wish I could teach the sad young of this mealy generation the courage of their confusions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2579, 18240, '', 21, 'You have to do what you need to do as an artist. You have to have that courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2580, 47778, '', 21, 'I don\'t understand why people say that I am full of courage. I feel terribly nervous.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2581, 14567, '', 21, 'A statesman wants courage and a statesman wants vision but believe me, after six months\' experience, he wants first, second, third and all the time - patience.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2582, 7410, '', 21, 'I went through a long period where I was afraid of doing things I wanted to do, and you get your courage back, which is what\'s important.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2583, 27783, '', 21, 'On sensitive issues, talk isn\'t cheap - it takes real courage to pry open topics nailed shut.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2584, 75680, '', 21, 'I have a lot of courage. I\'m a realist.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2585, 33980, '', 21, 'A military coup needs a sacrifice and courage that you can\'t find in an army without morale.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2586, 94090, '', 21, 'Courage is poorly housed that dwells in numbers the lion never counts the herd that are about him, nor weighs how many flocks he has to scatter.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2587, 5552, '', 21, 'Optimism is essential to achievement and it is also the foundation of courage and true progress.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2588, 26791, '', 21, 'We want deeper sincerity of motive, a greater courage in speech and earnestness in action.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2589, 62364, '', 21, 'I was a little doubtful about the propriety of going to the Mammoth Cave without a gentleman escort, but if two ladies travel alone they must have the courage of men.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2590, 67117, '', 21, 'You can\'t test courage cautiously.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2591, 75008, '', 21, 'Being gifted needs courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2592, 57773, '', 21, 'Some of the greatest survivors have been women. Look at the courage so many women have shown after surviving earthquakes in the rubble for days on end.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2593, 11141, '', 21, 'Limit to courage? There is no limit to courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2594, 91363, '', 21, 'There is hope in dreams, imagination, and in the courage of those who wish to make those dreams a reality.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2595, 47529, '', 21, 'Nothing gives a fearful man more courage than another\'s fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2596, 80232, '', 21, 'Your determination, selflessness and courage have brought the freedom struggle towards its fulfilment.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2597, 36959, '', 21, 'Real courage is knowing what faces you and knowing how to face it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2598, 58897, '', 21, 'True courage is like a kite a contrary wind raises it higher.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2599, 60401, '', 21, 'One has to have the courage of one\'s pessimism.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2600, 52821, '', 21, 'It takes a certain courage and a certain greatness to be truly base.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2601, 17513, '', 21, 'Until the day of his death, no man can be sure of his courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2602, 76903, '', 21, 'Falsehood is cowardice, the truth courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2603, 9103, '', 21, 'Have the courage to be ignorant of a great number of things, in order to avoid the calamity of being ignorant of everything.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2604, 61044, '', 21, 'Intellectuals try to keep going. But their situation is very difficult. Those who have had the courage to voice their opposition have often paid a very high price.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2605, 89913, '', 21, 'I\'ve always been inspired by artists who have shown musical and intellectual curiosity and the courage to take risks.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2606, 34205, '', 21, 'Courage! I have shown it for years think you I shall lose it at the moment when my sufferings are to end?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2607, 38194, '', 21, 'Men was formed for society, and is neither capable of living alone, nor has the courage to do it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2608, 22355, '', 21, 'One of the things that makes Hamlet unique among Shakespeare\'s characters is his courage to face up to the darker elements of his personality.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2609, 3614, '', 21, 'Often the test of courage is not to die but to live.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2610, 22495, '', 21, 'I have always had the courage for the new things that life sometimes offers.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2611, 50995, '', 21, 'Physical courage is a great test.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2612, 90029, '', 21, 'In my old age, I have been thinking about this, and I have reached the conclusion that those who have physical courage also have moral courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2613, 35143, '', 21, 'Ingenuity, plus courage, plus work, equals miracles.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2614, 47949, '', 21, 'Love makes a subtle man out of a crude one, it gives eloquence to the mute, it gives courage the cowardly and makes the idle quick and sharp.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2615, 7251, '', 21, 'The courage of a soldier is heightened by his knowledge of his profession.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2616, 59347, '', 21, 'Such decisions will be far reaching and difficult. But you never lacked courage in the past. Your courage is now needed for the future.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2617, 78769, '', 21, 'Courage is never to let your actions be influenced by your fears.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2618, 56112, '', 21, 'To me, there is no greater act of courage than being the one who kisses first.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2619, 71188, '', 21, 'Maybe you will be afraid and maybe you will fail, but the courage to take risks in any part of your life is, I feel, a very worthwhile way to live.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2620, 17203, '', 21, 'When I was straight, I had the courage and energy to become an actress. I owe my career to my will to stop using.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2621, 59569, '', 21, 'Courage to continue comes from deeper sources than outward results.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2622, 16218, '', 21, 'There are always a few who stand up in times of communal madness and have the courage to say that what unites us is greater than what divides us.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2623, 45766, '', 21, 'You must have love as the core it takes courage to be willing to constantly tell the truth to each other and risk letting the relationship go.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2624, 5988, '', 21, 'Courage is a peculiar kind of fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2625, 14495, '', 21, 'Courage is... the knowledge of how to fear what ought to be feared and how not to fear what ought not to be feared.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2626, 3633, '', 21, 'It takes both courage and talent to stand up in front of fellow human beings and make them crack a smile, and at the same time keep it clean.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2627, 913, '', 21, 'Keep courage. Whatever you do, do not feel sorry for yourself. You will win in a great age of opportunity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2628, 79840, '', 21, 'Leadership requires the courage to make decisions that will benefit the next generation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2629, 54640, '', 21, 'Part of courage is simple consistency.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2630, 44695, '', 21, 'Whether you be man or woman you will never do anything in this world without courage. It is the greatest quality of the mind next to honor.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2631, 56636, '', 21, 'We had no more courage than Harriet Tubman or Marcus Garvey had in their times. We just had a more vulnerable enemy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2632, 46104, '', 21, 'Pugnacity is a form of courage, but a very bad form.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2633, 33995, '', 21, 'The world will step aside for nearly anyone who has the courage of his of her opinions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2634, 9292, '', 21, 'If one suffers we all suffer. Togetherness is strength. Courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2635, 14023, '', 21, 'I saw courage both in the Vietnam War and in the struggle to stop it. I learned that patriotism includes protest, not just military service.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2636, 34012, '', 21, 'Peace is a fragile thing. It takes courage to secure it. It takes wisdom to maintain it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2637, 97859, '', 21, 'Grave was the man in years, in looks, in word, his locks were grey, yet was his courage green.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2638, 8038, '', 21, 'I\'ll know how to die with courage that is easier than living.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2639, 22153, '', 21, 'A leader must have the courage to act against an expert\'s advice.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2640, 7517, '', 21, 'It takes a great deal of courage to follow another person\'s lead.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:30'),
(2641, 41557, '', 21, 'The courage in journalism is sticking up for the unpopular, not the popular.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2642, 19146, '', 21, 'Have the courage of your desire.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2643, 4763, '', 21, 'I wish we lived in a society that made it safe and provided the courage for everyone to come out.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2644, 26043, '', 21, 'Now that I\'ve got some films under my belt, I have the courage of my convictions regarding acting. It gives me a leg to stand on.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2645, 95587, '', 21, 'Courage is very important. Like a muscle, it is strengthened by use.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2646, 2484, '', 21, 'Love is the most difficult and dangerous form of courage. Courage is the most desperate, admirable and noble kind of love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2647, 6405, '', 21, 'More firm and sure the hand of courage strikes, when it obeys the watchful eye of caution.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2648, 58935, '', 21, 'That\'s what acting is - it\'s about... having the courage to allow your audience into the private moments of your characters\' lives.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2649, 10401, '', 21, 'Presumption should never make us neglect that which appears easy to us, nor despair make us lose courage at the sight of difficulties.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2650, 57024, '', 21, 'No man in the world has more courage than the man who can stop after eating one peanut.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2651, 18381, '', 21, 'A man of courage flees forward, in the midst of new things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2652, 4858, '', 21, 'I think that people need to have the courage of their convictions and not be trying to fool people into thinking that they\'ve changed overnight.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2653, 99832, '', 21, 'It takes courage to know when you ought to be afraid.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2654, 6708, '', 21, 'Optimism is the foundation of courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2655, 45761, '', 21, 'Yes, you must have the courage of being free.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2656, 90549, '', 21, 'To see what is right and not to do it is want of courage, or of principle.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2657, 81148, '', 21, 'It is a wise man who knows where courage ends and stupidity begins.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2658, 5819, '', 21, 'I try to be a truthful artist and I try to show a level of courage. I enjoy that. I\'m a messenger.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2659, 14362, '', 21, 'Courage is the fear of being thought a coward.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2660, 3825, '', 21, 'Courage is action, not talk.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2661, 52198, '', 21, 'It would be sad if we lost our instinct and our courage to love and protect.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2662, 53208, '', 21, 'I think the moments that are difficult for anybody are when you see what your life could be, if only you had the courage to take the steps needed.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2663, 32049, '', 21, 'I know what real courage is, and I understand true compassion.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2664, 1531, '', 21, 'My talent is such that no undertaking, however vast in size... has ever surpassed my courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2665, 55322, '', 21, 'And as a child I was filled with passionate admiration for acts of civic courage I had seen performed by an elderly military doctor, who was a friend of my family.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2666, 35911, '', 21, 'It often takes more courage to change one\'s opinion than to keep it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2667, 27722, '', 21, 'Courage is always the surest wisdom.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2668, 36017, '', 21, 'One of the marks of a gift is to have the courage of it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2669, 73325, '', 21, 'But after this natural burst of indignation, no man of sense, courage, or prudence will waste his time or his strength in retrospective reproaches or repinings.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2670, 16821, '', 21, 'Freedom is a system based on courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:17', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2671, 42747, '', 32, 'I learned that courage was not the absence of fear, but the triumph over it. The brave man is not he who does not feel afraid, but he who conquers that fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2672, 94378, '', 32, 'Courage is what it takes to stand up and speak courage is also what it takes to sit down and listen.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2673, 97843, '', 32, 'There are no easy answers\' but there are simple answers. We must have the courage to do what we know is morally right.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2674, 45715, '', 32, 'Courage is grace under pressure.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2675, 44807, '', 32, 'We must build dikes of courage to hold back the flood of fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2676, 2164, '', 32, 'Courage is resistance to fear, mastery of fear, not absence of fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2677, 10318, '', 32, 'He who is not courageous enough to take risks will accomplish nothing in life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2678, 90776, '', 32, 'Courage is not simply one of the virtues, but the form of every virtue at the testing point.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2679, 13476, '', 32, 'Courage is being scared to death... and saddling up anyway.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2680, 48334, '', 32, 'You will never do anything in this world without courage. It is the greatest quality of the mind next to honor.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2681, 85144, '', 32, 'Efforts and courage are not enough without purpose and direction.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2682, 58433, '', 32, 'One man with courage is a majority.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2683, 83143, '', 32, 'Have the courage to say no. Have the courage to face the truth. Do the right thing because it is right. These are the magic keys to living your life with integrity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2684, 9806, '', 32, 'Faced with what is right, to leave it undone shows a lack of courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2685, 27830, '', 32, 'How few there are who have courage enough to own their faults, or resolution enough to mend them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2686, 32033, '', 32, 'Who could refrain that had a heart to love and in that heart courage to make love known?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2687, 22307, '', 32, 'Inaction breeds doubt and fear. Action breeds confidence and courage. If you want to conquer fear, do not sit home and think about it. Go out and get busy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2688, 59720, '', 32, 'A great part of courage is the courage of having done the thing before.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2689, 99974, '', 32, 'Have courage for the great sorrows of life and patience for the small ones and when you have laboriously accomplished your daily task, go to sleep in peace.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2690, 33590, '', 32, 'He is a man of courage who does not run away, but remains at his post and fights against the enemy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2691, 96922, '', 32, 'From caring comes courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2692, 79919, '', 32, 'Life shrinks or expands in proportion to one\'s courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2693, 80777, '', 32, 'The only service a friend can really render is to keep up your courage by holding up to you a mirror in which you can see a noble image of yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2694, 40877, '', 32, 'Failure is unimportant. It takes courage to make a fool of yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2695, 36995, '', 32, 'The most courageous act is still to think for yourself. Aloud.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2696, 76669, '', 32, 'Those who lack the courage will always find a philosophy to justify it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2697, 44178, '', 32, 'Success is never final, failure is never fatal. It\'s courage that counts.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2698, 3844, '', 32, 'Courage is contagious. When a brave man takes a stand, the spines of others are often stiffened.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2699, 94441, '', 32, 'Courage is a kind of salvation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2700, 25060, '', 32, 'Courage is fear holding on a minute longer.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2701, 1458, '', 32, 'Man cannot discover new oceans unless he has the courage to lose sight of the shore.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2702, 98441, '', 32, 'Creativity requires the courage to let go of certainties.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2703, 26744, '', 32, 'What would life be if we had no courage to attempt anything?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2704, 98860, '', 32, 'Courage is fire, and bullying is smoke.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2705, 62628, '', 32, 'It requires more courage to suffer than to die.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2706, 41307, '', 32, 'Courage is found in unlikely places.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2707, 34451, '', 32, 'Courage is the greatest of all virtues, because if you haven\'t courage, you may not have an opportunity to use any of the others.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2708, 52089, '', 32, 'To have courage for whatever comes in life - everything lies in that.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2709, 28076, '', 32, 'Any intelligent fool can make things bigger and more complex... It takes a touch of genius - and a lot of courage to move in the opposite direction.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2710, 99143, '', 32, 'The opposite for courage is not cowardice, it is conformity. Even a dead fish can go with the flow.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2711, 68010, '', 32, 'One man with courage makes a majority.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2712, 34876, '', 32, 'Real courage is when you know you\'re licked before you begin, but you begin anyway and see it through no matter what.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2713, 27060, '', 32, 'The secret to happiness is freedom... And the secret to freedom is courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2714, 5674, '', 32, 'A lot of people do not muster the courage to live their dreams because they are afraid to die.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2715, 84162, '', 32, 'We must have courage to bet on our ideas, to take the calculated risk, and to act. Everyday living requires courage if life is to be effective and bring happiness.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2716, 74043, '', 32, 'The courage to be is the courage to accept oneself, in spite of being unacceptable.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2717, 75403, '', 32, 'It is only necessary to have courage, for strength without self-confidence is useless.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2718, 5068, '', 32, 'We have a powerful potential in out youth, and we must have the courage to change old ideas and practices so that we may direct their power toward good ends.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2719, 47703, '', 32, 'Courage - a perfect sensibility of the measure of danger, and a mental willingness to endure it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2720, 87865, '', 32, 'If you are lucky enough to find a way of life you love, you have to find the courage to live it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2721, 98507, '', 32, 'Courage is not the absence of despair it is, rather, the capacity to move ahead in spite of despair.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2722, 19937, '', 32, 'Courage is being afraid but going on anyhow.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2723, 83492, '', 32, 'Clear thinking requires courage rather than intelligence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2724, 47847, '', 32, 'People with courage and character always seem sinister to the rest.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2725, 42620, '', 32, 'Do not lose courage in considering your own imperfections.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:31'),
(2726, 35825, '', 32, 'The best protection any woman can have... is courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2727, 68853, '', 32, 'The trials on the road to world harmony are no greater than the courage of those who accept the challenge.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2728, 52350, '', 32, 'Being deeply loved by someone gives you strength, while loving someone deeply gives you courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2729, 49816, '', 32, 'Success is not final, failure is not fatal: it is the courage to continue that counts.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2730, 68601, '', 32, 'We gain strength, and courage, and confidence by each experience in which we really stop to look fear in the face... we must do that which we think we cannot.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2731, 6271, '', 32, 'All our dreams can come true, if we have the courage to pursue them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2732, 3547, '', 32, 'Mistakes are always forgivable, if one has the courage to admit them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2733, 48088, '', 32, 'My great hope is to laugh as much as I cry to get my work done and try to love somebody and have the courage to accept the love in return.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2734, 40381, '', 32, 'You have to accept whatever comes and the only important thing is that you meet it with courage and with the best that you have to give.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2735, 25744, '', 32, 'Courage means to keep working a relationship, to continue seeking solutions to difficult problems, and to stay focused during stressful periods.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2736, 86935, '', 32, 'History, despite its wrenching pain, cannot be unlived, but if faced with courage, need not be lived again.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2737, 56443, '', 32, 'You don\'t develop courage by being happy in your relationships everyday. You develop it by surviving difficult times and challenging adversity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2738, 43879, '', 32, 'It is curious that physical courage should be so common in the world and moral courage so rare.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2739, 53216, '', 32, 'Wisdom, compassion, and courage are the three universally recognized moral qualities of men.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2740, 61313, '', 32, 'Courage is rightly esteemed the first of human qualities... because it is the quality which guarantees all others.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2741, 49976, '', 32, 'It takes courage to grow up and become who you really are.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2742, 45755, '', 32, 'The courage of life is often a less dramatic spectacle than the courage of a final moment but it is no less a magnificent mixture of triumph and tragedy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2743, 11999, '', 32, 'Courage is the first of human qualities because it is the quality which guarantees the others.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2744, 4037, '', 32, 'The greatest test of courage on earth is to bear defeat without losing heart.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2745, 78754, '', 32, 'Every man has his own courage, and is betrayed because he seeks in himself the courage of other persons.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2746, 97313, '', 32, 'The principles of living greatly include the capacity to face trouble with courage, disappointment with cheerfulness, and trial with humility.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2747, 90889, '', 32, 'Courage is a mean with regard to fear and confidence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2748, 10889, '', 32, 'I want to grow old without facelifts. I want to have the courage to be loyal to the face I have made.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2749, 50691, '', 32, 'A man of great common sense and good taste - meaning thereby a man without originality or moral courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2750, 9012, '', 32, 'It is only through labor and painful effort, by grim energy and resolute courage, that we move on to better things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2751, 75973, '', 32, 'I never thought much of the courage of a lion tamer. Inside the cage he is at least safe from people.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2752, 26996, '', 32, 'True courage is being afraid, and going ahead and doing your job anyhow, that\'s what courage is.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2753, 7186, '', 32, 'Courtesy is as much a mark of a gentleman as courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2754, 94495, '', 32, 'He\'s a man of great common sense and good taste - meaning thereby a man without originality or moral courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2755, 865, '', 32, 'Courage is like love it must have hope for nourishment.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2756, 70517, '', 32, 'Courage is knowing what not to fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2757, 30934, '', 32, 'Real nobility is based on scorn, courage, and profound indifference.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2758, 12199, '', 32, 'It takes a lot of courage to show your dreams to someone else.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2759, 65264, '', 32, 'Believers, look up - take courage. The angels are nearer than you think.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2760, 592, '', 32, 'All of us have moments in our lives that test our courage. Taking children into a house with a white carpet is one of them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2761, 56638, '', 32, 'Change will never happen when people lack the ability and courage to see themselves for who they are.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2762, 11019, '', 32, 'A mode of conduct, a standard of courage, discipline, fortitude and integrity can do a great deal to make a woman beautiful.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2763, 79702, '', 32, 'Give us grace and strength to forbear and to persevere. Give us courage and gaiety and the quiet mind, spare to us our friends, soften to us our enemies.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2764, 48085, '', 32, 'Keep your fears to yourself, but share your courage with others.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2765, 58121, '', 32, 'Most of us have far more courage than we ever dreamed we possessed.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2766, 90975, '', 32, 'Life is to be entered upon with courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2767, 52740, '', 32, 'I\'ve been through it all, baby, I\'m mother courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2768, 38331, '', 32, 'We need to find the courage to say no to the things and people that are not serving us if we want to rediscover ourselves and live our lives with authenticity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2769, 31507, '', 32, 'Untutored courage is useless in the face of educated bullets.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2770, 2723, '', 32, 'Courage is almost a contradiction in terms. It means a strong desire to live taking the form of readiness to die.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2771, 28845, '', 32, 'The first virtue in a soldier is endurance of fatigue courage is only the second virtue.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2772, 75872, '', 32, 'There can be no failure to a man who has not lost his courage, his character, his self respect, or his self-confidence. He is still a King.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2773, 34493, '', 32, 'Sometimes even to live is an act of courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2774, 1524, '', 32, 'Healing takes courage, and we all have courage, even if we have to dig a little to find it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2775, 91156, '', 32, 'If human beings had genuine courage, they\'d wear their costumes every day of the year, not just on Halloween.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2776, 91029, '', 32, 'There is nothing in the world so much admired as a man who knows how to bear unhappiness with courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2777, 80343, '', 32, 'Courage and grace are a formidable mixture. The only place to see it is in the bullring.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2778, 34281, '', 32, 'The courage we desire and prize is not the courage to die decently, but to live manfully.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2779, 67959, '', 32, 'The paradox of courage is that a man must be a little careless of his life even in order to keep it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2780, 68310, '', 32, 'Just as courage imperils life, fear protects it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2781, 59144, '', 32, 'There can be no great courage where there is no confidence or assurance, and half the battle is in the conviction that we can do what we undertake.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2782, 35439, '', 32, 'We need men with moral courage to speak and write their real thoughts, and to stand by their convictions, even to the very death.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2783, 89546, '', 32, 'The weak in courage is strong in cunning.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2784, 10887, '', 32, 'Freedom is the sure possession of those alone who have the courage to defend it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2785, 29856, '', 32, 'You will find as you grow older that courage is the rarest of all qualities to be found in public life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2786, 24820, '', 32, 'Every day begins with an act of courage and hope: getting out of bed.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2787, 73582, '', 32, 'A team is where a boy can prove his courage on his own. A gang is where a coward goes to hide.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2788, 52187, '', 32, 'It is a blessed thing that in every age some one has had the individuality enough and courage enough to stand by his own convictions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2789, 69227, '', 32, 'The opposite of courage in our society is not cowardice, it is conformity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2790, 62338, '', 32, 'Perfect courage is to do without witnesses what one would be capable of doing with the world looking on.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2791, 12399, '', 32, 'Courage can\'t see around corners but goes around them anyway.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2792, 25375, '', 32, 'The only courage that matters is the kind that gets you from one moment to the next.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2793, 5084, '', 32, 'Courage and perseverance have a magical talisman, before which difficulties disappear and obstacles vanish into air.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2794, 49176, '', 32, 'Courage without conscience is a wild beast.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2795, 71758, '', 32, 'Why should we honour those that die upon the field of battle? A man may show as reckless a courage in entering into the abyss of himself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2796, 61085, '', 32, 'To dare to live alone is the rarest courage since there are many who had rather meet their bitterest enemy in the field, than their own hearts in their closet.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2797, 24701, '', 32, 'Traits like humility, courage, and empathy are easily overlooked - but it\'s immensely important to find them in your closest relationships.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2798, 28667, '', 32, 'Valor is stability, not of legs and arms, but of courage and the soul.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2799, 98628, '', 32, 'It is courage, courage, courage, that raises the blood of life to crimson splendor. Live bravely and present a brave front to adversity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2800, 9434, '', 32, 'All you need is the plan, the road map, and the courage to press on to your destination.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2801, 21891, '', 32, 'Courage consists not in hazarding without fear but being resolutely minded in a just cause.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2802, 61012, '', 32, 'To create one\'s world in any of the arts takes courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2803, 88858, '', 32, 'The kind of beauty I want most is the hard-to-get kind that comes from within - strength, courage, dignity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2804, 74226, '', 32, 'Genius is talent set on fire by courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2805, 38155, '', 32, 'We\'ve begun to raise daughters more like sons... but few have the courage to raise our sons more like our daughters.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2806, 77692, '', 32, 'Despair gives courage to a coward.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2807, 80534, '', 32, 'He that fails in his endeavors after wealth or power will not long retain either honesty or courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2808, 81488, '', 32, 'Either life entails courage, or it ceases to be life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2809, 65009, '', 32, 'Courage stands halfway between cowardice and rashness, one of which is a lack, the other an excess of courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2810, 74427, '', 32, 'Everyone has talent. What is rare is the courage to follow the talent to the dark place where it leads.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2811, 32149, '', 32, 'To persevere, trusting in what hopes he has, is courage in a man.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2812, 51388, '', 32, 'Political courage is not political suicide.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2813, 19822, '', 32, 'Unless a reviewer has the courage to give you unqualified praise, I say ignore the bastard.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2814, 34908, '', 32, 'The strangest, most generous, and proudest of all virtues is true courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2815, 30956, '', 32, 'Courage, above all things, is the first quality of a warrior.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2816, 77137, '', 32, 'I beg you take courage the brave soul can mend even disaster.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2817, 54876, '', 32, 'The more wit the less courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2818, 53285, '', 32, 'One man scorned and covered with scars still strove with his last ounce of courage to reach the unreachable stars and the world will be better for this.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2819, 55063, '', 32, 'Take chances, make mistakes. That\'s how you grow. Pain nourishes your courage. You have to fail in order to practice being brave.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2820, 44659, '', 32, 'Determination, energy, and courage appear spontaneously when we care deeply about something. We take risks that are unimaginable in any other context.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2821, 98735, '', 32, 'Way down deep, we\'re all motivated by the same urges. Cats have the courage to live by them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2822, 79454, '', 32, 'Suffering! We owe to it all that is good in us, all that gives value to life we owe to it pity, we owe to it courage, we owe to it all the virtues.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:32'),
(2823, 13792, '', 32, 'Failure is only postponed success as long as courage \'coaches\' ambition. The habit of persistence is the habit of victory.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2824, 49386, '', 32, 'It takes as much courage to have tried and failed as it does to have tried and succeeded.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33');
INSERT INTO `quotes` (`id`, `order`, `entry_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `author`, `has_notif`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(2825, 32530, '', 32, 'Courage consists not in blindly overlooking danger, but in seeing it, and conquering it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2826, 48131, '', 32, 'Creativity takes courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2827, 11837, '', 32, 'Courage enlarges, cowardice diminishes resources. In desperate straits the fears of the timid aggravate the dangers that imperil the brave.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2828, 83068, '', 32, 'If we survive danger it steels our courage more than anything else.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2829, 39266, '', 32, 'There are pretenders to piety as well as to courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2830, 15657, '', 32, 'Religion in its humility restores man to his only dignity, the courage to live by grace.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2831, 16270, '', 32, 'Courage that grows from constitution often forsakes a man when he has occasion for it courage which arises from a sense of duty acts in a uniform manner.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2832, 7063, '', 32, 'We are very much what others think of us. The reception our observations meet with gives us courage to proceed, or damps our efforts.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2833, 98612, '', 32, 'It takes someone with a vision of the possibilities to attain new levels of experience. Someone with the courage to live his dreams.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2834, 27800, '', 32, 'The principal act of courage is to endure and withstand dangers doggedly rather than to attack them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2835, 19824, '', 32, 'Have the courage to act instead of react.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2836, 60153, '', 32, 'Time is neutral and does not change things. With courage and initiative, leaders change things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2837, 74083, '', 32, 'In strife who inquires whether stratagem or courage was used?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2838, 17639, '', 32, 'In fact, my courage and my bravery at a young age was the thing I was bullied for, a kind of \'Who do you think you are?\'', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2839, 86270, '', 32, 'There is in true beauty, as in courage, something which narrow souls cannot dare to admire.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2840, 67823, '', 32, 'Physical courage, which despises all danger, will make a man brave in one way and moral courage, which despises all opinion, will make a man brave in another.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2841, 59855, '', 32, 'I\'m sick of not having the courage to be an absolute nobody.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2842, 57395, '', 32, 'Courage conquers all things: it even gives strength to the body.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2843, 3103, '', 32, 'Courage is the price that life exacts for granting peace.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2844, 4761, '', 32, 'Courage, my friends \'tis not too late to build a better world.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2845, 38526, '', 32, 'Courage is doing what you are afraid to do. There can be no courage unless you are scared.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2846, 52560, '', 32, 'Courage is what preserves our liberty, safety, life, and our homes and parents, our country and children. Courage comprises all things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2847, 25206, '', 32, 'Courage is often lack of insight, whereas cowardice in many cases is based on good information.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2848, 72937, '', 32, 'Courage is simply the willingness to be afraid and act anyway.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2849, 28414, '', 32, 'Whether you be man or woman you will never do anything in this world without courage. It is the greatest quality of the mind next to honor.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2850, 41878, '', 32, 'Without courage, wisdom bears no fruit.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2851, 5618, '', 32, 'He who loses wealth loses much he who loses a friend loses more but he that loses his courage loses all.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2852, 7203, '', 32, 'True courage is not the brutal force of vulgar heroes, but the firm resolve of virtue and reason.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2853, 58466, '', 32, 'Physical bravery is an animal instinct moral bravery is much higher and truer courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2854, 59661, '', 32, 'Hope lies in dreams, in imagination, and in the courage of those who dare to make dreams into reality.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2855, 32401, '', 32, 'Success is that old ABC - ability, breaks, and courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2856, 61331, '', 32, 'Audacity augments courage hesitation, fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2857, 89442, '', 32, 'The courage of very ordinary people is all that stands between us and the dark.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2858, 48384, '', 32, 'To live we must conquer incessantly, we must have the courage to be happy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2859, 21166, '', 32, 'I have the courage of my convictions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2860, 45287, '', 32, 'In all realms of life it takes courage to stretch your limits, express your power, and fulfill your potential... it\'s no different in the financial realm.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2861, 90868, '', 32, 'A wise woman knows how to summon her courage and do what is right, rather than what is easy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2862, 19234, '', 32, 'Decision is a risk rooted in the courage of being free.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2863, 77013, '', 32, 'I think there\'s a difference between ditzy and dumb. Dumb is just not knowing. Ditzy is having the courage to ask!', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2864, 53283, '', 32, 'The test of courage comes when we are in the minority. The test of tolerance comes when we are in the majority.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2865, 80836, '', 32, 'I have no physical courage, I\'ve asked for a double.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2866, 45216, '', 32, 'Courage is the ladder on which all the other virtues mount.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2867, 7869, '', 32, 'Courage is the capacity to confront what can be imagined.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2868, 43492, '', 32, 'Patience, that blending of moral courage with physical timidity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2869, 62113, '', 32, 'The last thing a woman will consent to discover in a man whom she loves, or on whom she simply depends, is want of courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2870, 34143, '', 32, 'Courage in danger is half the battle.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2871, 93924, '', 32, 'Courage easily finds its own eloquence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2872, 84761, '', 32, 'Good courage in a bad affair is half of the evil overcome.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2873, 53801, '', 32, 'The courage of a soldier is found to be the cheapest and most common quality of human nature.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2874, 39979, '', 32, 'Courage is a special kind of knowledge: the knowledge of how to fear what ought to be feared and how not to fear what ought not to be feared.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2875, 69394, '', 32, 'My mother taught me that we all have the power to achieve our dreams. What I lacked was the courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2876, 11105, '', 32, 'Every man of courage is a man of his word.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2877, 31010, '', 32, 'A man of courage never needs weapons, but he may need bail.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2878, 94830, '', 32, 'But courage which goes against military expediency is stupidity, or, if it is insisted upon by a commander, irresponsibility.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2879, 56584, '', 32, 'Cowardice and courage are never without a measure of affectation. Nor is love. Feelings are never true. They play with their mirrors.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2880, 41004, '', 32, 'Let us go forth with fear and courage and rage to save the world.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2881, 10420, '', 32, 'Fashion should not be expected to serve in the stead of courage or character.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2882, 96845, '', 32, 'It takes a lot of courage to face up to things you can\'t do because we feed ourselves so much denial.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2883, 16643, '', 32, 'Never undertake anything for which you wouldn\'t have the courage to ask the blessings of heaven.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2884, 85036, '', 32, 'The courage to imagine the otherwise is our greatest resource, adding color and suspense to all our life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2885, 5847, '', 32, 'Discouragement is not the absence of adequacy but the absence of courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2886, 71467, '', 32, 'Conscience is the root of all true courage if a man would be brave let him obey his conscience.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2887, 13194, '', 32, 'I always disliked dogs, those protectors of cowards who lack the courage to fight an assailant themselves.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2888, 59592, '', 32, 'You cannot build character and courage by destroying men\'s initiative and independence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2889, 15903, '', 32, 'Courage is the art of being the only one who knows you\'re scared to death.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2890, 92344, '', 32, 'If you could get up the courage to begin, you have the courage to succeed.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2891, 94952, '', 32, 'Nothing gives us courage more readily than the desire to avoid looking like a damn fool.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2892, 32532, '', 32, 'What is more mortifying than to feel that you have missed the plum for want of courage to shake the tree?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2893, 28057, '', 32, 'Courage is always rewarded.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2894, 16851, '', 32, 'The enchanting charms of this sublime science reveal only to those who have the courage to go deeply into it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2895, 22379, '', 32, 'With enough courage, you can do without a reputation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2896, 64804, '', 32, 'I have reached the conclusion that those who have physical courage also have moral courage. Physical courage is a great test.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2897, 25058, '', 32, 'It takes a good deal of physical courage to ride a horse. This, however, I have. I get it at about forty cents a flask, and take it as required.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2898, 7976, '', 32, 'Success means having the courage, the determination, and the will to become the person you believe you were meant to be.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2899, 2178, '', 32, 'It is easy enough to praise men for the courage of their convictions. I wish I could teach the sad young of this mealy generation the courage of their confusions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2900, 42099, '', 32, 'You have to do what you need to do as an artist. You have to have that courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2901, 73269, '', 32, 'I don\'t understand why people say that I am full of courage. I feel terribly nervous.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2902, 20953, '', 32, 'A statesman wants courage and a statesman wants vision but believe me, after six months\' experience, he wants first, second, third and all the time - patience.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2903, 1202, '', 32, 'I went through a long period where I was afraid of doing things I wanted to do, and you get your courage back, which is what\'s important.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2904, 64920, '', 32, 'On sensitive issues, talk isn\'t cheap - it takes real courage to pry open topics nailed shut.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2905, 24999, '', 32, 'I have a lot of courage. I\'m a realist.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2906, 83600, '', 32, 'A military coup needs a sacrifice and courage that you can\'t find in an army without morale.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2907, 38125, '', 32, 'Courage is poorly housed that dwells in numbers the lion never counts the herd that are about him, nor weighs how many flocks he has to scatter.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2908, 83031, '', 32, 'Optimism is essential to achievement and it is also the foundation of courage and true progress.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2909, 13853, '', 32, 'We want deeper sincerity of motive, a greater courage in speech and earnestness in action.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2910, 78095, '', 32, 'I was a little doubtful about the propriety of going to the Mammoth Cave without a gentleman escort, but if two ladies travel alone they must have the courage of men.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2911, 70974, '', 32, 'You can\'t test courage cautiously.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2912, 11805, '', 32, 'Being gifted needs courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2913, 66974, '', 32, 'Some of the greatest survivors have been women. Look at the courage so many women have shown after surviving earthquakes in the rubble for days on end.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2914, 95220, '', 32, 'Limit to courage? There is no limit to courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:33'),
(2915, 40199, '', 32, 'There is hope in dreams, imagination, and in the courage of those who wish to make those dreams a reality.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2916, 7711, '', 32, 'Nothing gives a fearful man more courage than another\'s fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2917, 13282, '', 32, 'Your determination, selflessness and courage have brought the freedom struggle towards its fulfilment.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2918, 45412, '', 32, 'Real courage is knowing what faces you and knowing how to face it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2919, 12564, '', 32, 'True courage is like a kite a contrary wind raises it higher.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2920, 91016, '', 32, 'One has to have the courage of one\'s pessimism.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2921, 81985, '', 32, 'It takes a certain courage and a certain greatness to be truly base.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2922, 84273, '', 32, 'Until the day of his death, no man can be sure of his courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2923, 67710, '', 32, 'Falsehood is cowardice, the truth courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2924, 6144, '', 32, 'Have the courage to be ignorant of a great number of things, in order to avoid the calamity of being ignorant of everything.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2925, 80690, '', 32, 'Intellectuals try to keep going. But their situation is very difficult. Those who have had the courage to voice their opposition have often paid a very high price.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2926, 95345, '', 32, 'I\'ve always been inspired by artists who have shown musical and intellectual curiosity and the courage to take risks.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2927, 17224, '', 32, 'Courage! I have shown it for years think you I shall lose it at the moment when my sufferings are to end?', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2928, 27967, '', 32, 'Men was formed for society, and is neither capable of living alone, nor has the courage to do it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2929, 85895, '', 32, 'One of the things that makes Hamlet unique among Shakespeare\'s characters is his courage to face up to the darker elements of his personality.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2930, 67967, '', 32, 'Often the test of courage is not to die but to live.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2931, 91662, '', 32, 'I have always had the courage for the new things that life sometimes offers.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2932, 46572, '', 32, 'Physical courage is a great test.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2933, 63541, '', 32, 'In my old age, I have been thinking about this, and I have reached the conclusion that those who have physical courage also have moral courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2934, 85939, '', 32, 'Ingenuity, plus courage, plus work, equals miracles.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2935, 71420, '', 32, 'Love makes a subtle man out of a crude one, it gives eloquence to the mute, it gives courage the cowardly and makes the idle quick and sharp.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2936, 44582, '', 32, 'The courage of a soldier is heightened by his knowledge of his profession.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2937, 57612, '', 32, 'Such decisions will be far reaching and difficult. But you never lacked courage in the past. Your courage is now needed for the future.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2938, 91857, '', 32, 'Courage is never to let your actions be influenced by your fears.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2939, 78532, '', 32, 'To me, there is no greater act of courage than being the one who kisses first.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2940, 99532, '', 32, 'Maybe you will be afraid and maybe you will fail, but the courage to take risks in any part of your life is, I feel, a very worthwhile way to live.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2941, 54069, '', 32, 'When I was straight, I had the courage and energy to become an actress. I owe my career to my will to stop using.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2942, 9775, '', 32, 'Courage to continue comes from deeper sources than outward results.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2943, 47857, '', 32, 'There are always a few who stand up in times of communal madness and have the courage to say that what unites us is greater than what divides us.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2944, 89959, '', 32, 'You must have love as the core it takes courage to be willing to constantly tell the truth to each other and risk letting the relationship go.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2945, 53295, '', 32, 'Courage is a peculiar kind of fear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2946, 79076, '', 32, 'Courage is... the knowledge of how to fear what ought to be feared and how not to fear what ought not to be feared.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2947, 32343, '', 32, 'It takes both courage and talent to stand up in front of fellow human beings and make them crack a smile, and at the same time keep it clean.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2948, 55999, '', 32, 'Keep courage. Whatever you do, do not feel sorry for yourself. You will win in a great age of opportunity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2949, 22266, '', 32, 'Leadership requires the courage to make decisions that will benefit the next generation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2950, 32731, '', 32, 'Part of courage is simple consistency.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2951, 54550, '', 32, 'Whether you be man or woman you will never do anything in this world without courage. It is the greatest quality of the mind next to honor.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2952, 5729, '', 32, 'We had no more courage than Harriet Tubman or Marcus Garvey had in their times. We just had a more vulnerable enemy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2953, 52840, '', 32, 'Pugnacity is a form of courage, but a very bad form.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2954, 63784, '', 32, 'The world will step aside for nearly anyone who has the courage of his of her opinions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2955, 65674, '', 32, 'If one suffers we all suffer. Togetherness is strength. Courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2956, 47816, '', 32, 'I saw courage both in the Vietnam War and in the struggle to stop it. I learned that patriotism includes protest, not just military service.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2957, 81788, '', 32, 'Peace is a fragile thing. It takes courage to secure it. It takes wisdom to maintain it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2958, 73998, '', 32, 'Grave was the man in years, in looks, in word, his locks were grey, yet was his courage green.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2959, 9524, '', 32, 'I\'ll know how to die with courage that is easier than living.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2960, 66587, '', 32, 'A leader must have the courage to act against an expert\'s advice.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2961, 19783, '', 32, 'It takes a great deal of courage to follow another person\'s lead.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2962, 54751, '', 32, 'The courage in journalism is sticking up for the unpopular, not the popular.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2963, 11810, '', 32, 'Have the courage of your desire.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2964, 59682, '', 32, 'I wish we lived in a society that made it safe and provided the courage for everyone to come out.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2965, 41280, '', 32, 'Now that I\'ve got some films under my belt, I have the courage of my convictions regarding acting. It gives me a leg to stand on.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2966, 36775, '', 32, 'Courage is very important. Like a muscle, it is strengthened by use.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2967, 22719, '', 32, 'Love is the most difficult and dangerous form of courage. Courage is the most desperate, admirable and noble kind of love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2968, 73701, '', 32, 'More firm and sure the hand of courage strikes, when it obeys the watchful eye of caution.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2969, 83862, '', 32, 'That\'s what acting is - it\'s about... having the courage to allow your audience into the private moments of your characters\' lives.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2970, 40275, '', 32, 'Presumption should never make us neglect that which appears easy to us, nor despair make us lose courage at the sight of difficulties.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2971, 69567, '', 32, 'No man in the world has more courage than the man who can stop after eating one peanut.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2972, 49920, '', 32, 'A man of courage flees forward, in the midst of new things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2973, 70748, '', 32, 'I think that people need to have the courage of their convictions and not be trying to fool people into thinking that they\'ve changed overnight.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2974, 48604, '', 32, 'It takes courage to know when you ought to be afraid.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2975, 97012, '', 32, 'Optimism is the foundation of courage.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2976, 13383, '', 32, 'Yes, you must have the courage of being free.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2977, 45745, '', 32, 'To see what is right and not to do it is want of courage, or of principle.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2978, 61546, '', 32, 'It is a wise man who knows where courage ends and stupidity begins.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2979, 33532, '', 32, 'I try to be a truthful artist and I try to show a level of courage. I enjoy that. I\'m a messenger.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
(2980, 15406, '', 32, 'Courage is the fear of being thought a coward.', '', 0, 2, '2022-11-25 10:16:46', '2023-01-27 00:30:34'),
