(3294, 8960, '', 15, 'Love takes off masks that we fear we cannot live without and know we cannot live within. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3295, 57172, '', 15, 'A life without love is like a sunless garden where all flowers are dead so it is necessary to keep love in your heart. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3296, 86343, '', 15, 'Deeply loving someone gives you courage but you will get stronger when being deeply loved by someone. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
