(3316, 7545, '', 15, 'Love’s greatest gift is its ability to make everything it touches sacred. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3317, 10432, '', 15, 'Love is the expansion of two natures in such fashion that each include the other, each is enriched by the other. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3318, 13950, '', 15, 'Heart only sees what it wants to see which is invisible to the eye. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3319, 11717, '', 15, 'Love is a game where two opposite plays and both will win. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3320, 18554, '', 15, 'Love cures people – both the ones who give it and the ones who receive it. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3321, 39218, '', 15, 'Let the beauty of what you love be what you do. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
