(3362, 87668, '', 15, 'Everytime you smile at someone, it is an action of love, a gift to that person, a beautiful thing.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3363, 35189, '', 15, 'Good works are links that form a chain of love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3364, 84980, '', 15, 'If we want a love message to be heard, it has got to be sent out. To keep a lamp burning, we have to keep putting oil in it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3365, 38792, '', 15, 'Intense love does not measure, it just gives.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3366, 93981, '', 15, 'Let us always meet each other with smile, for the smile is the beginning of love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3367, 85720, '', 15, 'Love begins at home, and it is not how much we do... but how much love we put in that action.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3368, 40040, '', 15, 'Love begins by taking care of the closest ones - the ones at home.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3369, 85300, '', 15, 'Love is a fruit in season at all times, and within reach of every hand.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3370, 36272, '', 15, 'Spread love everywhere you go. Let no one ever come to you without leaving happier.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3371, 98241, '', 15, 'The hunger for love is much more difficult to remove than the hunger for bread.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3372, 50312, '', 15, 'How bold one gets when one is sure of being loved!', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3373, 18098, '', 15, 'Love is a canvas furnished by Nature and embroidered by imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3374, 74891, '', 15, 'Love isn\'t something you find. Love is something that finds you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3375, 45404, '', 15, 'Sometimes the heart sees what is invisible to the eye.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3376, 6673, '', 15, 'Love is when the other person\'s happiness is more important than your own.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3377, 48758, '', 15, 'The sweetest of all sounds is that of the voice of the woman we love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3378, 6036, '', 15, 'Love doesn\'t make the world go \'round. Love is what makes the ride worthwhile.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3379, 37434, '', 15, 'Where there is love there is life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3380, 38315, '', 15, 'Love is composed of a single soul inhabiting two bodies.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3381, 56186, '', 15, 'It is not a lack of love, but a lack of friendship that makes unhappy marriages.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3382, 64404, '', 15, 'When someone loves you, the way they talk about you is different. You feel safe and comfortable.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3383, 48928, '', 15, 'Choose a job you love and you will never have to work a day in your life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3384, 99260, '', 15, 'We\'re born alone, we live alone, we die alone. Only through our love and friendship can we create the illusion for the moment that we\'re not alone.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3385, 69253, '', 15, 'Blessed is the influence of one true, loving human soul on another.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3386, 72109, '', 15, 'Love has no age, no limit; and no death.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3387, 43006, '', 15, 'Love is something sent from heaven to worry the hell out of you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3388, 31573, '', 15, 'Kindness in words creates confidence. Kindness in thinking creates profoundness. Kindness in giving creates love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3389, 15944, '', 15, 'Love has no errors, for all errors are the want for love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3390, 40472, '', 15, 'True love is eternal, infinite, and always like itself. It is equal and pure, without violent demonstrations: it is seen with white hairs and is always young in the heart. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3391, 73591, '', 15, 'Man must evolve for all human conflict, a method which rejects revenge, aggression and retaliation. The foundation of such a method is love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3392, 17383, '', 15, 'Love is a mutual self giving which ends in self recovery.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3393, 19536, '', 15, 'We waste time looking for the perfect lover, instead of creating the perfect love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3394, 3198, '', 15, 'A loving heart is the beginning of all knowledge.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3395, 56438, '', 15, 'Love is needing someone. Love is putting up with someone\'s bad qualities because they somehow complete you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:38'),
(3396, 27168, '', 15, 'You can love someone so much...But you can never love people as much as you can miss them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3397, 98645, '', 15, 'Nobody has ever measured, not even poets, how much the heart can hold.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3398, 12673, '', 15, 'You don\'t love someone for their looks, or their clothes, or for their fancy car, but because they sing a song only you can hear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3399, 41512, '', 15, 'One love, one heart, one destiny.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3400, 37218, '', 15, 'Love is so short, forgetting is so long.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3401, 90451, '', 15, 'Love is a sacred reserve of energy; it is like the blood of spiritual evolution.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3402, 41286, '', 15, 'We can\'t command our love, but we can our actions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3403, 25370, '', 15, 'Though lovers be lost love shall not.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3404, 52875, '', 15, 'People think love is an emotion. Love is good sense.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3405, 82471, '', 15, 'Love is the triumph of imagination over intelligence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3406, 90519, '', 15, 'Love consists in this, that two solitudes protect and touch and greet each other.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3407, 37298, '', 15, 'To love oneself is the beginning of a lifelong romance.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3408, 95361, '', 15, 'Love can make even nice people do awful things.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3409, 24155, '', 15, 'Love: it will kill you and save you, both.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3410, 52383, '', 15, 'Trust your heart if the seas catch fire, live by love though the stars walk backward.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3411, 54274, '', 15, 'Love has nothing to do with what you are expecting to get only with what you are expecting to give which is everything.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3412, 31821, '', 15, 'There is only one good thing in life, and that is love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3413, 41457, '', 15, 'In our life there is a single colour, as on an artist\'s palette, which provides the meaning of life and art. It is the color of love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3414, 56185, '', 15, 'If your heart is a volcano, how shall you expect flowers to bloom.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3415, 63183, '', 15, 'Hatred does not cease by hatred, but only by love; this is the eternal rule.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3416, 41103, '', 15, 'Love is life. And if you miss love, you miss life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3417, 14484, '', 15, 'Only divine love bestows the keys of knowledge.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3418, 60191, '', 15, 'Faith makes all things possible...love makes all things easy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3419, 71890, '', 15, 'Love is the only sane and satisfactory answer to the problem of human existence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3420, 86846, '', 15, 'There is always something left to love. And if you ain\'t learned that, you ain\'t learned nothing.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3421, 8505, '', 15, 'The richest love is that which submits to the arbitration of time.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3422, 94597, '', 15, 'You can give without loving, but you can never love without giving.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3423, 31851, '', 15, 'Being in love is the only transcendent experience.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3424, 74135, '', 15, 'The only thing we can never get enough of is love. And the one thing we never give enough is love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3425, 39766, '', 15, 'Love possesses not nor will it be possessed, for love is sufficient unto love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39');
INSERT INTO `quotes` (`id`, `order`, `entry_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `author`, `has_notif`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(3426, 50227, '', 15, 'A pair of powerful spectacles has sometimes sufficed to cure a person in love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3427, 80657, '', 15, 'Loving others always costs us something and requires effort. And you have to decide to do it on purpose. You can\'t wait for a feeling to motivate you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3428, 7711, '', 15, 'True love is quiescent, except in the nascent moments of true humility.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3429, 53465, '', 15, 'To fear love is to fear life, and those who fear life are already three parts dead.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3430, 90278, '', 15, 'True love is usually the most inconvenient kind.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3431, 7368, '', 15, 'When you love someone, you love the person as they are, and not as you\'d like them to be.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3432, 97188, '', 15, 'Love is the strongest force the world possesses and yet it is the humblest imaginable.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3433, 3650, '', 15, 'Falling in love consists merely in uncorking the imagination and bottling the common sense.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3434, 57155, '', 15, 'The greatest thing you\'ll ever learn is just to love and be loved in return.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3435, 91103, '', 15, 'If we are bold, love strikes away the chains of fear from our souls.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3436, 4617, '', 15, 'In dreams and in love there are no impossibilities.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3437, 72303, '', 15, 'Happiest is he who expects no happiness from others. Love delights and glorifies in giving, not receiving. So learn to love and give, and not to expect anything from others.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3438, 53808, '', 15, 'Where there is the greatest love, there are miracles.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3439, 4662, '', 15, 'The day that man allows true love to appear, those things which are well made will fall into confusion and will overturn everything we believe to be right and true.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3440, 27611, '', 15, 'If you love a flower, don\'t pick it up. Because if you pick it up, it dies and it ceases to be what you love. So if you love a flower, let it be. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3441, 43500, '', 15, 'Love is not about possession. Love is about appreciation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3442, 39788, '', 15, 'First best is falling in love. Second best is being in love. Least best is falling out of love. But any of it is better than never having been in love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3443, 88231, '', 15, 'Love is the whole and more than all.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3444, 59816, '', 15, 'Love is the voice under all silences, the hope which has no opposite in fear; the strength so strong mere force is feebleness: the truth more first than sun, more last than star.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3445, 20329, '', 15, 'To love is to burn, to be on fire.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3446, 34749, '', 15, 'Keep love in your heart. A life without it is like a sunless garden when the flowers are dead.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3447, 30669, '', 15, 'One is very crazy when in love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3448, 7706, '', 15, 'There is all kinds of love in this world but never the same love twice.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3449, 57483, '', 15, 'A most mediocre person can be the object of a love which is wild, extravagant, and beautiful as the poison lillies of the swamp.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3450, 62735, '', 15, 'And we are put on this earth a little space that we might learn to bear the beams of love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3451, 53537, '', 15, 'You know you are in love when the two of you can go grocery shopping together.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3452, 36731, '', 15, 'The value and quality of any love is determined solely by the lover himself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3453, 21519, '', 15, 'A woman knows the face of the man she loves as a sailor knows the open sea.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3454, 26964, '', 15, 'Have enough courage to trust love one more time and always one more time.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3455, 20333, '', 15, 'Love is that condition in the human spirit so profound that it allows people to survive, and better than that, to thrive with passion, compassion and style.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3456, 78619, '', 15, 'If nothing saves us from death, at least love should save us from life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3457, 40030, '', 15, 'Yet it is only love which sets us free.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3458, 22592, '', 15, 'Love is the only thing that we can carry with us when we go, and it makes the end so easy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3459, 86393, '', 15, 'It is love that asks, that seeks, that knocks, that finds, and that is faithful to what it finds.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3460, 19319, '', 15, 'Beauty grows in you to the extent that love grows, because charity itself is the soul\'s beauty.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3461, 25252, '', 15, 'There is only one thing infamous in love, and that is a falsehood.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3462, 24763, '', 15, 'Duty makes us do things well, but love makes us do them beautifully.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3463, 99801, '', 15, 'Whoever lives true life, will love true love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3464, 96377, '', 15, 'Love is the greatest advantage a parent can give.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3465, 47738, '', 15, 'The falling out of lovers is the renewing of love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3466, 43900, '', 15, 'You are at the beginning of your life, perhaps you will have many loves, but if you are fortunate, you will have only one love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3467, 8252, '', 15, 'If everything is imperfect in this imperfect world, love is most perfect in its perfect imperfection.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3468, 14309, '', 15, 'Love is the substance of all life. Everything is connected in love, absolutely everything.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3469, 13244, '', 15, 'For love is ever the beginning of knowledge, as fire is of light.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3470, 46511, '', 15, 'Love the world. Otherwise, you will be forced to carry the heaviest load: your own bitter self.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3471, 66798, '', 15, 'If you really want to love humanity, then you have to love humanity as it is now.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3472, 26993, '', 15, 'Man is by nature a lover. Only he has yet to discover the real thing to love. This quest awakens him to the fulfillment of his real self.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3473, 35157, '', 15, 'Love is something that never cared to learn how to judge anybody.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3474, 44933, '', 15, 'Instead of creating a reason why you cannot love the world, try to create a reason why you should and must love the world.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3475, 67448, '', 15, 'World-peace can be achieved when the power of love replaces the love of power.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3476, 63811, '', 15, 'Do not judge but love and be loved, if you want to be really happy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3477, 27271, '', 15, 'The wise are wise only because they love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3478, 82370, '', 15, 'One is loved because one is loved. No reason is needed for loving.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3479, 69601, '', 15, 'Love is the force that transforms and improves the Soul of the World.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3480, 11118, '', 15, 'We must never forget that spiritual experience is above all a practical experience of love. And with love, there are no rules.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3481, 96400, '', 15, 'Lovers need to know how to lose themselves and then how to find themselves again.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3482, 12116, '', 15, 'The moment we begin to see love, love begins to see us. And to save us.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3483, 90855, '', 15, 'Even if loving meant leaving, or solitude, or sorrow, love was worth every penny of its price.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3484, 17142, '', 15, 'Anyone who is in love is making love the whole time, even when they\'re not.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3485, 24858, '', 15, 'Love is the only thing that will save us, independent of any mistakes we may make. Love is always stronger.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3486, 10070, '', 15, 'Love always triumphs over what we call death. That\'s why there\'s no need to grieve for our loved ones because they continue to be loved and remain by our side.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3487, 18633, '', 15, 'Be loving, and you will never want for love; be humble, and you will never want for guiding.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3488, 89377, '', 15, 'A universal love is not only psychologically possible; it is the only complete and final way in which we are able to love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:39'),
(3489, 88828, '', 15, 'The salvation of man is through love and in love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:40'),
(3490, 38888, '', 15, 'Love is the ultimate and the highest goal to which man can aspire.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:40'),
(3491, 42947, '', 15, 'Lovers who love truly do not write down their happiness.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:40'),
