(3627, 63893, '', 15, 'Do not seek the because - in love there is no because, no reason, no explanation, no solutions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3628, 83013, '', 15, 'Any man who can drive safely while kissing a pretty girl is simply not giving the kiss the attention it deserves.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3629, 42383, '', 15, 'A woman should soften but not weaken a man.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3630, 13375, '', 15, 'Blessed are the hearts that can bend; they shall never be broken.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3631, 89856, '', 15, 'The story of life is quicker than the blink of an eye, the story of love is hello, goodbye.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3632, 36905, '', 15, 'Love does not alter the beloved, it alters itself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3633, 49539, '', 15, 'Love is an untamed force. When we try to control it, it destroys us. When we try to imprison it, it enslaves us. When we try to understand it, it leaves us feeling lost and confused.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3634, 5416, '', 15, 'Love is a promise, love is a souvenir, once given never forgotten, never let it disappear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3635, 72857, '', 15, 'We are not held back by the love we didn\'t receive in the past, but by the love we\'re not extending in the present.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3636, 58644, '', 15, 'Love is all, it gives all, and it takes all.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3637, 38477, '', 15, 'In the absence of love, we began slowly but surely to fall apart.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3638, 72382, '', 15, 'When the power of love, will overcome the love of power; the world will know peace.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3639, 15986, '', 15, 'Genuine love is volitional rather than emotional.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3640, 90013, '', 15, 'Real love is a permanently self-enlarging experience.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3641, 83743, '', 15, 'All happiness or unhappiness solely depends upon the quality of the object to which we are attached by love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3642, 61467, '', 15, 'What can you do to promote world peace? Go home and love your family. - Mother Teresa', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3643, 97127, '', 15, 'Kind words can be short and easy to speak, but their echoes are truly endless.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:41'),
(3644, 15509, '', 15, 'The extent of your consciousness is limited only by your ability to love and to embrace with your love the space around you, and all it contains.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3645, 87590, '', 15, 'You must remember to love people and use things, rather than to love things and use people.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3646, 38083, '', 15, 'Real magic in relationships means an absence of judgement of others.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3647, 30120, '', 15, 'Lovers don\'t finally meet somewhere. They\'re in each other all along.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3648, 85864, '', 15, 'Whenever you are confronted with an opponent. Conquer him with love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3649, 85320, '', 15, 'If you truly loved yourself, you could never hurt another.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3650, 45939, '', 15, 'Only one who loves can remember so well.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3651, 43064, '', 15, 'Life’s a game made for everyone and love is the prize.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3652, 77173, '', 15, 'Two things you will never have to chase: True friends & true love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:08:45', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3653, 54234, '', 16, 'Friends are the family you choose.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3654, 79491, '', 16, 'Life is partly what we make it, and partly what it is made by the friends we choose.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
