(3714, 33225, '', 16, 'True friendship comes when the silence between two people is comfortable.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3715, 41602, '', 16, 'Real friends care like a mom, scold like a dad, tease like a sister, irritate like a brother, and love more than a lover.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3716, 41445, '', 16, 'A true friend is one who overlooks your failures and tolerates your success!', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3717, 4270, '', 16, 'A sweet friendship refreshes the soul.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3718, 30399, '', 16, 'Try to be a rainbow in someone’s cloud.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3719, 7739, '', 16, 'It’s not that diamonds are a girl’s best friend, but it’s your best friends who are your diamonds.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3720, 63303, '', 16, 'In the cookie of life, friends are the chocolate chips.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3721, 42201, '', 16, 'There are friends, there is family, and then there are friends that become family.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
(3722, 18835, '', 16, 'Good friends are like stars. You don’t always see them, but you know they’re always there.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:42'),
