(3756, 75598, '', 16, 'A true friend is someone who thinks that you are a good egg even though he knows that you are slightly cracked.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3757, 42031, '', 16, 'Friends buy you food. Best friends eat your food. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3758, 45085, '', 16, 'Never let your best friends get lonely…keep disturbing them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3759, 10243, '', 16, 'True friends aren’t the ones who make your problems disappear. They are the ones who won’t disappear when you’re facing problems. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3760, 73050, '', 16, 'A friend can tell you things you don’t want to tell yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3761, 15980, '', 16, 'Everyone hears what you say. Friends listen to what you say. Best friends listen to what you don’t say. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3762, 29632, '', 16, 'A strong friendship doesn’t need daily conversation or being together. As long as the relationship lives in the heart, true friends never part. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3763, 27595, '', 16, 'Friendship is always a sweet responsibility, never an opportunity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3764, 15830, '', 16, 'False friendship, like the ivy, decays and ruins the walls it embraces; but true friendship gives new life and animation to the object it supports.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3765, 36670, '', 16, 'Everyone has a friend during each stage of life. But only lucky ones have the same friend in all stages of life. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3766, 15009, '', 16, 'Ultimately the bond of all companionship, whether in marriage or in friendship, is conversation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3767, 39411, '', 16, 'The love that comes from friendship is the underlying facet of a happy life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3768, 62317, '', 16, 'Friendship is accepting a person with all their qualities — good and bad.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3769, 60472, '', 16, 'Each new friendship can make you a new person, because it opens up new doors inside of you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3770, 85785, '', 16, 'Since there is nothing so well worth having as friends, never lose a chance to make them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3771, 45943, '', 16, 'Every new friend is a new adventure… the start of more memories.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3772, 93523, '', 16, 'The kindest way of helping yourself is to find a friend.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3773, 6628, '', 16, 'Getting to know new people and gaining new friends is one of life’s greatest pleasures. So conquer your fears and get out there.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3774, 96154, '', 16, 'There are friendships imprinted in our hearts that will never be diminished by time and distance.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3775, 42823, '', 16, 'No distance of place or lapse of time can lessen the friendship of those who are thoroughly persuaded of each other’s worth.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3776, 69391, '', 16, 'A real friendship should not fade as time passes, and should not weaken because of space separation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3777, 63001, '', 16, 'A friend who is far away is sometimes much nearer than one who is at hand.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3778, 94631, '', 16, 'It’s an insane world, but in it there’s one sanity, the loyalty of old friends.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3779, 28184, '', 16, 'Only a true friend would be that truly honest.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3780, 86730, '', 16, 'Good friends will help you until you’re unstuck.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3781, 57461, '', 16, 'Make friends and have fun. You\'ll be making memories without realising it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3782, 74479, '', 16, 'A day without a friend is like a pot without a single drop of honey left inside.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3783, 36301, '', 16, 'There are three things that grow more precious with age; old wood to burn, old books to read, and old friends to enjoy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3784, 98868, '', 16, 'The language of friendship is not words but meanings.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3785, 19140, '', 16, 'Be slow to fall into friendship; but when thou art in, continue firm & constant.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3786, 81456, '', 16, 'Anybody can sympathize with the sufferings of a friend, but it requires a very fine nature to sympathize with a friend\'s success.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3787, 30926, '', 16, 'Wishing to be friends is quick work, but friendship is a slow ripening fruit.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3788, 1974, '', 16, 'A good friend can tell when something is wrong with you. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3789, 74698, '', 16, 'Friendship is unnecessary, like philosophy, like art.... It has no survival value; rather it is one of those things which give value to survival.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3790, 23293, '', 16, 'Tis the privilege of friendship to talk nonsense, and to have her nonsense respected.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3791, 54202, '', 16, 'In prosperity our friends know us; in adversity we know our friends.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3792, 97294, '', 16, 'Friendship improves happiness, and abates misery, by doubling our joys, and dividing our grief.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3793, 90324, '', 16, 'A friend is the oxygen that breathes life back into the deflated parts of ourselves so that we may rise again.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3794, 30365, '', 16, 'One friend with whom you have a lot in common is better than three with whom you struggle to find things to talk about', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3795, 56449, '', 16, 'Only a true best friend can protect you from your immortal enemies', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3796, 1677, '', 16, 'A friend may be waiting behind a stranger’s face.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3797, 40738, '', 16, 'Friendship is everything. Friendship is more than talent. It is more than the government. It is almost the equal of family.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3798, 37447, '', 16, 'A real friend isn’t capable of feeling sorry for you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3799, 60005, '', 16, 'To throw away an honest friend is, as it were, to throw your life away.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3800, 56264, '', 16, 'Friendship isn\'t about who you\'ve known the longest, it\'s about who came and never left your side.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3801, 72661, '', 16, 'The language of friendship is not words, but meanings. It is an intelligence above language', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3802, 48739, '', 16, 'Celebrate the people in your life who are there because they love you for no other reason than because you are you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3803, 7244, '', 16, 'Many people will walk in and out of your life, but only true friends will leave footprints in your heart.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3804, 96816, '', 16, 'Accountability in friendship is the equivalent of love without strategy', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3805, 33961, '', 16, 'A man\'s friendships are one of the best measures of his worth.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3806, 96008, '', 16, 'If you have one true friend you have more than your share.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3807, 68099, '', 16, 'Friendship is another word for love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3808, 63041, '', 16, 'A quarrel between friends, when made up, adds a new tie to friendship.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3809, 30637, '', 16, 'Of all possessions a friend is the most precious.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3810, 50481, '', 16, 'There\'s nothing like a really loyal, dependable, good friend. Nothing.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3811, 79856, '', 16, 'Awards become corroded. Friends gather no dust.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3812, 67978, '', 16, 'True friends are always together in spirit.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3813, 83997, '', 16, 'Friends are those rare people who ask how we are and then wait to hear the answer.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3814, 33366, '', 16, 'Silences make the real conversations between friends. Not the saying but the never needing to say is what counts.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3815, 12154, '', 16, 'Rejoicing in our joy, not suffering over our suffering, makes someone a friend.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3816, 42365, '', 16, 'Friends and good manners will carry you where money won\'t go.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3817, 30412, '', 16, 'It is one of the blessings of old friends that you can afford to be stupid with them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3818, 82600, '', 16, 'Friendship multiplies the good of life and divides the evil.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3819, 92161, '', 16, 'The greatest healing therapy is friendship and love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3820, 59250, '', 16, 'True friendship ought never to conceal what it thinks.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3821, 6757, '', 16, 'Friendship is certainly the finest balm for the pangs of disappointed love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3822, 46866, '', 16, 'One’s friends are that part of the human race with which one can be human.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3823, 864, '', 16, 'Friends are the siblings God never gave us.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3824, 39132, '', 16, 'A good friend knows all your best stories, but a best friend has lived them with you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3825, 73150, '', 16, 'Some people arrive and make such a beautiful impact on your life, you can barely remember what life was like without them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3826, 78014, '', 16, 'Your friends will know you better in the first minute you meet than your acquaintances will know you in a thousand years.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3827, 74691, '', 16, 'Friendship is the source of the greatest pleasures, and without friends even the most agreeable pursuits become tedious.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3828, 70284, '', 16, 'Friendship is a wildly underrated medication.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3829, 23761, '', 16, 'Real friendship, like real poetry, is extremely rare — and precious as a pearl.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3830, 12720, '', 16, 'Distance means so little, when someone means so much.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3831, 78115, '', 16, 'To like and dislike the same things, that is what makes a solid friendship', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3832, 43431, '', 16, 'Friendship is being there when someone’s feeling low and not being afraid to kick them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3833, 52308, '', 16, 'Best friend isn’t a person; it’s a tier.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:43'),
(3834, 23669, '', 16, 'Make new friends, but keep the old; Those are silver, these are gold.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3835, 86008, '', 16, 'Friendships that have stood the test of time and change are surely best.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3836, 14620, '', 16, 'Remember that the most valuable antiques are dear old friends.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3837, 84064, '', 16, 'A loyal friend laughs at your jokes when they’re not so good, and sympathizes with your problems when they’re not so bad.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3838, 80610, '', 16, 'A true friend never gets in your way unless you happen to be going down.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3839, 70762, '', 16, 'Friendship’s the wine of life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3840, 60766, '', 16, 'What draws people to be friends is that they see the same truth. They share it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3841, 39809, '', 16, 'A friend is someone who makes it easy to believe in yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3842, 41770, '', 16, 'True friendship is when two friends can walk in opposite directions, yet remain side by side.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3843, 49151, '', 16, 'The only way to have a friend is to be one.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3844, 45605, '', 16, 'Two things you will never have to chase: True friends & true love.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3845, 31639, '', 16, 'There are no strangers here, Only friends you haven’t yet met.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3846, 29029, '', 16, 'Friends show their love in times of trouble, not in happiness.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3847, 28254, '', 16, 'Depth of friendship does not depend on length of acquaintance.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3848, 85823, '', 16, 'True friendship is like sound health; the value of it is seldom known until it be lost.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3849, 59432, '', 16, 'When you choose your friends, don’t be short-changed by choosing personality over character.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3850, 2825, '', 16, 'Friendship improves happiness, and abates misery, by doubling our joys, and dividing our grief', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3851, 16914, '', 16, 'A friend is someone with whom you dare to be yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3852, 82720, '', 16, 'Tis a great confidence in a friend to tell him your faults; greater to tell him his.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3853, 24066, '', 16, 'By chance we met, by choice we become friend', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3854, 96068, '', 16, 'Friends should be like books, few, but hand-selected.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3855, 43456, '', 16, 'Without friends, no one would want to live, even if he had all other goods.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3856, 79127, '', 16, 'Be slow in choosing a friend, slower in changing.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3857, 71501, '', 16, 'Friendships take minutes to make, moments to break, years to repair.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3858, 62400, '', 16, 'Two persons cannot be friends for long if they cannot forgive each other’s little failings.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3859, 62024, '', 16, 'Of all the means to insure happiness throughout the whole life, by far the most important is the acquisition of friends.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3860, 73903, '', 16, 'Stay is a charming word in a friend’s vocabulary.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3861, 79047, '', 16, 'The pain of parting is nothing to the joy of meeting again.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3862, 30372, '', 16, 'A friend is one who has the same enemies as you have.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3863, 99559, '', 16, 'Friendship is a single soul dwelling in two bodies.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3864, 86631, '', 16, 'No road is long with good company.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3865, 36583, '', 16, 'Shared joy is a double joy; shared sorrow is half a sorrow.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3866, 25437, '', 16, 'The friend who hold your hand and says the wrong thing is made of dearer stuff than the one who stays away.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3867, 3507, '', 16, 'Friends are the sailors who guide your rickety boat safely across the dangerous waters of life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3868, 97812, '', 16, 'A true friend unbosoms freely, advises justly, assists readily, adventures boldly, takes all patiently, defends courageously, and continues a friend unchangeably.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3869, 26083, '', 16, 'The bird a nest, the spider a web, man friendship.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3870, 16174, '', 16, 'It takes a long time to grow an old friend.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3871, 14464, '', 16, 'At some point, our inner fire goes out in everyone\'s life. It is then burst into flame by an encounter with another human being. We should be thankful to those who rekindle the inner spirit.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3872, 32, '', 16, 'Friends are relatives you make for yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(3873, 94015, '', 16, 'A good friend is a connection to life - a tie to the past, a road to the future, the key to sanity in a totally insane world.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3874, 88797, '', 16, 'Remember we all stumble, every one of us. That\'s why it\'s a comfort to go hand in hand.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3875, 46943, '', 16, 'Do good to your friends to keep them, to your enemies to win them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3876, 98718, '', 16, 'Have no friends not equal to yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3877, 66792, '', 16, 'A good friend is cheaper than therapy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3878, 94989, '', 16, 'If a friend is in trouble, don\'t annoy him by asking if there is anything you can do. Think up something appropriate and do it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3879, 42015, '', 16, 'A friend is the one who comes in when the whole world has gone out. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3880, 50297, '', 16, 'There are big ships and small ships. But the best ship of all is friendship.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3881, 98872, '', 16, 'A friend in need is a friend indeed.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3882, 47418, '', 16, 'A real friend is someone who would feel loss if you jumped on a train, or in front of one.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3883, 58867, '', 16, 'It is not so much our friends\'  help that helps us, as the confidence of their help.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3884, 85757, '', 16, 'A friend is a gift you give yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
(3885, 51979, '', 16, 'Of what shall a man be proud, if he is not proud of his friends?', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:11:18', '2023-01-27 00:30:44'),
