(4348, 87032, '', 27, 'Learning is the beginning of wealth, health and spirituality. Searching and learning is where the miracle process happens.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:23:03', '2023-01-27 00:30:49'),
(4349, 1250, '', 27, 'Health is the thing that makes you feel that now is the best time of the year.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:23:03', '2023-01-27 00:30:49'),
(4350, 6059, '', 27, 'True friendship is like sound health; the value of it is seldom known until it is lost.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:23:03', '2023-01-27 00:30:49'),
(4351, 56468, '', 27, 'Good health and good sense are two of life\'s greatest blessings.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:23:03', '2023-01-27 00:30:49'),
