(4925, 1462, '', 24, 'Ambition is like love, impatient both of delays and rivals.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4926, 61414, '', 24, 'Those who aim at great deeds must also suffer greatly.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4927, 59633, '', 24, 'The very substance of the ambitious is merely the shadow of a dream.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4928, 98111, '', 24, 'Make no little plans, they have no magic to stir men\'s blood. Make big plans, aim high in hope and work.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4929, 74046, '', 24, 'An ounce of hypocrisy is worth a pound of ambition.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4930, 14979, '', 24, 'Though ambition in itself is a vice, it often is also the parent of virtue.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4931, 70817, '', 24, 'Give way to the better if way to the better there be, it exacts a full look at the worst.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4932, 54245, '', 24, 'The tragedy is that so many have ambition and so few have ability.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4933, 70859, '', 24, 'Ambition is the last refuge of failure.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4934, 71364, '', 24, 'The most absurd and reckless aspirations have sometimes led to extraordinary success.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4935, 26644, '', 24, 'A man\'s worth is no greater than the worth of his ambitions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4936, 54249, '', 24, 'He only earns his freedom and his life who takes them every day by storm.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4937, 44398, '', 24, 'The world stands aside to let anyone pass who knows where he is going.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4938, 78979, '', 24, 'It\'s a funny thing about life; if you refuse to accept anything but the best, you very often get it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4939, 40905, '', 24, 'A man without ambition is dead. A man with ambition but no love is dead.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4940, 58806, '', 24, 'The significance of a man is not in what he attains but rather in what he longs to attain.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4941, 23771, '', 24, 'Basically you have to suppress your own ambitions in order to be who you need to be.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4942, 84742, '', 24, 'All rising to great places is by a winding stair.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4943, 79647, '', 24, 'Ambition is an idol, on whose wings great minds are carried only to extreme - to be sublimely great or to be nothing.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4944, 86706, '', 24, 'Most people would succeed in small things if they were not troubled with great ambitions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4945, 42182, '', 24, 'To be happy at home is the ultimate result of all ambition.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4946, 14695, '', 24, 'Better to live one year as a tiger, than a hundred as a sheep.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4947, 50207, '', 24, 'You have to remember something: Everybody pities the weak. Jealousy you have to earn.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4948, 60032, '', 24, 'Live together like brothers, and do business like strangers.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4949, 54976, '', 24, 'Business is a lot like a game of tennis - those who serve well usually end up winning.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4950, 28831, '', 24, 'In this world nothing is certain but death and taxes.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4951, 26654, '', 24, 'He profits most who serves best.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4952, 72603, '', 24, 'The great leaders are like the best conductors - they reach beyond the notes to reach the magic in the players.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4953, 59270, '', 24, 'If you don\'t drive your business, you will be driven out of business.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4954, 71219, '', 24, 'High achievement always takes place in the framework of high expectation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4955, 40458, '', 24, 'The difference between a boss and a leader: a boss says, \"Go!\" -a leader says, \"let\'s go!\".', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4956, 68600, '', 24, 'Business makes a man as well as tries him.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4957, 38788, '', 24, 'A friendship founded on business is better than a business found on friendship.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4958, 89747, '', 24, 'Don\'t simply retire from something; have something to retire to.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4959, 32503, '', 24, 'Promotion should not be more important than accomplishment, or avoiding instability more important than taking the right risk.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4960, 51046, '', 24, 'Do not craze yourself with thinking, but go about your business anywhere.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4961, 54068, '', 24, 'A business that makes nothing but money is a poor business.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4962, 78287, '', 24, 'If you cannot work with love but only with distaste it is better that you should leave your work.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4963, 54009, '', 24, 'The purpose of business is to create and keep a customer.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4964, 47598, '', 24, 'You can make a lot of mistakes and still recover if you run on an efficient operation. Or you can be brilliant and still go out of business if you\'re too inefficient.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4965, 44183, '', 24, 'If we could sell our experiences for what they cost us, we\'d all be millionaires.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4966, 18154, '', 24, 'We know nothing of what will happen in future, but by the analogy of experience.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4967, 31840, '', 24, 'Men are wise in proportion, not to their experience, but to their capacity for experience.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4968, 65316, '', 24, 'Even if you don\'t have the answer, you certainly have to admire the problem.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4969, 84084, '', 24, 'A procrastinator\'s work is never finished.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:55'),
(4970, 7667, '', 24, 'The professional has learned that success, like happiness, comes as a by-product of hard work.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4971, 43433, '', 24, 'If you\'re good at something, never let your friends know, because for their purpose,they will make you do it for free.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4972, 76584, '', 24, 'In business \'professionalism\' is not a tactic but a moral value.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4973, 14012, '', 24, 'Leadership is never an avenue to be self-serving but,a platform to render great service to people.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4974, 62638, '', 24, 'It is very unprofessional for a professional to declare another professional an unprofessional without professional expertise.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4975, 16200, '', 24, 'The more you enjoy the game.. the better you\'ll play.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4976, 92149, '', 24, 'Professionalism has a universal culture, irrespective of language, religion or country.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4977, 19093, '', 24, 'Miracle will happen when passion is part of the profession', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4978, 9103, '', 24, 'Professionalism is a compassionate study of behavior from human kind to passion about work.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4979, 67621, '', 24, 'You are the authors of your life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4980, 86478, '', 24, 'The best preparation for tomorrow is doing your best today.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4981, 18170, '', 24, 'Start where you are, use what you have, do what you can.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4982, 93154, '', 24, 'Focus on being productive instead of busy.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4983, 18256, '', 24, 'Work smarter, not harder.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4984, 61446, '', 24, 'If you hate waking up on Mondays, change your job.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4985, 87646, '', 24, 'Everything begins with an idea.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4986, 46746, '', 24, 'Every job is a self-portrait of the person who does it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4987, 77092, '', 24, 'Success requires daily action.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4988, 76336, '', 24, 'A job isn\'t just a job. It\'s who you are.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4989, 6331, '', 24, 'Pleasure in the job puts perfection in the work.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4990, 62642, '', 24, 'If you fell down yesterday, stand up today.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4991, 75164, '', 24, 'You may encounter many defeats, but you must not be defeated. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4992, 21405, '', 24, 'Courage doesn’t always roar, sometimes it’s the quiet voice at the end of the day whispering ‘I will try again tomorrow.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4993, 36043, '', 24, 'Every strike brings you closer to the next home run.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4994, 46780, '', 24, 'A bend in the road is not the end of the road…unless you fail to make the turn.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4995, 44381, '', 24, 'It always seems impossible until it’s done.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4996, 57062, '', 24, 'Fail often so you can succeed sooner.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4997, 27013, '', 24, 'If you want the rainbow, you gotta put up with the rain.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4998, 16568, '', 24, 'Throw off the bowlines. Sail away from the safe harbor. Catch the trade wind in your sails. Explore. Dream. Discover.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(4999, 49596, '', 24, 'Remember that not getting what you want is sometimes a wonderful stroke of luck.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5000, 83823, '', 24, 'A large oak tree is just a little nut that refused to give up.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5001, 95586, '', 24, 'Don\'t let anyone scare you out of your full potential.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5002, 17598, '', 24, 'When you come to the end of your rope, tie a knot and hang on.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5003, 21013, '', 24, 'Remember that guy that gave up? Neither does anyone else.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5004, 79742, '', 24, 'No important endeavor that required innovation was done without risk. You have to be willing to take those risks.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5005, 9617, '', 24, 'If you are insecure, guess what? The rest of the world is too. Do not overestimate the competition and underestimate yourself. You are better than you think.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5006, 82743, '', 24, 'I think that the power is the principle. The principle of moving forward, as though you have the confidence to move forward, eventually gives you confidence when you look back and see what you’ve done.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5007, 3498, '', 24, 'The brick walls are there for a reason. The brick walls are not there to keep us out. The brick walls are there to show us how badly we want something.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5008, 54876, '', 24, 'Success seems to be connected to action. Successful people keep moving. They make mistakes, but they never quit', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5009, 45134, '', 24, 'You’ll never please everyone, but you only have to please a few people to get an offer.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5010, 14486, '', 24, 'You don’t need a new day to start over, you only need a new mindset.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5011, 55162, '', 24, 'You can’t do boring things with epic people.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5012, 31577, '', 24, 'Choose a lazy person to do a hard job because a lazy person will find an easy way to do it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5013, 97907, '', 24, 'You were born prepacked. God looked at your entire life, determined your assignment, and gave you the tools to do the job.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5014, 25649, '', 24, 'Think about how much more engaged we would be at work if we were truly inspired ... if we had leaders who viewed their jobs as triggers for an inspired workforce.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5015, 52158, '', 24, 'There\'s no job too immense, when you got confidence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5016, 68443, '', 24, 'Even sweeping floors is not such a bad job if it puts you closer to your dream. It is only a bad job if it is taking you nowhere.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56');
INSERT INTO `quotes` (`id`, `order`, `entry_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `author`, `has_notif`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(5017, 92562, '', 24, 'Our attitude toward our job can determine whether our days are filled with excitement and the sense of fulfillment that comes from top performance - or with frustration, boredom, and fatigue.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5018, 33290, '', 24, 'Give me six hours to chop down a tree and I will spend the first four sharpening the axe. - Abraham Lincoln', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5019, 24789, '', 24, 'The secret of getting ahead is getting started. The secret of getting started is breaking your complex overwhelming tasks into small manageable tasks, and starting on the first one.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5020, 81390, '', 24, 'There are 3 outcomes for you in any job: you\'ll be fired, quit or get laid off. You WILL change jobs.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5021, 53501, '', 24, 'You will never change what you tolerate.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5022, 11355, '', 24, 'Even if you have a job that\'s not necessarily the most fulfilling job, start looking for the one or two things you do like about your job and focus on those.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5023, 15826, '', 24, 'People who are proud of their job are usually driven by an inner enthusiasm that allows them to obtain bigger goals.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5024, 16393, '', 24, 'A success is anyone who is doing deliberately a predetermined job because that\'s what he decided to do deliberately', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5025, 33810, '', 24, 'If we focus on the things that are positive about our jobs, then we can tackle those activities we don’t enjoy with a better attitude and, in some cases, actually learn to enjoy them.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5026, 45784, '', 24, 'Doing a good job and taking pride in your customer service accomplishments is a way to prevent job burnout.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5027, 4024, '', 24, 'Don\'t make a habit out of choosing what feels good over what\'s actually good for you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5028, 46602, '', 24, 'Television is NOT real life. In real life people actually have to leave the coffee shop and go to jobs.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5029, 81285, '', 24, 'You are the CEO of YOU. There is no job security, you must ensure that your company of YOU is one where if you were hiring a person you would pick you', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5030, 39972, '', 24, 'Well done, is better than well said.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5031, 74858, '', 24, 'When you prevail - and you eventually will if you stick to the job - they will all tell you that they knew all along you could do it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5032, 74704, '', 24, 'Whether you think you can or you think you can’t, you’re right.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5033, 80281, '', 24, 'Risk something or forever sit with your dreams.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5034, 67590, '', 24, 'Believe you can and you’re halfway there.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5035, 76772, '', 24, 'Perfection is not attainable, but if we chase perfection we can catch excellence.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5036, 75672, '', 24, 'It is during our darkest moments that we must focus to see the light.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5037, 51488, '', 24, 'Stop looking outside, strength and confidence comes from within. It is there all the time.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5038, 62763, '', 24, 'Don\'t limit yourself. Many people limit themselves to what they think they can do. You can go as far as your mind lets you. What you believe you can achieve.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5039, 3860, '', 24, 'In a chronically leaking boat, energy devoted to changing vessels is more productive than energy devoted to patching leaks', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5040, 47709, '', 24, 'Man cannot discover new oceans unless he has the courage to lose sight of the shore.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5041, 48127, '', 24, 'You don\'t learn to walk by following rules. You learn by doing and falling over.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5042, 62732, '', 24, 'The man who removes a mountain begins by carrying away small stones.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5043, 30591, '', 24, 'So many of our dreams at first seem impossible, then they seem improbable, and then, when we summon the will, they soon become inevitable.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5044, 83503, '', 24, 'Do not let what you cannot do interfere with what you can do.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5045, 56110, '', 24, 'The important thing is not being afraid to take a chance. Remember, the greatest failure is to not try. Once you find something you love to do, be the best at doing it', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5046, 54737, '', 24, 'Obstacles don\'t have to stop you. If you run into a wall, don\'t turn around and give up. Figure out how to climb it, go through it, or work around it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5047, 58994, '', 24, 'Chase the vision, not the money; the money will end up following you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5048, 58078, '', 24, 'Working hard and long hours is worth it only if you enjoy what you are doing... it is never worth it only for a career.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5049, 42833, '', 24, 'Do you know what your career goals are? What job did you want to get.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5050, 99791, '', 24, 'If you are preparing for a career transition or wanting to transform your current one, use low-risk situations to practice building your inner resilience to change.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5051, 99500, '', 24, 'Many things catch your fancy but true, lasting, career oriented success can only come if you are willing to combine that passion of choice with hard work and determination', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
(5052, 17445, '', 24, 'Humor can make a difference in every career path and job situation.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:24:13', '2023-01-27 00:30:56'),
