(5177, 35, '', 25, 'The ability to be in the present moment is a major component of mental wellness', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(5178, 93692, '', 25, 'A great hallmark of mental wellness is the ability to be in the present moment, fully and with no thoughts of being elsewhere.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5179, 89819, '', 25, 'Having a lot of friends and family around you – that’s all a part of wellness.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5180, 17358, '', 25, 'Cooking at home is a great wellness trend simply because you know exactly what goes into your meal and you can tweak it to your tastes.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5181, 21079, '', 25, 'Sometimes weight gain isn’t a lack of willpower.  Sometimes it’s a sign of having enough strength to allow yourself to heal, despite cultural expectations.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5182, 72995, '', 25, 'You cannot mess up your healing process unless you quit.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5183, 75398, '', 25, 'This is about health and longevity! Nourishing your body into balance. Forget the scales. Focus on real health markers.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5184, 39938, '', 25, 'The number one tip for glowing skin is not the skin products but the food you’re eating', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5185, 66923, '', 25, 'Eliminating the things you love is not wellness. Wellness feeds your soul and makes you feel good.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5186, 20179, '', 25, 'There are six components of wellness: proper weight and diet, proper exercise, breaking the smoking habit, control of alcohol, stress management and periodic exams.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5187, 66322, '', 25, 'Every living cell in your body is made from the food you eat. If you consistently eat junk food then you’ll have a junk body.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5188, 47184, '', 25, 'Leave all the afternoon for exercise and recreation, which are as necessary as reading. I will rather say more necessary because health is worth more than learning', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5189, 7334, '', 25, 'Fitness for me is wellness. It means being healthy – mentally and physically. - Suniel Shetty.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5190, 9147, '', 25, 'Nutrition is very important to me for both my own health and wellness, but also for my children.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5191, 25321, '', 25, 'When things start to feel whacky I’ll either walk in the woods or ride or sit. I’ll then focus on wellness, affirmations and goals.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5192, 94983, '', 25, 'There is a point where you have to start regaining yourself and managing your time, and your mental wellness.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5193, 2778, '', 25, 'Health and wellness does mean different things to different people.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5194, 60670, '', 25, 'Taking care of myself used to be at the bottom of my list, but I’m all about wellness. - Caroline Ghosn', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5195, 13651, '', 25, 'The doctor of the future will no longer treat the human frame with drugs, but rather will cure and prevent disease with nutrition.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5196, 70799, '', 25, 'Let food be thy medicine, thy medicine shall be thy food.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5197, 1260, '', 25, 'Proper nutrition is the difference between feeling exhausted and getting the most out of a workout.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5198, 43449, '', 25, 'A healthy attitude is contagious but don’t wait to catch it from others. Be a carrier.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5199, 52899, '', 25, 'Healthy eating isn’t about counting fat grams, dieting, cleanses and antioxidants; it’s about eating food untouched from the way we find it in nature in a balanced way.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5200, 65699, '', 25, 'By choosing healthy over skinny, you are choosing self-love over self-judgment.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5201, 90662, '', 25, 'Eating healthy food fills your body with energy and nutrients. Imagine your cells smiling back at you and saying: ‘Thank you!’', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5202, 28811, '', 25, 'Good health is not something we can buy. However, it can be an extremely valuable savings account.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5203, 19247, '', 25, 'You can’t control what goes on outside, but you can control what goes on inside.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5204, 12377, '', 25, 'Make eating fruits and vegetables a priority. This is so simple and beneficial, yet most people don’t do it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5205, 14920, '', 25, 'A healthy lifestyle includes exercise, nutrition, healthy sleep patterns and a healthy group of friends.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5206, 57455, '', 25, 'It’s never too early or too late to work towards being the healthiest you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5207, 51381, '', 25, 'Keep healthy veggies at home, so you’ll snack on healthy veggies.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5208, 61740, '', 25, 'Games are such a powerful intervention in health and wellness.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5209, 45, '', 25, 'Even people who aren’t sick may not have optimal wellness.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(5210, 49765, '', 25, 'Wellness is not the absence of pain ….. But the absence of limitation', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5211, 67067, '', 25, 'Committing to a lifetime of wellness is not a luxury-it’s a necessity. You’ll never have enough time; you have to make the time.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5212, 26137, '', 25, 'Life expectancy would grow by leaps and bounds if green vegetables smelled as good as bacon.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5213, 4432, '', 25, 'You can do a lot for your diet by eliminating foods that have mascots.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5214, 37306, '', 25, 'One should eat to live, not live to eat.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5215, 30031, '', 25, 'You say you’re ‘depressed’ – all I see is resilience. You are allowed to feel messed up and inside out. It doesn’t mean you’re defective – it just means you’re human. - David Mitchell', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5216, 69387, '', 25, 'You don’t have to live a lie. Living a lie will mess you up. It will send you into depression. It will warp your values.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5217, 17344, '', 25, 'Anger, resentment and jealousy doesn’t change the heart of others– it only changes yours.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5218, 19421, '', 25, 'If you are chronically down, it is a lifelong fight to keep from sinking', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
