(5220, 46790, '', 25, 'It’s brilliant, being depressed; you can behave as badly as you like.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5221, 46673, '', 25, 'Sufficient sleep, exercise, healthy food, friendship, and peace of mind are necessities, not luxuries.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5222, 64578, '', 25, 'He who has health has hope, and he who has hope has everything.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5223, 7781, '', 25, 'Create healthy habits, not restrictions.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5224, 69636, '', 25, 'We are what we repeatedly do.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5225, 9005, '', 25, 'Health is a relationship between you and your body.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5226, 1360, '', 25, 'What is called genius is the abundance of life and health.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5227, 33269, '', 25, 'The mind and body are not separate. what affects one, affects the other.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5228, 19430, '', 25, 'Nobody can be in good health if he does not have all the time fresh air, sunshine, and good water.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5229, 60743, '', 25, 'Take care of yourself, be healthy, and always believe you can be successful in anything you truly want.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5230, 41771, '', 25, 'For happy healthy, fuel yourself with dreams and greens.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5231, 7839, '', 25, 'If you have health, you probably will be happy, and if you have health and happiness, you have all the wealth you need, even if it is not all you want.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5232, 51794, '', 25, 'The clock is ticking. Are you becoming the person you want to be?', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
