(5234, 17857, '', 25, 'To keep the body in good health is a duty, otherwise we shall not be able to keep our mind strong and clear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5235, 46293, '', 25, 'If we could give every individual the right amount of nourishment and exercise, not too little and not too much, we would have found the safest way to health.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5236, 45694, '', 25, 'Being healthy is a success that many people forget to celebrate.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5237, 63553, '', 25, 'Pleasure is always derived from something outside you, whereas joy arises from within.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5238, 87962, '', 25, 'When you do the right thing, you get the feeling of peace and serenity associated with it. Do it again and again.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5239, 1469, '', 25, 'You will find peace not by trying to escape your problems, but by confronting them courageously. You will find peace not in denial, but in victory.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5240, 36451, '', 25, 'Do not look for happiness outside yourself. The awakened seek happiness inside.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5241, 91880, '', 25, 'Beautify your inner dialogue. Beautify your inner world with love light and compassion. Life will be beautiful.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5242, 8416, '', 25, 'Each one has to find his peace from within. And peace to be real must be unaffected by outside circumstances.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5243, 4706, '', 25, 'You find peace not by rearranging the circumstances of your life, but by realizing who you are at the deepest level.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5244, 38168, '', 25, 'A quiet conscience makes one strong!', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5245, 59038, '', 25, 'Have love for your inner Self and everything else is done for you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5246, 78723, '', 25, 'Learning to distance yourself from all the negativity is one of the greatest lessons to achieve inner peace.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5247, 37461, '', 25, 'Your mind will answer most questions if you learn to relax and wait for the answer.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5248, 30418, '', 25, 'The time to relax is when you don\'t have time for it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5249, 16548, '', 25, 'A good half of the art of living is resilience.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:58'),
(5250, 75106, '', 25, 'Resilience, in a sense, is applied optimism.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5251, 25408, '', 25, 'You have power over your mind – not outside events. Realize this, and you will find strength.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5252, 41117, '', 25, 'Health is the thing that makes you feel that now is the best time of the year. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5253, 6642, '', 25, 'Mind over matter. There is no greater pain than what a mind can create. Be mindful. A healthy mind can remedy or cure almost anything.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5254, 46699, '', 25, 'Take care of yourself, you only get one life, and you want to live as long as possible. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5255, 89855, '', 25, 'Good humour is the health of the soul, sadness its poison.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5256, 79169, '', 25, 'The root of all health is in the brain. The trunk of it is in emotion. The branches and leaves are the body. The flower of health blooms when all parts work together.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5257, 67677, '', 25, 'Healthier parents, create healthier leaders and a healthier future for our children! Wake up, get out, and do your thing.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5258, 22554, '', 25, 'Cherish your life, Cherish your health, Cherish your family, Cherish your friends. For these are the things that money can’t buy and will define your true wealth.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5259, 44594, '', 25, 'They say if you don’t have your health you ain’t got nothing, but the truth is, you ain’t got nothing if you have no one to worry about your health. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5260, 11379, '', 25, 'Eating crappy food isn’t a reward — it’s a punishment. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5261, 2502, '', 25, 'It is important to keep in mind that our bodies must work pretty well, or there wouldn’t be so many humans on the planet. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5262, 48314, '', 25, 'Health is the greatest possession. Contentment is the greatest treasure. Confidence is the greatest friend. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
