(5264, 52777, '', 25, 'Health is hearty, health is harmony, health is happiness. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5265, 12590, '', 25, 'What some call health if purchased by perpetual anxiety about diet, isn’t much better than tedious disease.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5266, 13238, '', 25, 'Humour and health, the staples of wealth. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5267, 74675, '', 25, 'When the character is lost, nothing is lost; when wealth is lost, something is lost; but when health is lost, everything is lost.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5268, 96580, '', 25, 'Don’t let your emotions build inside! Just let it all out. Embrace it. That is a part of growth and health for your life defences.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5269, 26854, '', 25, 'There’s nothing more important than our good health – that’s our principal capital asset.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5270, 73033, '', 25, 'Every one of you has health that is unique and totally different from everybody else. Completely! Because we are all like snowflakes.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5271, 55438, '', 25, 'Cakes are healthy too, you just eat a small slice. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5272, 31674, '', 25, 'A fit, healthy body—that is the best fashion statement. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5273, 11645, '', 25, 'When health is absent, wisdom cannot reveal itself, art cannot manifest, strength cannot fight, wealth becomes useless, and intelligence cannot be applied.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5274, 79290, '', 25, 'An over-indulgence of anything, even something as pure as water, can intoxicate.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5275, 77862, '', 25, 'Nothing is as chaotic as it seems. Nothing is worth diminishing your health. Nothing is worth poisoning yourself with stress, anxiety, and fear. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5276, 45078, '', 25, 'The greatest gift you can give your family and the world is a healthy you.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5277, 7546, '', 25, 'Respect your body. Eat well. Dance forever. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5278, 4413, '', 25, 'Health does not come from a bottle, exercise program, or herbal supplement. It comes from the choices that we make on our behalf.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5279, 72303, '', 25, 'To ensure good health: eat lightly, breathe deeply, live moderately, cultivate cheerfulness, and maintain an interest in life.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5280, 49166, '', 25, 'Health is a state of complete physical, mental, and social well-being, and not merely the absence of disease or infirmity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5281, 37290, '', 25, 'A fit, healthy body—that is the best fashion statement. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5282, 44668, '', 25, 'Health is worth more than learning.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5283, 74134, '', 25, 'The soul always knows what to do to heal itself. The challenge is to silence the mind.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5284, 6582, '', 25, 'To keep the body in good health is a duty otherwise we shall not be able to keep our mind strong and clear.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5285, 58425, '', 25, 'The higher your energy level, the more efficient your body. The more efficient your body, the better you feel and the more you will use your talent to produce outstanding results. ', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5286, 71947, '', 25, 'The existence of illness in the body may no doubt be called a shadow of the true illness that is held by a man in his mind.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5287, 62997, '', 25, 'Healthy is an outfit that looks different on everybody.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5288, 23035, '', 25, 'You can enjoy life and be healthy at the same time.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5289, 67524, '', 25, 'Healing is a matter of time, but it is sometimes also a matter of opportunity.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5290, 62963, '', 25, 'Life is not merely to be alive, but to be well.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
(5291, 92298, '', 25, 'Health and cheerfulness mutually beget each other.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:25:38', '2023-01-27 00:30:59'),
