(6775, 95199, '', 7, 'The moment where you doubt you can fly, you cease for ever being able to do it.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:30:13', '2023-01-27 00:31:14'),
(6776, 32475, '', 7, 'Think and wonder. Wonder and think.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:30:13', '2023-01-27 00:31:14'),
(6777, 40549, '', 7, 'Just for the record darling, not all positive change feels positive in the beginning.', '', 0, 2, '2022-12-20 21:30:13', '2023-01-27 00:31:14'),
