(9490, 76631, '', 26, 'When you\'re a beautiful person on the inside, nothing in the world can change that about you … If you can\'t accept yourself, then certainly no one else will.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9491, 75190, '', 26, 'If people were more concerned with how they looked on the inside, then on the outside, the world would be a nicer place to exist.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9492, 84094, '', 26, 'True beauty is when someone radiates that they like themselves.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9493, 5923, '', 26, 'Character develops in stream of struggle and adversity. Character is the foundation of your inner beauty which reflects in your personality.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9494, 64351, '', 26, 'Beauty comes from within. If you\'re happy and look at life in the best way you can, even when there are problems, it can make you beautiful on the outside.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9495, 79851, '', 26, 'Beauty lives with kindness.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9496, 49062, '', 26, 'We should look to the mind, and not to the outward appearance.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9497, 58353, '', 26, 'Beauty shouldn\'t be about changing yourself to achieve an ideal or be more socially acceptable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9498, 13858, '', 26, 'Real beauty is knowing that someone else\'s definition of beauty has no hold over you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9499, 1078, '', 26, 'Kindness and awareness work together. Through awareness, we understand the underlying beauty of everything and every being.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9500, 91237, '', 26, 'It is not fancy hair, gold jewelry, or fine clothes that should make you beautiful. No, your beauty should come from within you - the beauty of a gentle and quiet spirit', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9501, 82470, '', 26, 'True beauty could be discovered only by one who mentally complete the incomplete.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9502, 34274, '', 26, 'Whole life is a search for beauty. But, when the beauty is found inside, the search ends and a beautiful journey begins.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9503, 84921, '', 26, 'Create a beautiful inside, and you will look beautiful on the outside.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9504, 50735, '', 26, 'Don\'t let anyone take away your inner glow.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9505, 29759, '', 26, 'Children are our future. Teach them well and let them lead the way. Show them all the beauty they possess inside.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9506, 35530, '', 26, 'A pure heart is the vessel that contains a soul\'s true beauty.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9507, 19911, '', 26, 'My father used to say, \'Let them see you and not the suit. That should be secondary.\' - Cary Grant.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9508, 63104, '', 26, 'It\'s that heart of gold and stardust shine that makes you beautiful.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9509, 71172, '', 26, 'You\'re beautiful, just the way you are. Shine on. And dare anyone to turn off the lights.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9510, 51141, '', 26, 'At the core of your heart, you are perfect and pure. No one and nothing can alter that.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9511, 20155, '', 26, 'Focus on your inner beauty. Outer beauty will draw people to you, inner beauty will keep them in your presence.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9512, 40286, '', 26, 'Be kind. It will reveal your true inner beauty.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9513, 124, '', 26, 'Beauty is an expression of the inner and outer simplicity, kindness, and uniqueness of a person.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(9514, 58113, '', 26, 'Do all the good you can & create a life that feels good on the inside,not one that just looks good on the outside. It is inner beauty which matters most.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9515, 85821, '', 26, 'Groom yourself with a comb of confidence and inner beauty.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9516, 92971, '', 26, 'True beauty is not related to what color your hair is or what color your eyes are. True beauty is about who you are as a human being, your principles, your moral compass.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9517, 7332, '', 26, 'The more we control our mind, the more our inner peace increases and the happier we become.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9518, 57876, '', 26, 'The life of inner peace, being harmonious and without stress, is the easiest type of existence.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9519, 21438, '', 26, 'Learning to ignore things is one of the great paths to inner peace.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9520, 22386, '', 26, 'Happiness looks beautiful on you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9521, 82043, '', 26, 'Shine like the whole universe is yours.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9522, 86494, '', 26, 'Admire someone\'s beauty without questioning your own.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9523, 61305, '', 26, 'You are powerful, beautiful, brilliant and brave.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9524, 8376, '', 26, 'Life is a gift. Wake up everyday and realize that.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9525, 20778, '', 26, 'If you see someone without a smile, give them one of yours.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9526, 96932, '', 26, 'It\'s so strange that autumn is so beautiful; yet everything is dying.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9527, 58184, '', 26, 'A beautiful heart will bring things into your life that all the money in the world couldn\'t get you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:35:36', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9528, 51847, '', 17, 'The most important thing in the world is family and love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9529, 35018, '', 17, 'Nothing is better than going home to family and eating good food and relaxing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9530, 71846, '', 17, 'To us, family means putting your arms around each other and being there. - Barbara Bush', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9531, 41762, '', 17, 'In family life, love is the oil that eases friction, the cement that binds closer together, and the music that brings harmony.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9532, 76002, '', 17, 'Other things may change us, but we start and end with the family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9533, 47617, '', 17, 'Having somewhere to go is home. Having someone to love is family. And having both is a blessing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9534, 55904, '', 17, 'Being a family means you are a part of something very wonderful. It means you will love and be loved for the rest of your life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9535, 25439, '', 17, 'Family is not an important thing. It’s everything.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9536, 28745, '', 17, 'The memories we make with our family is everything.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9537, 74138, '', 17, 'The family is one of nature’s masterpieces.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9538, 78780, '', 17, 'In time of test, family is best. - Burmese Proverb.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9539, 10172, '', 17, 'It’s all about the quality of life and finding a happy balance between work, friends and family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9540, 12556, '', 17, 'Family and friendships are two of the greatest facilitators of happiness.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9541, 115, '', 17, 'Treat your family like friends and your friends like family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(9542, 60389, '', 17, 'Family and friends are hidden treasures, seek them and enjoy their riches.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9543, 65702, '', 17, 'To be a good parent, you need to take care of yourself so that you can have the physical and emotional energy to take care of your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9544, 57080, '', 17, 'Stick to the basics, hold on to your family and friends – they will never go out of fashion.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9545, 21658, '', 17, 'My family is my life, and everything else comes second as far as what’s important to me. - Michael Imperioli', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9546, 97817, '', 17, 'The family is the test of freedom; because the family is the only thing that the free man makes for himself and by himself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9547, 2789, '', 17, 'Think of your family today and every day thereafter, don’t let the busy world of today keep you from showing how much you love and appreciate your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9548, 70707, '', 17, 'Our family is a circle of strength of love with every birth and every union the circle grows.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9549, 6918, '', 17, 'There is no doubt that it is around the family and the home that all the greatest virtues… are created, strengthened and maintained.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9550, 90611, '', 17, 'Family is not defined by our genes, it is built and maintained through love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9551, 9316, '', 17, 'Family means nobody gets left behind or forgotten.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9552, 86551, '', 17, 'We may have our differences, but nothing’s more important than family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9553, 31730, '', 17, 'Life is beautiful. It’s about giving. It’s about family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9554, 81073, '', 17, 'Rejoice with your family in the beautiful land of life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9555, 61864, '', 17, 'Where there is family, there is love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9556, 8275, '', 17, 'Family gives you the roots to stand tall and strong.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9557, 17485, '', 17, 'Family is the heart of a home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9558, 4281, '', 17, 'It didn’t matter how big our house was; it mattered that there was love in it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9559, 4601, '', 17, 'The bond that links your true family is not one of blood, but of respect and joy in each other’s life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9560, 17672, '', 17, 'Call it a clan, call it a network, call it a tribe, call it a family: Whatever you call it, whoever you are, you need one.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9561, 29723, '', 17, 'Families are the compass that guides us. They are the inspiration to reach great heights, and our comfort when we occasionally falter.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9562, 75241, '', 17, 'The only rock I know that stays steady, the only institution I know that works, is the family. - Lee Lacocca.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9563, 9793, '', 17, 'When trouble comes, it’s your family that supports you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9564, 36922, '', 17, 'A happy family is but an earlier heaven.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9565, 12670, '', 17, 'Happiness is having a large, loving, caring, close-knit family in another city.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9566, 70175, '', 17, 'The strength of a family, like the strength of an army, lies in its loyalty to each other.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:47'),
(9567, 18808, '', 17, 'When everything goes to hell, the people who stand by you without flinching–they are your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9568, 96845, '', 17, 'Family faces are magic mirrors. Looking at people who belong to us, we see the past, present, and future.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9569, 69735, '', 17, 'The greatest thing in family life is to take a hint when a hint is intended-and not to take a hint when a hint isn\'t intended.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9570, 51065, '', 17, 'So much of what is best in us is bound up in our love of family, that it remains the measure of our stability because it measures our sense of loyalty.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9571, 17028, '', 17, 'A man should never neglect his family for business.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9572, 42745, '', 17, 'Everyone needs a house to live in, but a supportive family is what builds a home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9573, 39416, '', 17, 'Sister is probably the most competitive relationship within the family, but once the sisters are grown, it becomes the strongest relationship.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9574, 33876, '', 17, 'The informality of family life is a blessed condition that allows us all to become our best while looking our worst.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9575, 30137, '', 17, 'The greatest gift of family life is to be intimately acquainted with people you might never even introduce yourself to, had life not done it for you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9576, 125, '', 17, 'That\'s what people do who love you. They put their arms around you and love you when you\'re not so lovable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(9577, 97917, '', 17, 'There’s nothing that makes you more insane than family. Or more happy, or more exasperated, or more secure.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9578, 22471, '', 17, 'If the family were a boat, it would be a canoe that makes no progress unless everyone paddles.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9579, 25433, '', 17, 'One day you will do things for me that you hate. That is what it means to be family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9580, 68018, '', 17, 'The family–that dear octopus from whose tentacles we never quite escape, nor, in our inmost hearts, ever quite wish to.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9581, 44420, '', 17, 'The family is the first essential cell of human society.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9582, 37191, '', 17, 'My dear young cousin, if there\'s one thing I\'ve learned over the eons, it\'s that you can\'t give up on your family, no matter how tempting they make it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9583, 59382, '', 17, 'Sticking with your family is what makes it a family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9584, 86207, '', 17, 'What can you do to promote world peace? Go home and love your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9585, 38054, '', 17, 'If you cannot get rid of the family skeleton, you may as well make it dance.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9586, 66281, '', 17, 'Show me a family of readers, and I will show you the people who move the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9587, 38091, '', 17, 'Friends are the family you choose.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9588, 23825, '', 17, 'When push comes to shove, you always know who to turn to. That being a family isn\'t a social construct but an instinct.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9589, 33414, '', 17, 'Togetherness is an important ingredient of family life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9590, 99352, '', 17, 'The world, we\'d discovered, doesn\'t love you like your family loves you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9591, 40172, '', 17, 'Home is people. Not a place. If you go back there after the people are gone, then all you can see is what is not there any more.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9592, 99875, '', 17, 'It is the smile of a child, the love of a mother, the joy of a father, the togetherness of a family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9593, 76252, '', 17, 'Home is where you are loved the most and act the worst.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9594, 62867, '', 17, 'The love of family and the admiration of friends are much more important than wealth and privilege.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48');
INSERT INTO `quotes` (`id`, `order`, `entry_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `author`, `has_notif`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(9595, 53038, '', 17, 'You need a rock-solid foundation of friends and family to keep you where you need to be.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9596, 7017, '', 17, 'I sustain myself with the love of family. - Maya Angelou', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9597, 135, '', 17, 'Nothing purchased can come close to the renewed sense of gratitude for having family and friends.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(9598, 34945, '', 17, 'Home isn\'t where you\'re from, it\'s where you find light when all grows dark.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9599, 40193, '', 17, 'Our most basic instinct is not for survival but for family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9600, 145, '', 17, 'Families are like fudge–mostly sweet, with a few nuts.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(9601, 97671, '', 17, 'A man travels the world over in search of what he needs, and returns home to find it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9602, 79488, '', 17, 'I don\'t think quantity time is as special as quality time with your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9603, 79367, '', 17, 'You are born into your family and your family is born into you. No returns. No exchanges.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9604, 46755, '', 17, 'Family isn’t something that’s supposed to be static, or set. People marry in, divorce out. They’re born, they die. It’s always evolving, turning into something else.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9605, 63117, '', 17, 'I have a wonderful shelter, which is my family. - José Carreras', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9606, 61969, '', 17, 'In every conceivable manner, the family is a link to your past and a bridge to your future.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9607, 63949, '', 17, 'Cherish your human connections - your relationships with friends and family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9608, 46939, '', 17, 'A family is a place where principles are hammered and honed on the anvil of everyday living.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9609, 87830, '', 17, 'Give a little love to a child, and you get a great deal back.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9610, 40017, '', 17, 'Dignity is not negotiable. Dignity is the honor of the family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9611, 60583, '', 17, 'One of the things that binds us as a family is a shared sense of humor.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9612, 21550, '', 17, 'The family you come from isn\'t as important as the family you\'re going to have.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9613, 155, '', 17, 'The family is the nucleus of civilization.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(9614, 83364, '', 17, 'It takes a lot of work to put together a marriage, to put together a family and a home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9615, 24723, '', 17, 'You leave home to seek your fortune and, when you get it, you go home and share it with your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9616, 58154, '', 17, 'You have to defend your honor. And your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9617, 49694, '', 17, 'Happy is said to be the family which can eat onions together. They are, for the time being, separate, from the world, and have a harmony of aspiration.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9618, 73451, '', 17, 'Parents need all the help they can get. The strongest as well as the most fragile family requires a vital network of social supports.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9619, 18315, '', 17, 'When you start about family, about lineage and ancestry, you are talking about every person on earth.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9620, 17868, '', 17, 'Family, nature and health all go together.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9621, 64092, '', 17, 'As the family goes, so goes the nation and so goes the whole world in which we live.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9622, 43691, '', 17, 'Any problem, big or small, within a family, always seems to start with bad communication. Someone isn\'t listening.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9623, 99138, '', 17, 'Perhaps the greatest social service that can be rendered by anybody to the country and to mankind is to bring up a family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9624, 50584, '', 17, 'The first-born in every family is always dreaming for an imaginary older brother or sister who will look out for them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9625, 17035, '', 17, 'Blood relatives often have nothing to do with family, and similarly, family is about who you choose to make your life with.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9626, 66881, '', 17, 'Family love is messy, clinging, and of an annoying and repetitive pattern, like bad wallpaper. But you know they\'ll be always there for you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9627, 44400, '', 17, 'As you age naturally, your family shows more and more on your face. If you deny that, you deny your heritage.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9628, 49851, '', 17, 'If you have issues with family, friends, and people at work, try and solve these issues head on so you can move on and concentrate on having the life you want.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9629, 93185, '', 17, 'A family is a unit composed not only of children but of men, women, an occasional animal, and the common cold.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9630, 14221, '', 17, 'Your ability to communicate is an important tool in your pursuit of your goals, whether it is with your family, your co-workers or your clients and customers.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9631, 39338, '', 17, 'Everything family does is reflection on the other people.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9632, 17384, '', 17, 'You go through life wondering what is it all about but at the end of the day it\'s all about family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9633, 43864, '', 17, 'Historically, the family has played the primary role in educating children for life, with the school providing supplemental scaffolding to the family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9634, 83617, '', 17, 'Children in a family are like flowers in a bouquet: there\'s always one determined to face in an opposite direction from the way the arranger desires.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9635, 31090, '', 17, 'Everybody has basically the same family, it\'s just reconfigured slightly differently from one to the next.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9636, 66600, '', 17, 'There can be hope only for a society which acts as one big family, not as many separate ones.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9637, 1130, '', 17, 'The only people that you really have, are your family because they love you no matter what.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9638, 40044, '', 17, 'When you live on the road, going home is a place to escape and just be with your family to unwind.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9639, 24737, '', 17, 'With a family of six, there is always something to make, create and do together.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9640, 2710, '', 17, 'Having family responsibilities and concerns just has to make you a more understanding person.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9641, 12550, '', 17, 'However poor a man is; if he has a family, he\'s rich.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9642, 63603, '', 17, 'It\'s not flesh and blood but the heart which makes us fathers and sons.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9643, 34406, '', 17, 'When you look at your life, the greatest happiness are family happiness.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9644, 97328, '', 17, 'An ounce of blood is worth more than a pound of friendship. - Spanish proverb.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9645, 98227, '', 17, 'Blood\'s thicker than water, and when one\'s in trouble best to seek out the relative\'s open arms.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9646, 98064, '', 17, 'The great advantage of living in a large family is that early lesson of life\'s essential unfairness.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9647, 43462, '', 17, 'Spend some time this weekend on home improvement; improve your attitude toward your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9648, 80236, '', 17, 'Without a family, man, alone in the world, trembles with the cold.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9649, 89825, '', 17, 'You don\'t have to give birth to someone to have a family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9650, 85614, '', 17, 'My family was my guide to my reality. - Haywood Nelson.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9651, 79248, '', 17, 'People are pretty forgiving when it comes to other people\'s families. The only family that ever horrifies you is your own.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9652, 68197, '', 17, 'It didn\'t matter how big the house was; it mattered that there was love in it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9653, 24823, '', 17, 'Children need our unconditional love — whether they succeed or make mistakes; when life is easy and when life is tough.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9654, 86925, '', 17, 'That’s what people do who love you. They put their arms around you and love you when you’re not so lovable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9655, 56178, '', 17, 'In the family sandwich, the older people and the younger ones can recognize one another as the bread. Those in the middle are, for a time, the meat.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9656, 25822, '', 17, 'I grew up with six brothers. That\'s how I learned to dance — waiting for the bathroom. - Bob Hope.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9657, 13059, '', 17, 'There is no doubt that it is around the family and the home that all the greatest virtues, the most dominating virtues of human, are created, strengthened and maintained.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9658, 61029, '', 17, 'A family is what you make it. It is made strong, not by the number of heads counted at the dinner table, but by the memories you share, the commitment of time, caring and love you show to one another.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9659, 33463, '', 17, 'When all the dust is settled and all the crowds are gone, the things that matter are faith, family and friends', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9660, 87093, '', 17, 'A family doesn\'t have to perfect; it just needs to be united.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9661, 36105, '', 17, 'Family is a life jacket in the stormy sea of life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9662, 32684, '', 17, 'There\'s only one thing more precious than our time and that\'s who we spend it on.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:48'),
(9663, 56626, '', 17, 'Home should be an anchor, a port in a storm, a refuge, a happy place in which to dwell, a place where we are loved and where we can love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9664, 27948, '', 17, 'Families are like branches on a tree. We grow in different directions yet our roots remain as one.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9665, 66431, '', 17, 'The greatest moments in life are not concerned with selfish achievements but rather with the things we do for the people we love and esteem.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9666, 4894, '', 17, 'Where there is a family, there is sacrifices, happiness and love for others.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9667, 80148, '', 17, 'Family members are the relations where life begins and love never ends.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9668, 32980, '', 17, 'Family is the biggest support system in the times of trouble.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9669, 54252, '', 17, 'Families are the tie that reminds us of yesterday, provides strength and support for today, and give us hope for tomorrow.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9670, 26984, '', 17, 'How lucky you are to have something that makes saying goodbye so hard.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9671, 29304, '', 17, 'Family is a unique gift that needs to be appreciated and treasured, even when they’re driving you crazy.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9672, 14102, '', 17, 'Be grateful for the home you have, knowing that at this moment, all you have is all you need.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9673, 42443, '', 17, 'Love your family. Spend time, be kind & serve one another. Make no room for regrets. Tomorrow is not promised & today is short.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9674, 34150, '', 17, 'Many men can make a fortune but very few can build a family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9675, 49194, '', 17, 'Family is the people in your life who want you in theirs. The ones who accept you for who you are. The ones who would do anything to see you smile and who love you no matter what.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9676, 70342, '', 17, 'Your children need your presence more than your presents.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9677, 13697, '', 17, 'Tennis is just a game, family is forever. - Serena Williams', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9678, 95979, '', 17, 'Let us nurture the practice of family values, by embracing policies that value families.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9679, 36073, '', 17, 'Family isn’t defined only by last names or by blood; it’s defined by commitment and by love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9680, 39207, '', 17, 'Family and friends are a support system. They tell you what you need to hear, not what you want to hear, and they are there for you in good and bad times.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9681, 55421, '', 17, 'Blood makes you related. Loyalty makes you family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9682, 79326, '', 17, 'You may have your differences, but nothing’s more important than family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9683, 80540, '', 17, 'You need a strong family because, at the end, they will love you and support you unconditionally.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9684, 52520, '', 17, 'Spread love. Hug the people you care about and make sure they know that you care and appreciate them. Make it known to your friends and family that you love them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9685, 36073, '', 17, 'A man who doesn’t spend time with his family can never be a real man.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9686, 9341, '', 17, 'At the end of the day, a loving family should find everything forgivable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9687, 18384, '', 17, 'Our job as parents is to give our kids roots to grow and wings to fly.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9688, 82625, '', 17, 'Govern a family as you would cook a small fish – very gently.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9689, 9704, '', 17, 'Children get values, principles and etiquettes  from their family. Ensure to nurture good ones.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9690, 36643, '', 17, 'Quantity time is not as special as quality time with your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9691, 69826, '', 17, 'You are the bows from which your children as living arrows are sent forth.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9692, 26737, '', 17, 'The homemaker has the ultimate career. All other careers exist for one purpose only-and that is to support the ultimate career.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9693, 63449, '', 17, 'Home isn’t where you’re from, it’s where you find light when all grows dark.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9694, 59849, '', 17, 'Your family and your love must be cultivated like a garden. Time, effort, and imagination must be summoned constantly to keep any relationship flourishing and growing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9695, 5845, '', 17, 'Families keep us grounded when hopelessness surrounds us.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9696, 53540, '', 17, 'Anything is possible when you have the right people there to support you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9697, 40968, '', 17, 'There will always be steps you can take toward unity in your blended family. You will make—one step at a time!', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9698, 91353, '', 17, 'Bright families are just like bright colors: When you blend two, you get something beautiful!', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9699, 92236, '', 17, 'Blended families are made by choice, but it’s the love that strengthens them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9700, 22112, '', 17, 'Connections within a family are powerful forces of nature.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9701, 27060, '', 17, 'Family ties are like spider webs. They are delicate, yet so strong, And if they are broken or destroyed, They can be woven again.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9702, 14030, '', 17, 'I know every family has its problems, but I admire those that stick together. - Karina Barton.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9703, 1967, '', 17, 'Family: where life begins and love never ends.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9704, 86623, '', 17, 'Peace is the beauty of life. It is sunshine. It is the smile of a child, the love of a mother, the joy of a father, the togetherness of a family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9705, 4344, '', 17, 'When we have each other, we have everything.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9706, 14419, '', 17, 'You can kiss your family goodbye and put miles between you, but at the same time you carry them with you in your heart, and your mind, because you do not just live in a world but a world lives in you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9707, 27680, '', 17, 'Family members can be your best friends, you know. And best friends, whether or not they are related to you, can be your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9708, 92948, '', 17, 'The love in our family flows strong and deep, leaving us memories to treasure and keep.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9709, 21081, '', 17, 'Pass along the value of empathy to our children. Not sympathy, but empathy—the ability to stand in somebody else\'s shoes; to look at the world through their eyes.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9710, 76068, '', 17, 'Family is family, whether it’s the one you start out with the one you end up with, or the family you gain along the way.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9711, 80944, '', 17, 'To care for those who once cared for us is one of the highest honors.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9712, 31181, '', 17, 'Families don’t have to match. You don’t have to look like someone else to love them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9713, 7996, '', 17, 'I believe the world is one big family, and we need to help each other. - Jet Li', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9714, 15268, '', 17, 'Alone, you are strong, but together, you’ll be stronger than ever.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9715, 92721, '', 17, 'Life feels complete when you’re together with your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9716, 76268, '', 17, 'Children can never have too many positive adult role models in their lives.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9717, 3441, '', 17, 'Being happy in your family is more important than being perfect.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9718, 20476, '', 17, 'Family. We may not have it all together, but together we have it all.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9719, 81232, '', 17, 'Never forget who was with you from the start.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9720, 95850, '', 17, 'No family is perfect... we argue, we fight. We even stop talking to each other at times. But in the end, family is family... The love will always be there.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9721, 23010, '', 17, 'The love of a family is life\'s greatest blessing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9722, 63680, '', 17, 'Family doesn\'t have to be perfect; it just needs to be united.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9723, 10327, '', 17, 'You might be afraid of crossing an ocean or walking through flames but family would make you do even riskier things because that\'s how powerful the boy you have become.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9724, 83769, '', 17, 'Family is the support you will never have to pay for because come rain, or shine, they will be here to cheer you on with every of your life goals.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9725, 43698, '', 17, 'It\'s not necessarily what a family is typically supposed to look like. But it is what it is. It\'s about a connection and bond that everyone can identify with.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9726, 25884, '', 17, 'Blood makes you related, loyalty makes you family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9727, 74996, '', 17, 'Family is the best thing you could ever wish for. They are there for you during the ups and downs, and love you no matter what.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9728, 98600, '', 17, 'Family is a gift that lasts forever.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9729, 71118, '', 17, 'The most important thing a father can do for his children is to love their mother.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9730, 14346, '', 17, 'Our family is a circle of strength and love, with every birth and union it grows. Every crisis faced together makes the circle stronger.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9731, 56330, '', 17, 'If you are too busy to enjoy quality time with your family, then you need to re-evaluate your priorities.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9732, 1281, '', 17, 'The bonds of family bind us up, support us, help us. And they are also a bond from which it is difficult, perhaps impossible to extricate oneself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9733, 3503, '', 17, 'Family is in our hearts, bonded together for life, no matter where you rest your head.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9734, 5674, '', 17, 'Marriage bound us for a little while, but our children keep us together as a family for life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9735, 6486, '', 17, 'On the outside, it may look like we\'ve fallen apart, but as a family, we always stay together in our hearts.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9736, 58351, '', 17, 'Recipe for a unified family: 3 cups love, 1 cup empathy, 1/4 cup patience, 1 tablespoon teamwork.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9737, 11688, '', 17, 'Like a team in the championship game, our family will rally together in triumph.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9738, 83120, '', 17, 'Healing happens when individual hearts combine forces to beat as one at the center of a family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9739, 13247, '', 17, 'Take away all our possessions, and we are left with one structure held together by love: family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9740, 34790, '', 17, 'Our family cannot be divided, only rearranged. The end result looks different, but still feels unified and full of love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9741, 35087, '', 17, 'Each member of this family is a first responder; when we hear the call, we don\'t hesitate to unite and take action.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9742, 6379, '', 17, 'Life may carry us apart, but together we remain in each other\'s hearts.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9743, 61025, '', 17, 'Near or far, we\'re only separated by car. As long as we exist, there is no distance across which our family can\'t persist.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9744, 66686, '', 17, 'No matter where we each stand, together we can look upon the same sun, the same moon, and the same sky, so we are forever one family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9745, 85523, '', 17, 'You can\'t see air, but you need it to breathe and it is always there. Likewise, your family may not be in sight, but we need each other and will always be there.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9746, 98829, '', 17, 'As a family, we make - not take - time for each other. That is the key to a strong chain even though some links don\'t touch.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9747, 88797, '', 17, 'Oceans apart are not enough to break a family\'s bond.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9748, 97001, '', 17, 'The moments we talk to each other or think of each other will add up to the greater sum that is our family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9749, 8515, '', 17, 'On the front lines of love, we stick together as a family and win every time.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9750, 60029, '', 17, 'In a lifestyle filled with changing surroundings, our family remains bright as the beacon signaling home', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9751, 92890, '', 17, 'Though we don\'t all wear the uniform, we are all members of the same unit.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9752, 65672, '', 17, 'When one member of our family is in need, everyone deploys to offer aid.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9753, 15690, '', 17, 'There\'s an invisible bond that ties soldiers together, it\'s called family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9754, 59825, '', 17, 'When times get dark and the road is winding, know we are here waiting and praying for your safe return.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9755, 39866, '', 17, 'We cannot fight alongside you, but we take up arms in our hearts.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9756, 69332, '', 17, 'The foundation of a tight family can start with us.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9757, 78508, '', 17, 'Together as siblings, we have all we need to build a strong family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9758, 48907, '', 17, 'The bond between siblings is strong enough to keep any family together.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:49'),
(9759, 7859, '', 17, 'When siblings vow to stick together, the family can grow.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9760, 35643, '', 17, 'You are my sibling, my blood and my best friend by choice.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9761, 54251, '', 17, 'We make a great team, sib. You have my back and I\'ll pick up the slack.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9762, 65438, '', 17, 'Sharing bloodlines doesn\'t bond families together, love does.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9763, 21524, '', 17, 'Our shared love and devotion to each other is what makes us a family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9764, 80008, '', 17, 'Choosing to be a family together takes far more strength and love than genetics.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9765, 77378, '', 17, 'The day we decided to connect our lives together forever, was the day we became family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9766, 78562, '', 17, 'We don\'t share DNA, we share FNA: Family Never Abandons.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9767, 78832, '', 17, 'Together we make a perfect family puzzle.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9768, 85448, '', 17, 'Like gum to a shoe, you\'re stuck with me and I\'m stuck with you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9769, 1805, '', 17, 'Keeping a family together is like building a puzzle. It may be hard to gather all the pieces, but once gathered, they fit together seamlessly.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9770, 44764, '', 17, 'Keeping our family together means doing what\'s best for each individual, and what\'s best for the family as a whole.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9771, 58703, '', 17, 'On our own, we each make waves. Together, we form an ocean too vast and strong to be separated.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9772, 35617, '', 17, 'Family means Forever All Members Imprint Love on You.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9773, 9452, '', 17, 'Family can extend far beyond one household.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9774, 18435, '', 17, 'The further out you extend family togetherness, the stronger the entity becomes.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9775, 59932, '', 17, 'Extended family bonding provides a solid foundation for every individual\'s life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9776, 77668, '', 17, 'Extending love as far as your family reaches creates a web of love that\'s unbreakable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9777, 27255, '', 17, 'Family unity begins with U - N - I.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9778, 48118, '', 17, 'Family unity is not about being on the same page at the same time, it\'s about being in the same book working toward the same ending.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9779, 95101, '', 17, 'United we are family, divided we are alone', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9780, 49393, '', 17, 'Individually, we are vastly unique, but when put together, we are a total masterpiece.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9781, 76964, '', 17, 'The power created by family unity could keep the whole world alight.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9782, 95620, '', 17, 'The loving embrace of family brings all the warmth you\'ll ever need.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9783, 76156, '', 17, 'The love of family can never be replaced, it\'s one-of-a-kind.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9784, 35879, '', 17, 'Love to the infinite degree equals family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9785, 40820, '', 17, 'When our family is together, it\'s impossible not to feel the love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9786, 24925, '', 17, 'A strong family is the glue binding each individual to the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9787, 22217, '', 17, 'The strongest people are those backed by a loving family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9788, 5055, '', 17, 'Family togetherness is the driving force behind a loving heart.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9789, 81497, '', 17, 'When you fall in life, your family catches you and stands you back up.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9790, 47810, '', 17, 'The key to endurance and strength is a family standing together.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9791, 49047, '', 17, 'Nothing can break you when you have your family standing beside you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9792, 777, '', 17, 'Families are stuck together by love, so spread it around like glue.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9793, 602, '', 17, 'Keep your family together by being their biggest cheerleader and their biggest resource.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9794, 92968, '', 17, 'Family isn\'t a noun, it\'s a verb requiring action from each member to keep the whole afloat.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9795, 53765, '', 17, 'You may not choose your family, but you can choose to make it yours.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9796, 69125, '', 17, 'Focus on what ties you together, and your family can never fall apart.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9797, 52265, '', 17, 'Families are the individual parts that make up the whole world. Humanity depends on their togetherness.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9798, 12416, '', 17, 'Without family bonds, there isn\'t anything in the universe strong enough to hold people together.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9799, 48245, '', 17, 'When you choose to swim with family, you\'re creating a natural safety net from the dangers of the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9800, 80914, '', 17, 'Your family needs you as much as you need them; that\'s why it\'s important to stick together.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9801, 33114, '', 17, 'There\'s no one in the world more equipped and prepared to help you thrive than your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9802, 10386, '', 17, 'A family divided against itself cannot love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9803, 5916, '', 17, 'While a family can be divided by its individuals, it can never be divided into nothing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9804, 10744, '', 17, 'All families can be divided into two categories: those who choose each other and those tied together by invisible bonds.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9805, 52339, '', 17, 'Families who keep loving until they get it right will never be divided.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9806, 68542, '', 17, 'You can never divide a family so far that it ceases to exist. Some semblance of it always remains.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9807, 28697, '', 17, 'When you are ready to return, we will be right here waiting.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9808, 90045, '', 17, 'Go if you must, but know that home will still be here when you return.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9809, 93155, '', 17, 'Never fear coming home, for all you will see are open arms awaiting your embrace.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9810, 59992, '', 17, 'Keeping your family together is an extraordinary feat - especially in the face of great conflict.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9811, 51200, '', 17, 'The more we get together, the happier we\'ll be.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9812, 67932, '', 17, 'A family stitched together with love seldom unravels.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9813, 47859, '', 17, 'This is part of what a family is about, not just love. It’s knowing that your family will be there watching out for you. Nothing else will give you that. Not money. Not fame. Not work.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9814, 51368, '', 17, 'While we try to teach our children all about life, our children teach us what life is all about.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9815, 55703, '', 17, 'There is no such thing as a perfect family. Behind every door there are issues, the difference is accepting and encouraging each family member as they are not as we would like them to be.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9816, 77080, '', 17, 'Don’t take for granted the things closest to your heart. Cling to them as you would your life, for without them life is meaningless.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9817, 77074, '', 17, 'No one’s family is normal. Normalcy is a lie invented by advertising agencies to make the rest of us feel inferior.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9818, 53669, '', 17, 'Smile at each other, make time for each other in your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9819, 30133, '', 17, 'You need to make time for your family no matter what happens in your life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9820, 25656, '', 17, 'Some of us are so self-reliant that we won’t ask for help from our family members or close friends. You can’t do it all, all the time, by yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9821, 75171, '', 17, 'It’s amazing how ‘What can I do to help?’ said honestly and openly can bring you closer to your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9822, 60672, '', 17, 'No matter what you’ve done for yourself or for humanity, if you can’t look back on having given love and attention to your own family, what have you really accomplished?', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9823, 75618, '', 17, 'To maintain a joyful family requires much from both the parents and the children. Each member of the family has to become, in a special way, the servant of the others.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9824, 90621, '', 17, 'There is no rule book, no right or wrong; you just have to make it up and do the very best you can to care for your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9825, 68144, '', 17, 'May you be surrounded by friends and family, and if this is not your lot, may the blessings find you in your solitude.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9826, 60602, '', 17, 'Family should be the place where you can be your most complete self.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9827, 47788, '', 17, 'The love of a family is a life\'s greatest blessing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9828, 9610, '', 17, 'I find the family the most mysterious and fascinating institution in the world. - Amos Oz', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9829, 62495, '', 17, 'Family, we may not have it all together, but together we have it all.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9830, 31849, '', 17, 'Dad, a son\'s first hero, a daughter\'s first love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9831, 5165, '', 17, 'A family is a little world created by love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9832, 77645, '', 17, 'Time spent with family is worth every second.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9833, 31564, '', 17, 'You should never sacrifice tree things: your family, your heart, or your dignity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9834, 82374, '', 17, 'The family is a haven in a heartless world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9835, 1173, '', 17, 'It is a wise father that knows his own child.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9836, 28238, '', 17, 'The most precious jewels you\'ll ever have around your neck are the arms of your children. ', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9837, 76067, '', 17, 'Children don\'t need more things. The best toys a child can have is a parent who gets down on the floor and plays with them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9838, 59796, '', 17, 'Hold on to the tiny moments and cherish the little snuggles. They grow up so fast.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9839, 76360, '', 17, 'We must take care of our families wherever we find them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9840, 79738, '', 17, 'Family. Being loved no matter what.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9841, 70816, '', 17, 'Home is where your story begins.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9842, 58064, '', 17, 'Family isn’t just blood. It’s the people who love you. The people who have your back. ', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9843, 89479, '', 17, 'It only takes two to make a family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9844, 34690, '', 17, 'In the cookies of life, siblings are the chocolate chips.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9845, 91761, '', 17, 'Sibling: a combination of best friend and a pain in the neck.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9846, 28208, '', 17, 'Being a brother or a sister (if you are lucky enough) is a role of a lifetime.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9847, 29373, '', 17, 'In the family, there is strength that all the power in the world cannot undo.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9848, 89587, '', 17, 'No matter what situation you’re in, as long as you have a supportive family, you can achieve anything.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:50'),
(9849, 28644, '', 17, 'Nobody knows you or understands you like family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9850, 48636, '', 17, 'Family is the anchor during rough waters.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9851, 95672, '', 17, 'Family is anyone who loves you unconditionally.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9852, 92909, '', 17, 'Your family is the best team you could ever have.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9853, 3174, '', 17, 'Family strength is a marvellous thing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9854, 77303, '', 17, 'Love is the foundation of strength in a family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9855, 10660, '', 17, 'Family: We may not have it all together, but together we have it all.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9856, 89577, '', 17, 'Family is a strength who supports in every ups and downs.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9857, 90064, '', 17, 'Families are about love overcoming emotional torture.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9858, 63266, '', 17, 'Family is like music, some high notes, some low notes, but always a beautiful song.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9859, 78795, '', 17, 'People don’t understand the power of love and family and strength.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9860, 87424, '', 17, 'Family consists of people that love and care about each other mutually.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9861, 12070, '', 17, 'Draw great strength from your family and give in turn to those who come after you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9862, 60263, '', 17, 'The strength of a family isn’t determined by the number of members, but rather by the amount of love given and received.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9863, 83912, '', 17, 'Families survive, one way or another. You have a tie, a connection that exists long after death, through many lifetimes.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9864, 37500, '', 17, 'While at work, put a picture of your family on your desk. This will remind you that there is another world of yours at home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9865, 32926, '', 17, 'Family is key, and if you have love for family, then you have love for others–and you have unity as a people.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9866, 52223, '', 17, 'Family is one of the sweetest words anyone can say because the letters of family means “father and mother I love you”. So love your family always.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9867, 39992, '', 17, 'One of the primary purposes of civilization – and certainly its primary strength – is the guarantee that family life can flourish in unity, peace, and order.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9868, 16938, '', 17, 'Like the seaweed that clings to each other after each passing boat separates them, so too a family will come together with the passing of each crisis.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9869, 86801, '', 17, 'Whenever a woman strengthens the faith of a child, she contributes to the strength of a family – now and in the future.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9870, 3852, '', 17, 'Family strengthen each other during storms. They help us to be strong. After all, it is a family tradition. Our roots are deeper, our hearts are stronger, and we never give up.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9871, 52697, '', 17, 'A person\'s own family is, without a doubt, the greatest wealth that we will ever possess.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9872, 50232, '', 17, 'The bond of family blesses us with an immeasurable power.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9873, 15353, '', 17, 'Everyone needs to live within a house. But, having the love and support of your family? That is what makes your house a home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9874, 13149, '', 17, 'The only strength that really matters is the strength that makes you what you are in the eyes of those you love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9875, 68856, '', 17, 'We cannot destroy kindred: our chains stretch a little sometimes, but they never break.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9876, 75099, '', 17, 'Just as a house needs a foundation in order to stand firm, so does a person.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9877, 3312, '', 17, 'We will respect family life. We will develop it and encourage it in any way we can, for strong families are the foundation of strong communities.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9878, 7708, '', 17, 'Family life contributes immensely to an individual\'s happiness. Only in a happy home life can complete contentment be found.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9879, 84520, '', 17, 'People who have good relationships at home are more effective in the marketplace.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9880, 64021, '', 17, 'The strength of a man is in his character. A strong man is great man of wisdom who understands, his top priority is to his family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9881, 76645, '', 17, 'You are blood. You are sisters. No man can break that bond.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9882, 33090, '', 17, 'Family life is too intimate to be preserved by the spirit of justice. It can be sustained by a spirit of love which goes beyond justice.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9883, 62290, '', 17, 'The bond that links your true family is not one of blood, but of respect and joy in each other’s life. Rarely do members of the same family grow up under the same roof.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9884, 81706, '', 17, 'Family. A little bit of crazy, a little bit of loud and a whole lot of love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51');
INSERT INTO `quotes` (`id`, `order`, `entry_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `author`, `has_notif`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(9885, 93541, '', 17, 'He is happiest, be he king or peasant, who finds peace in his home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9886, 78879, '', 17, 'There is nothing like staying at home for real comfort.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9887, 12786, '', 17, 'Home is where the heart is.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9888, 70113, '', 17, 'People usually are the happiest at home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9889, 36646, '', 17, 'Home is not where you live but where they understand you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9890, 43443, '', 17, 'Home, the spot of earth supremely blest, a dearer, sweeter spot than all the rest.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9891, 35943, '', 17, 'Where we love is home, home that our feet may leave, but not our hearts.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9892, 26173, '', 17, 'The light is what guides you home, the warmth is what keeps you there.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9893, 74252, '', 17, 'Home is where we should feel secure and comfortable. ', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9894, 88333, '', 17, 'A house is made of walls and beams; a home is built with love and warmth.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9895, 56295, '', 17, 'Home is where there\'s one to love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9896, 73633, '', 17, 'We share our dwellings, and afterwards our dwellings shape us.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9897, 89284, '', 17, 'Home is four walls that enclose the right person.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9898, 4015, '', 17, 'Home is the place where we are treated the best, but grumble the most.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9899, 48187, '', 17, 'There is room in the smallest cottage for a happy loving pair.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9900, 17695, '', 17, 'A comfortable house is a great source of happiness. It ranks immediately after health and a good conscience.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9901, 93955, '', 17, 'A good home must be made, not bought.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9902, 87430, '', 17, 'May your walls know joy; May every room hold laughter and every window open to great possibility.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9903, 72020, '', 17, 'Home is where love resides, memories are created, friends and family belong and laughter never ends.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9904, 50922, '', 17, 'The home has endless love, laughter and laundry.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9905, 88318, '', 17, 'You can design, create, and build the most wonderful place in the world. But it takes people to make the dream a reality.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9906, 44458, '', 17, 'Our homes should inspire us to go out into the world to do great things & then welcome us back for refreshment.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9907, 10137, '', 17, 'The ache for home lives in all of us, the safe place where we can go as we are and not be questioned.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9908, 17422, '', 17, 'Home is a place you grow up wanting to leave, and grow old wanting to get back to.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9909, 25583, '', 17, 'Home is the place where it feels right to walk around without shoes.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9910, 78688, '', 17, 'The home should be the treasure chest of living.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9911, 5644, '', 17, 'The magic thing about home is that it feels good to leave, and it feels even better to come back.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9912, 81110, '', 17, 'Chase your dreams but always remember the road that will lead you home again.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9913, 46899, '', 17, 'Home is where you feel loved, appreciated, and safe.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9914, 49429, '', 17, 'Three keys unlock the door to a gracious atmosphere at home: Respect, influence, and forgiveness.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9915, 81809, '', 17, 'It takes hands to build a house, but only hearts can build a home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9916, 795, '', 17, 'Life takes you to unexpected places. Love brings you home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9917, 47975, '', 17, 'A well-loved home will always be a bit of a beautiful mess.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9918, 62657, '', 17, 'The most important work you will ever do will be within the walls of your own home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9919, 39711, '', 17, 'Home is not a place… it’s a feeling.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9920, 9830, '', 17, 'There is nothing more important than a good, safe, secure home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9921, 58166, '', 17, 'Home is where our story begins.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9922, 12118, '', 17, 'A house is made of bricks and beams. A home is made of hopes and dreams.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9923, 25367, '', 17, 'Where we love is home- home that our feet may leave, but not our hearts.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9924, 72823, '', 17, 'It’s like coming home after a long trip. That’s what love is like. It’s like coming home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9925, 6746, '', 17, 'The thrill of coming home has never changed.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9926, 70295, '', 17, 'No matter who you are or where you are, instinct tells you to go home to your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9927, 22030, '', 17, 'Never leave home without a kiss, a hug and an I love you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9928, 40968, '', 17, 'You can have more than one home. You can carry your roots with you, and decide where they grow.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9929, 53306, '', 17, 'Seek home for rest, for home is best.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9930, 50886, '', 17, 'The power of finding beauty in the humblest things makes home happy and life lovely.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9931, 4800, '', 17, 'There is a magic in that little world, home; it is a mystic circle that surrounds comforts and virtues never known beyond its hallowed limits', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9932, 18650, '', 17, 'Home is the most popular, and will be the most enduring of all earthly establishments.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9933, 73179, '', 17, 'The sun at home warms better than the sun elsewhere. - Albania Proverb.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:51'),
(9934, 78526, '', 17, 'Home is where you feel at home and are treated well.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9935, 83988, '', 17, 'Love begins at home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9936, 71040, '', 17, 'The ultimate luxury is being able to go home, relax, and enjoy your time with your family.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:37:09', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9937, 88722, '', 23, 'Creativity is contagious. Pass it on.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9938, 80235, '', 23, 'Creativity makes a leap, then looks to see where it is.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9939, 68655, '', 23, 'Thinking is the enemy of creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9940, 89080, '', 23, 'Creativity comes from a conflict of ideas.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9941, 66731, '', 23, 'Creativity takes courage.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9942, 17435, '', 23, 'To be creative means to be in love with life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9943, 41464, '', 23, 'Creativity is the ability to introduce order into the randomness of nature.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9944, 84414, '', 23, 'You can’t use up creativity. The more you use, the more you have.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9945, 12125, '', 23, 'Creativity involves breaking out of established patterns in order to look at things in a different way.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9946, 69101, '', 23, 'Necessity is the mother of invention, it is true, but its father is creativity, and knowledge is the midwife.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9947, 16308, '', 23, 'There’s no one way to be creative. Any old way will work.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9948, 58738, '', 23, 'Controversy is part of the nature of art and creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9949, 88001, '', 23, 'Creativity is a natural extension of our enthusiasm.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9950, 94529, '', 23, 'Creativity is the greatest rebellion in existence.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9951, 41584, '', 23, 'Creativity is a wild mind and a disciplined eye.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9952, 4088, '', 23, 'The worst enemy to creativity is self-doubt.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9953, 5146, '', 23, 'Creativity doesn’t need to be a Herculean event. But it does need consistent fostering.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9954, 17182, '', 23, 'Energy is the key to creativity. Energy is the key to life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9955, 23921, '', 23, 'It is better to fail in originality, than to succeed in imitation.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9956, 82905, '', 23, 'There is no doubt that creativity is the most important human resource of all. Without creativity, there would be no progress, and we would be forever repeating the same patterns.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9957, 6298, '', 23, 'Creative activity could be described as a type of learning process where teacher and pupil are located in the same individual.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9958, 6861, '', 23, 'Creativity is the process of having original ideas that have value. It is a process; it’s not random.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9959, 50056, '', 23, 'Curiosity is really the wellspring of creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9960, 62956, '', 23, 'Absurdity and anti-absurdity are the two poles of creative energy.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9961, 12556, '', 23, 'Creativity is just connecting things.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9962, 20021, '', 23, 'To live is to express, and to express you have to create. Creation is never merely repetition. To live is to express oneself freely in creation.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9963, 6562, '', 23, 'Creativity is obscured by the conscious mind.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9964, 1491, '', 23, 'Creativity doesn’t wait for that perfect moment. It fashions its own perfect moments out of ordinary ones.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9965, 7247, '', 23, 'Creativity is always a leap of faith. You’re faced with a blank page, blank easel, or an empty stage.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9966, 7033, '', 23, 'Odd how the creative power at once brings the whole universe to order.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9967, 18328, '', 23, 'Creativity has got to start with humanity and when you’re a human being, you feel, you suffer.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9968, 82141, '', 23, 'There is creative reading as well as creative writing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9969, 93215, '', 23, 'Creativity is seeing something that doesn’t exist already. You need to find out how you can bring it into being.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9970, 7714, '', 23, 'The works must be conceived with fire in the soul but executed with clinical coolness.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9971, 59390, '', 23, 'Written reports stifle creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9972, 6092, '', 23, 'Creativity is the greatest expression of liberty.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9973, 40812, '', 23, 'Creativity is piercing the mundane to find the marvelous.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9974, 22078, '', 23, 'Creativity is based on the belief that there’s no particular virtue in doing things the way they’ve always been done.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9975, 79221, '', 23, 'Creativity can be described as letting go of certainties.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9976, 42222, '', 23, 'Creativity is inventing, experimenting, growing, taking risks, breaking rules, making mistakes, and having fun.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9977, 59849, '', 23, 'Anxiety is part of creativity, the need to get something out.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9978, 7608, '', 23, 'Creative thinking – in terms of idea creativity – is not a mystical talent. It is a skill that can be practiced and nurtured.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9979, 52539, '', 23, 'Without freedom, there is no creation.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9980, 53458, '', 23, 'The chief enemy of creativity is good sense. - Pablo Picasso', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9981, 29044, '', 23, 'The difficulty lies not so much in developing new ideas as in escaping from old ones.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9982, 11536, '', 23, 'Creativity can solve almost any problem. The creative act, the defeat of habit by originality, overcomes everything.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9983, 73804, '', 23, 'Creativity is the sudden cessation of stupidity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9984, 81255, '', 23, 'The world always seems brighter when you’ve just made something that wasn’t there before.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9985, 89244, '', 23, 'Conditions for creativity are to be puzzled; to concentrate; to accept conflict and tension; to be born everyday; to feel a sense of self.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9986, 4648, '', 23, 'Creativity is the quality that you bring to the activity that you are doing. It is an attitude, an inner approach – how you look at things.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9987, 1869, '', 23, 'Whatsoever you do, if you do it joyfully, if you do it lovingly, if your act of doing is not purely economical, then it is creative.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9988, 3102, '', 23, 'Truly creative people care a little about what they have done, and a lot about what they are doing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9989, 84982, '', 23, 'Creative people are often found either disagreeable or intimidating by mediocrities.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9990, 68683, '', 23, 'Some people use things; they destroy. You’re a creator, a builder.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9991, 72596, '', 23, 'Curiosity about life in all of its aspects is still the secret of great creative people.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9992, 54136, '', 23, 'Creativity is the soul of the true scholar.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9993, 81768, '', 23, 'Creativity comes from trust. Trust your instincts. And never hope more than you work.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9994, 93086, '', 23, 'All creative people want to do the unexpected.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9995, 52128, '', 23, 'When you can do a common thing in an uncommon way; you will command the attention of the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9996, 84190, '', 23, 'Creativity is people who care enough to keep thinking about something until they find the simplest way to do it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9997, 35291, '', 23, 'If you want creative workers, give them enough time to play.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9998, 36097, '', 23, 'When we engage in what we are naturally suited to do, our work takes on the quality of play and it is play that stimulates creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(9999, 15039, '', 23, 'Everybody has a creative potential and from the moment you can express this creative potential, you can start changing the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10000, 60534, '', 23, 'A truly creative person rids him or herself of all self-imposed limitations.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10001, 54577, '', 23, 'Be careful what you put on the canvas of your mind today – it matters.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10002, 746, '', 23, 'In order to be creative you have to be allowed to fail.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10003, 116, '', 23, 'Creativity is seeing what everyone else has seen, and thinking what no one else has thought.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(10004, 49506, '', 23, 'When anybody pays you to be creative, you’re very lucky.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10005, 11270, '', 23, 'A creative man is motivated by the desire to achieve, not by the desire to beat others.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10006, 37661, '', 23, 'The creative person is flexible; he is able to change as the situation changes, to break habits, to face indecision and changes in conditions without undue stress.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10007, 68128, '', 23, 'The principle goal of education is to create men who are capable of doing new things, not simply of repeating what other generations have done – men who are creative, inventive and discoverers.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10008, 17979, '', 23, 'Creativity is more than just being different. Anybody can plan weird; that’s easy. What’s hard is to be as simple as Bach. Making the simple, awesomely simple, that’s creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10009, 9511, '', 23, 'The creative person is willing to live with ambiguity. He doesn’t need problems solved immediately and can afford to wait for the right ideas.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10010, 89592, '', 23, 'A man may die, nations may rise and fall, but an idea lives on.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10011, 126, '', 23, 'An idea that is developed and put into action is more important than an idea that exists only as an idea.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(10012, 14420, '', 23, 'If you want something new, you have to stop doing something old.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10013, 82293, '', 23, 'Replace fear with curiosity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10014, 54869, '', 23, 'All our knowledge has its origin in our perceptions.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10015, 10373, '', 23, 'When the uncreative tell the creative what to do, it stops being art.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10016, 35527, '', 23, 'Creative works may indeed be kind of like property, but it’s the property that we’re all building on.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10017, 5286, '', 23, 'Held in the palms of thousands of disgruntled people over the centuries have been ideas worth millions – if they only had taken the first step and then followed through.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10018, 32121, '', 23, 'The uncreative mind can spot wrong answers, but it takes a very creative mind to spot wrong questions.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10019, 38384, '', 23, 'Rational thoughts never drive people’s creativity the way emotions do.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10020, 99675, '', 23, 'It is better to have enough ideas for some of them to be wrong, than to be always right by having no ideas at all.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10021, 77458, '', 23, 'It seems to be one of the paradoxes of creativity that in order to think originally, we must familiarize ourselves with the ideas of others.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:52'),
(10022, 18320, '', 23, 'Find something only you can say. - James Dickey.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10023, 29001, '', 23, 'An idea is like a virus. Resilient.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10024, 73405, '', 23, 'An invasion of armies can be resisted, but not an idea whose time has come.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10025, 17190, '', 23, 'Anyone who lives within their means suffers from a lack of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10026, 64190, '', 23, 'Clean out a corner of your mind and creativity will instantly fill it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10027, 22757, '', 23, 'Invention strictly speaking, is little more than a new combination of those images which have been previously gathered and deposited in the memory; nothing can come from nothing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10028, 55177, '', 23, 'Originality is nothing but judicious imitation.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10029, 136, '', 23, 'Create with the heart; build with the mind.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(10030, 16849, '', 23, 'To cease to think creatively is to cease to live. - Benjamin Franklin.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10031, 21489, '', 23, 'In the end, creativity isn’t just the things we choose to put in, it’s the things we choose to leave out.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10032, 52880, '', 23, 'The creation of something new is not accomplished by the intellect but by the play instinct acting from inner necessity. ', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10033, 48251, '', 23, 'All the works of man have their origin in creative fantasy. What right have we then to depreciate imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10034, 64839, '', 23, 'An idea that is not dangerous is unworthy of being called an idea at all.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10035, 24446, '', 23, 'By believing passionately in something that still does not exist, we create it. The non-existent is whatever we have not sufficiently desired.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10036, 97018, '', 23, 'The creative mind plays with the objects it loves.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10037, 9414, '', 23, 'Reason is a harmonizing, controlling force rather than a creative one.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10038, 56773, '', 23, 'The important thing for you is to be alert, to question, to find out, so that your own initiative may be awakened.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10039, 57862, '', 23, 'Somewhere, something incredible is waiting to be known.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10040, 146, '', 23, 'Creativity is allowing yourself to make mistakes. Art is knowing which ones to keep.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(10041, 34789, '', 23, 'Creativity is thinking up new things. Innovation is doing new things.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10042, 24945, '', 23, 'An artist paints, dances, draws, writes, designs, or acts at the expanding edge of consciousness. We press into the unknown rather than the known. This makes life lovely and lively.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10043, 85052, '', 23, 'Invention, it must be humbly admitted, does not consist in creating out of void but out of chaos.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10044, 37899, '', 23, 'Outrageous behavior, also known as the lunatic fringe, is the seed bed of innovation and creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10045, 156, '', 23, 'Imagination is the beginning of creation. You imagine what you desire, you will what you imagine, and at last, you create what you will.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(10046, 1028, '', 23, 'Vulnerability is the birthplace of innovation, creativity and change.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10047, 85098, '', 23, 'Innovation is saying no to a thousand things. - Steve Jobs', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10048, 8857, '', 23, 'Imagination is everything. It is the preview of life’s coming attractions.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10049, 74245, '', 23, 'Genius means little more than the faculty of perceiving in an unhabitual way.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10050, 31284, '', 23, 'You need chaos in your soul to give birth to a dancing star.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10051, 92095, '', 23, 'Creative power, is that receptive attitude of expectancy which makes a mold into which the plastic and as yet undifferentiated substance can flow and take the desired form.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10052, 56922, '', 23, 'Genius without education is like silver in the mine.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10053, 28034, '', 23, 'Do not fear to be eccentric in opinion, for every opinion now accepted was once eccentric.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10054, 3527, '', 23, 'The most talented, thought-provoking, game-changing people are never normal.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10055, 10845, '', 23, 'Your soul is infinitely creative. It is alive and expansive in nature. It is curious and playful, changing with the tides of time.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10056, 4215, '', 23, 'The inner fire is the most important thing mankind possesses.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10057, 22230, '', 23, 'The principal mark of genius is not perfection but originality, the opening of new frontiers.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10058, 89471, '', 23, 'For me, insanity is super sanity. The normal is psychotic. Normal means lack of imagination, lack of creativity. - Jean Dubuffet.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10059, 47177, '', 23, 'Criticize by creation, not by finding fault.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10060, 98343, '', 23, 'It is the mystery of the creative act that something other than our conscious self takes over.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10061, 74602, '', 23, 'The creative is the place where no one else has ever been. You have to leave the city of your comfort and go into the wilderness of your intuition.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10062, 10711, '', 23, 'There is only one of you in all time, this expression is unique. And if you block it, it will never exist through any other medium and it will be lost.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10063, 29409, '', 23, 'Create whatever causes a revolution in your heart.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10064, 83475, '', 23, 'A creative person of any kind goes about their work because it’s their path, it’s what excites them, it’s what aligns their soul with who they truly are, who they showed up to be.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10065, 27680, '', 23, 'Genius is nothing but a greater aptitude for patience.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10066, 97696, '', 23, 'The creative process is a process of surrender, not control.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10067, 61053, '', 23, 'A rock pile ceases to be a rock pile the moment a single man contemplates it, bearing within him the image of a cathedral.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10068, 6880, '', 23, 'It is good taste, and good taste alone, that possesses the power to sterilize and is always the first handicap to any creative functioning.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10069, 97227, '', 23, 'The secret to creativity is knowing how to hide your sources. - Albert Einstein.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10070, 47826, '', 23, 'A first-rate soup is more creative than a second-rate painting.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10071, 81624, '', 23, 'The road to creativity passes so close to the madhouse and often detours or ends there.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10072, 89416, '', 23, 'To invent, you need a good imagination and a pile of junk. - Thomas Edison.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10073, 4609, '', 23, 'Creative people need time to just sit around and do nothing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10074, 58394, '', 23, 'Human salvation lies in the hands of the creatively maladjusted.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10075, 27676, '', 23, 'Creative things have to sell to get acknowledged as such.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10076, 74856, '', 23, 'The Stone Age didn’t end because they ran out of stones.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10077, 91484, '', 23, 'Innovation is taking two things that exist and putting them together in a new way.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10078, 34007, '', 23, 'The value of an idea lies in the using of it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10079, 47057, '', 23, 'Innovation is the unrelenting drive to break the status quo and develop anew where few have dared to go.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10080, 81673, '', 23, 'Innovation takes birth in sync with the evolution of customer’s expectations and demands or vice versa.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10081, 63770, '', 23, 'If you look at history, innovation doesn’t come just from giving people incentives; it comes from creating environments where their ideas can connect.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10082, 61798, '', 23, 'You have to be willing to be misunderstood if you’re going to innovate.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10083, 10184, '', 23, 'If I had asked the public what they wanted, they would have said a faster horse. - Henry Ford.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10084, 65366, '', 23, 'When the winds of change blow, some people build walls and others build windmills.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10085, 31893, '', 23, 'The reasonable man adapts himself to the world; the unreasonable one persists in trying to adapt the world to himself. Therefore all progress depends on the unreasonable man.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10086, 77592, '', 23, 'To stay ahead in innovation, look at horizontal industries and the ones leading your current industry, someone is always doing something new.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10087, 99398, '', 23, 'The best way to predict the future is to create it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10088, 47912, '', 23, 'Innovation is progress in the face of tradition.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10089, 17183, '', 23, 'You can’t allow tradition to get in the way of innovation. There’s a need to respect the past, but it’s a mistake to revere your past.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10090, 30130, '', 23, 'Most innovation involves doing the things we do every day a little bit better rather than creating something completely new and different.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10091, 76315, '', 23, 'They always say time changes things, but you actually have to change them yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10092, 77403, '', 23, 'Don’t be afraid to take big steps when one is indicated. You can’t cross a chasm in two small jumps.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10093, 61972, '', 23, 'Be an innovator, not an imitator.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10094, 80108, '', 23, 'There’s a way to do it better. Find it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10095, 65118, '', 23, 'Innovation survives only when people believe in their own ideas.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10096, 4861, '', 23, 'There’s always an element of chance and you must be willing to live with that element. If you insist on certainty, you will paralyze yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10097, 4654, '', 23, 'If at first the idea is not absurd, then there is no hope for it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10098, 66141, '', 23, 'Confusion is a word we have invented for an order that is not yet understood.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10099, 88831, '', 23, 'When looking to innovate—fail forward. Innovation can be a chaotic process, embrace it and learn from your failures.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10100, 4674, '', 23, 'If you’re not failing every now and again, it’s a sign you’re not doing anything very innovative.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10101, 70501, '', 23, 'Innovation is more likely to come from a person who sits down and does the same thing every single day until they become an expert than from a person who sits down once because they feel inspired.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10102, 53604, '', 23, 'There is no innovation and creativity without failure. Period.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10103, 50548, '', 23, 'Everything you’ve ever wanted is on the other side of fear.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10104, 14868, '', 23, 'What good is an idea if it remains an idea? Try. Experiment. Fail. Try again. Change the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10105, 951, '', 23, 'You can have brilliant ideas, but if you can’t get them across, your ideas won’t get you anywhere.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10106, 35332, '', 23, 'Listen to anyone with an original idea, no matter how absurd it may sound at first. If you put fences around people, you get sheep. Give people the room they need.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10107, 9718, '', 23, 'Ideas are like rabbits. You get a couple and learn how to handle them, and pretty soon you have a dozen.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10108, 15612, '', 23, 'A dream will not become an innovation if there is no realization.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10109, 66284, '', 23, 'Never tell people how to do things. Tell them what to do and they will surprise you with their ingenuity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10110, 22618, '', 23, 'The way to get good ideas is to get lots of ideas and throw the bad ones away.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10111, 73456, '', 23, 'You can’t just ask customers what they want and then try to give that to them. By the time you get it built, they’ll want something new.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10112, 38788, '', 23, 'It’s easy to come up with new ideas; the hard part is letting go of what worked for you two years ago, but will soon be out of date.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10113, 1220, '', 23, 'Daring ideas are like chessmen moved forward; they may be beaten, but they may start a winning game.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10114, 92628, '', 23, 'What is now proved was once only imagined.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10115, 19011, '', 23, 'The world needs dreamers and the world needs doers. But above all what the world needs most are dreamers that do.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10116, 92308, '', 23, 'They did not know it was impossible so they did it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10117, 61597, '', 23, 'If the only tool you have is a hammer, you tend to see every problem as a nail.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10118, 19122, '', 23, 'Finding opportunity is a matter of believing it’s there.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10119, 3505, '', 23, 'Modern society is built upon two things: truth, which is discovered, and innovation, which is created.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10120, 67254, '', 23, 'When something is important enough, you do it even if the odds are not in your favor.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:53'),
(10121, 72032, '', 23, 'Creativity is the act of turning new and imaginative ideas into reality.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10122, 97527, '', 23, 'Creativity involves two processes: thinking, then producing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10123, 36282, '', 23, 'Innovation is the production or implementation of a creative idea.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10124, 58222, '', 23, 'Creativity is a function of leadership. It requires navigating uncharted territory and having the courage to face adversity to bring your vision into fruition.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10125, 45244, '', 23, 'For innovation to flourish, organizations must create an environment that fosters creativity — exchanging knowledge, ideas and shaping the direction of the future.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10126, 38087, '', 23, 'The economic future of an organization depends on its ability to create wealth by fostering innovation, creativity and entrepreneurship.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10127, 23132, '', 23, 'Improvisation can feel like jumping into the abyss at first, but once you jump, fear turns into excitement, and your imagination kicks in.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10128, 3945, '', 23, 'Creativity is the power to create something new, to reach deep into our subconscious for that “aha” solution. ', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10129, 59589, '', 23, 'The life of the creative man is lead, directed and controlled by boredom. Avoiding boredom is one of our most important purposes.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10130, 70686, '', 23, 'There’s zero correlation between being the best talker and having the best ideas.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10131, 76249, '', 23, 'To be successful we must live from our imaginations, not from our memories.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10132, 83666, '', 23, 'We are not creatures of circumstance; we are creators of circumstance.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10133, 40292, '', 23, 'Access to talented and creative people is to modern business what access to coal and iron ore was to steel-making.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10134, 25060, '', 23, 'Creativity may be hard to nurture, but it’s easy to thwart.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10135, 29466, '', 23, 'To generate creative ideas, you have to start from an unusual place. But to explain those ideas, you have to connect them to something familiar.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10136, 26430, '', 23, 'You cannot mandate productivity, you must provide the tools to let people become their best.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10137, 79634, '', 23, 'When you ask creative people how they did something, they feel a little guilty because they didn’t really do it, they just saw something. It seemed obvious to them after a while. ', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10138, 69653, '', 23, 'Design is not just what it looks like and feels like. Design is how it works.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10139, 41272, '', 23, 'Innovation comes from people calling each other at 10.30 at night because they realised something that shoots holes in how we’ve been thinking about a problem.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10140, 12379, '', 23, 'Creativity is so delicate a flower that praise tends to make it bloom while discouragement often nips it at the bud.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10141, 35854, '', 23, 'In the modern world of business, it is useless to be a creative original thinker unless you can also sell what you create.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10142, 62556, '', 23, 'Without change, there is no innovation, creativity, or incentive for improvement. Those who initiate change will have a better opportunity to manage the change that is inevitable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10143, 83650, '', 23, 'Ideas are not solutions; they are the raw material of solutions.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10144, 97227, '', 23, 'Innovation arises from ongoing circles of exchange, where information is not just accumulated or stored, but created. Knowledge is generated anew from connections that weren’t there before.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10145, 43012, '', 23, 'The things we fear most in organizations–fluctuations, disturbances, imbalances–are the primary sources of creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10146, 59623, '', 23, 'Ideas won\'t keep: something must be done about them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10147, 46096, '', 23, 'The visionary starts with a clean sheet of paper, and re-imagines the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10148, 82287, '', 23, 'It is better to have enough ideas for some of them to be wrong than to be always right by having no ideas at all.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10149, 55049, '', 23, 'Every artist dips his brush in his own soul, and paints his own nature into his pictures.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10150, 69991, '', 23, 'The world is but a canvas to the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10151, 25974, '', 23, 'So you see, imagination needs moodling – long, inefficient, happy idling, dawdling and puttering.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10152, 22071, '', 23, 'As competition intensifies, the need for creative thinking increases. It is no longer enough to do the same thing better . . . no longer enough to be efficient and solve problems', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10153, 50955, '', 23, 'Everyone who’s ever taken a shower has had an idea. It’s the person who gets out of the shower, dries off and does something about it who makes a difference.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10154, 12319, '', 23, 'All great deeds and all great thoughts have a ridiculous beginning.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10155, 53528, '', 23, 'To draw, you must close your eyes and sing. - Pablo Picasso.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10156, 85515, '', 23, 'The truly creative person is one who can think crazy; such a person knows full well that many of his great ideas will prove to be worthless. ', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10157, 83943, '', 23, 'Conditions for creativity are to be puzzled; to concentrate; to accept conflict and tension; to be born every day; to feel a sense of self.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10158, 21141, '', 23, 'You become more divine as you become more creative.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10159, 42085, '', 23, 'Every day is an opportunity to be creative – the canvas is your mind, the brushes and colours are your thoughts and feelings.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10160, 67313, '', 23, 'The highest prize we can receive for creative work is the joy of being creative.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10161, 39206, '', 23, 'You can be creative only if you love life enough that you want to enhance its beauty, you want to bring a little more music to it, a little more poetry to it, a little more dance to it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10162, 21463, '', 23, 'Creative effort spent for any other reason than the joy of being in that light-filled space, love, whatever we want to call it, is lacking in integrity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10163, 30598, '', 23, 'I can’t understand why people are frightened of new ideas. I’m frightened of the old ones. - John Cage.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10164, 80010, '', 23, 'To live a creative life, we must lose our fear of being wrong.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10165, 50072, '', 23, 'By believing passionately in something that still does not exist, we create it. The nonexistent is whatever we have not sufficiently desired.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10166, 91777, '', 23, 'Behind all creation is silence. Silence is the essential condition, the vital ingredient for all creation and all that is created.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10167, 74139, '', 23, 'You need to find your own magic to stay in the world of creative play.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10168, 14003, '', 23, 'Life is trying things to see if they work.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10169, 58027, '', 23, 'Learning and innovation go hand in hand. The arrogance of success is to think that what you did yesterday will be sufficient for tomorrow.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10170, 87326, '', 23, 'An essential aspect of creativity is not being afraid to fail.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10171, 60130, '', 23, 'Your ego can become an obstacle to your work. If you start believing in your greatness, it is the death of your creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10172, 58565, '', 23, 'Innovation distinguishes between a leader and a follower.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10173, 88717, '', 23, 'Creativity is a habit, and the best creativity is the result of good work habits.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10174, 26333, '', 23, 'The true sign of intelligence is not knowledge but imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10175, 53621, '', 23, 'Art is the elimination of the unnecessary.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10176, 39491, '', 23, 'You use a glass mirror to see your face. You use works of art to see your soul.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10177, 80890, '', 23, 'A creative life is an amplified life. It\'s a bigger life, a happier life, an expanded life, and a hell of a lot more interesting life. - Elizabeth Gilbert.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10178, 76676, '', 23, 'Don’t wait for inspiration. It comes while working.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54');
INSERT INTO `quotes` (`id`, `order`, `entry_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `author`, `has_notif`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(10179, 22186, '', 23, 'It\'s no good being too easily swayed by people\'s opinions. You have to believe in yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10180, 89987, '', 23, 'Begin by learning to draw and paint like the old masters. After that, you can do as you like; everyone will respect you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10181, 89211, '', 23, 'Deadlines and things make you creative.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10182, 24593, '', 23, 'You can be cautious or you can be creative, but there\'s no such thing as a cautiously creative.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10183, 68485, '', 23, 'The creative adult is the child who survived.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10184, 75816, '', 23, 'Great things are done by a series of small things brought together.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10185, 62206, '', 23, 'Make visible what, without you, might perhaps never have been seen.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10186, 63186, '', 23, 'Simplicity is the ultimate sophistication.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10187, 61514, '', 23, 'Creative ideas don’t grow on trees, but they are an unlimited resource if you keep them flowing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10188, 35772, '', 23, 'Refining and simplifying are what lead to a beautiful finished product. It’s a skill that must be learned!', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10189, 99367, '', 23, 'Self-doubt is normal. Create anyway.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10190, 9312, '', 23, 'Your unique perspective is your creative gold.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10191, 84394, '', 23, 'Bringing the spirit of fun, excitement, and child-like wonder is extremely valuable to be creative.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10192, 9048, '', 23, 'The more you live a life that inspires you, the more access you have to your creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10193, 37251, '', 23, 'You’re not always going to be inspired; you’ve got to sit down and work anyway.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10194, 92780, '', 23, 'Create for yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10195, 56112, '', 23, 'Creativity comes from your inner world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10196, 35355, '', 23, 'When all think alike, then no one is thinking.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10197, 13680, '', 23, 'Great is the human who has not lost his childlike heart.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10198, 2794, '', 23, 'To think creatively, we must be able to look afresh at what we normally take for granted.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10199, 29576, '', 23, 'No great discovery was ever made without a bold guess.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10200, 30398, '', 23, 'To raise new questions and new possibilities, to regard old problems from a new angle, requires creative imagination and marks real advances in science. - Albert Einstein.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10201, 72245, '', 23, 'Without the playing with fantasy no creative work has ever yet come to birth. The debt we owe to the play of imagination is incalculable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10202, 94576, '', 23, 'We shall not cease from exploration, and at the end of all our exploring will be to arrive where we started and know the place for the first time.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10203, 45286, '', 23, 'There\'s a way to do it better—find it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10204, 68755, '', 23, 'Creativity is not the finding of a thing, but the making something out of it after it is found.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10205, 74027, '', 23, 'The achievement of excellence can only occur if the organization promotes a culture of creative dissatisfaction.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10206, 26833, '', 23, 'You don\'t understand anything unless you understand there are at least 3 ways.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10207, 75682, '', 23, 'Creative thinking is not a talent, it is a skill that can be learnt. It empowers people by adding strength to their natural abilities.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10208, 82006, '', 23, 'All human development, no matter what form it takes, must be outside the rules; otherwise we would never have anything new.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10209, 89599, '', 23, 'Anyone can look for fashion in a boutique or history in a museum. The creative explorer looks for history in a hardware store and fashion in an airport.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10210, 85411, '', 23, 'Discoveries are often made by not following instructions, by going off the main road, by trying the untried.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10211, 20612, '', 23, 'Every act of creation is first of all an act of destruction.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10212, 62501, '', 23, 'The organizations of the future will increasingly depend on the creativity of their members to survive.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10213, 94751, '', 23, 'In a truly creative collaboration, work is pleasure, and the only rules and procedures are those that advance the common cause.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10214, 70322, '', 23, 'In the beginner\'s mind there are many possibilities, but in the expert\'s mind there are few.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10215, 49821, '', 23, 'Money never starts an idea; it is the idea that starts the money.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10216, 71259, '', 23, 'If you do not express your own original ideas, if you do not listen to your own being, you will have betrayed yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:54'),
(10217, 63232, '', 23, 'There is no innovation and creativity without failure. Period. - Brené Brown.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10218, 2491, '', 23, 'If you have always done it that way, it is probably wrong.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10219, 62858, '', 23, 'Logic will get you from A to B. Imagination will take you everywhere.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10220, 45687, '', 23, 'Swipe from the best, then adapt.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10221, 92475, '', 23, 'The lightning spark of thought generated in the solitary mind awakens its likeness in another mind.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10222, 99918, '', 23, 'Innovation opportunities do not come with the tempest but with the rustling of the breeze.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10223, 61825, '', 23, 'No idea is so outlandish that it should not be considered.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10224, 17525, '', 23, 'Exploration is the engine that drives innovation. Innovation drives economic growth.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10225, 12382, '', 23, 'It is better to entertain an idea than to take it home to live with you for the rest of your life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10226, 27984, '', 23, 'The most powerful factors in the world are clear ideas in the minds of energetic men of good will.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10227, 42939, '', 23, 'For good ideas and true innovation, you need human interaction, conflict, argument, debate.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10228, 10556, '', 23, 'Creative thinking inspires ideaas. Ideas inspire change.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10229, 7990, '', 23, 'No intelligent idea can gain general acceptance unless some stupidity is mixed in with it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10230, 40375, '', 23, 'There are some ideas so wrong that only a very intelligent person could believe in them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10231, 73199, '', 23, 'The only sure weapon against bad ideas is better ideas.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10232, 57664, '', 23, 'The best ideas come as jokes. Make your thinking as funny as possible.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10233, 50573, '', 23, 'Ideas are easy. It\'s the execution of ideas that really seperates the sheep from the goats.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10234, 47987, '', 23, 'No grand idea was ever born in a conference, but a lot of foolish ideas have died there.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10235, 60638, '', 23, 'Nothing imagined too long can be perfect in a worldly way.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10236, 55119, '', 23, 'Imagination is more important than knowledge.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10237, 68075, '', 23, 'The creative person is both more primitive and more cultivated, a lot madder and a lot saner, than the average person.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10238, 45552, '', 23, 'The function of the imagination is not to make strange things settled, so much as to make settled things strange.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10239, 66176, '', 23, 'It\'s not what you look at that matters, it\'s what you see.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10240, 42386, '', 23, 'Nothing encourages creativity like the chance to fall flat on one\'s face.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10241, 53502, '', 23, 'Fiction reveals truths that reality obscures.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10242, 31888, '', 23, 'Imagination continually frustrates tradition, that is it\'s function.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10243, 64944, '', 23, 'He who has imagination without learning has wings but no feet.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10244, 61007, '', 23, 'Imagination is the air of mind.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10245, 91211, '', 23, 'The human race is governed by it\'s imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10246, 62806, '', 23, 'There is no healthier drug than creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10247, 60161, '', 23, 'You can’t wait for inspiration, you have to go after it with a club.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10248, 18993, '', 23, 'Start where you are. Use what you have. Do what you can.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10249, 8556, '', 23, 'You never have to change anything you got up in the middle of the night to write.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10250, 15982, '', 23, 'Creativity is intelligence having fun.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10251, 90951, '', 23, 'There is no such thing as a new idea. We simply take a lot of old ideas and put them into a sort of mental kaleidoscope.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10252, 70247, '', 23, 'Inspiration exists, but it has to find you working.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10253, 92762, '', 23, 'Making the simple complicated is commonplace. Making the complicated simple, awesomely simple, that’s creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10254, 18359, '', 23, 'Our species is the only creative species, and it has only one creative instrument, the individual mind and spirit of man. Nothing was ever created by two men.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10255, 84367, '', 23, 'Creativity is a way of living life, no matter our vocation or how we earn our living. Creativity is not limited to the arts, or having some kind of important career.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10256, 17573, '', 23, 'That’s the great secret of creativity. You treat ideas like cats: you make them follow you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10257, 99952, '', 23, 'What keeps life fascinating is the constant creativity of the soul.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10258, 23696, '', 23, 'The criminal is the creative artist; the detective only the critic.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10259, 44790, '', 23, 'All profound distraction opens certain doors. You have to allow yourself to be distracted when you are unable to concentrate.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10260, 71087, '', 23, 'I’ve always felt that the best whips and chains are in the mind. With a little creativity, the physical ones are hardly necessary.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10261, 56343, '', 23, 'When learning is purposeful, creativity blossoms. When creativity blossoms, thinking emanates. When thinking emanates, knowledge is fully lit. When knowledge is lit, economy flourishes.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10262, 28211, '', 23, 'Routine kills creative thought.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10263, 54027, '', 23, 'The only unique contribution that we will ever make in this world will be born of our creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10264, 80870, '', 23, 'Those who do not want to imitate anything, produce nothing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10265, 26074, '', 23, 'Leap, and the net will appear.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10266, 21829, '', 23, 'Without art, the crudeness of reality would make the world unbearable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10267, 9969, '', 23, 'Sometimes when you innovate, you make mistakes. It is best to admit them quickly and get on with improving your other innovations.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10268, 24133, '', 23, 'Creativity requires the courage to let go of certainties.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10269, 93782, '', 23, 'Art is parasitic on life, just as criticism is parasitic on art.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10270, 11667, '', 23, 'The waking mind is the least serviceable in the arts.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10271, 25860, '', 23, 'Advertising is the greatest art form of the 20th century.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10272, 68378, '', 23, 'What art offers is space - a certain breathing room for the spirit.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10273, 5852, '', 23, 'To send light into the darkness of men\'s hearts - such is the duty of the artist.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10274, 8961, '', 23, 'Rules and models destroy genius and art.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10275, 35282, '', 23, 'Immature artists imitate. Mature artists steal.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10276, 89501, '', 23, 'Art is magic delivered from the lie of being truth.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10277, 99196, '', 23, 'All art is autobiographical. The pearl is the oyster\'s autobiography.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10278, 93599, '', 23, 'The task of art today is to bring chaos into order.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10279, 30216, '', 23, 'Art is either plagiarism or revolution.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10280, 76793, '', 23, 'The artist belongs to his work, not the work to the artist.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10281, 68089, '', 23, 'Art is the daughter of freedom.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10282, 49864, '', 23, 'Every artist writes his own autobiography.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10283, 2177, '', 23, 'Great art picks up where nature ends.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10284, 6676, '', 23, 'The perfection of art is to conceal art.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10285, 65303, '', 23, 'Art, in itself, is an attempt to bring order out of chaos.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10286, 86464, '', 23, 'Art is a revolt against fate. All art is a revolt against man\'s fate.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10287, 95215, '', 23, 'Art is the stored honey of the human soul, gathered on wings of misery and travail.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
(10288, 46506, '', 23, 'There\'s no artist of any value who doesn\'t doubt what they\'re doing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:38:03', '2023-01-27 00:31:55'),
