(10509, 70023, '', 13, 'Make voyages. Attempt them. There\'s nothing else more important.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:57'),
(10510, 80938, '', 13, 'Once you have traveled, the voyage never ends, but is played out over and over again in the quietest chambers. The mind can never break off from the journey.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:57'),
