(10520, 8691, '', 13, 'Travel is the only context in which some people ever look around. If we spent half the energy looking at our own neighborhoods, we\'d probably learn twice as much.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:58'),
(10521, 77353, '', 13, 'Too often travel, instead of broadening the mind, merely lengthens the conversation ', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:58'),
