(10686, 97637, '', 13, 'Journeys are the midwives of thought. Few places are more conducive to internal conversations than moving planes, ships or trains.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10687, 44678, '', 13, 'People travel to faraway places to watch, in fascination, the kind of people they ignore at home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10688, 38911, '', 13, 'How you live your life is up to you. You have to go out and grab the world by the horns. Rope it before it ties you down and decides for you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10689, 10469, '', 13, 'Stuff your eyes with wonder, live as if you’d drop dead in ten seconds. See the world. It’s more fantastic than any dream made or paid for in factories.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10690, 3535, '', 13, 'Focus on the journey, not the destination. Joy is found not in finishing an activity but in doing it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10691, 11007, '', 13, 'He who knows no foreign languages knows nothing of his own.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10692, 67332, '', 13, 'Broad, wholesome, charitable views of men and things cannot be acquired by vegetating in one little corner of the earth all of one’s lifetime.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10693, 29527, '', 13, 'Traveling outgrows its motives. It soon proves sufficient in itself. You think you are making a trip, but soon it is making you – or unmaking you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10694, 59452, '', 13, 'Whenever you go on a trip to visit foreign lands or distant places, remember that they are all someone’s home and backyard.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10695, 38739, '', 13, 'The journey is part of the experience – an expression of the seriousness of one’s intent. One doesn’t take the A train to Mecca.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10696, 31826, '', 13, 'To get away from one’s working environment is, in a sense, to get away from one’s self; and this is often the chief advantage of travel and change.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10697, 33385, '', 13, 'We must go beyond textbooks, go out into the bypaths and untrodden depths of the wilderness and tell the world the glories of our journey.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10698, 77617, '', 13, 'Only by going alone in silence, can one truly get into the heart of the wilderness. All other travel is mere dust and hotels and baggage and chatter.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10699, 59932, '', 13, 'The more I traveled the more I realized that fear makes strangers of people who should be friends.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10700, 31285, '', 13, 'Noone else can travel that road for you, You must travel it for yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10701, 93427, '', 13, 'Great things are done when men and mountains meet.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10702, 69793, '', 13, 'A child on a farm sees a plane fly overhead and dreams of a faraway place. A traveler on the plane sees the farmhouse…and thinks of home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10703, 89561, '', 13, 'All travel has its advantages. If the passenger visits better countries, he may learn to improve his own. And if fortune carries him to worse, he may learn to enjoy it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10704, 30550, '', 13, 'Remember that a foreign country is not designed to make you comfortable. It is designed to make its own people comfortable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10705, 21420, '', 13, 'The first condition of understanding a foreign country is to smell it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10706, 6085, '', 13, 'When overseas you learn more about your own country, than you do the place you’re visiting.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10707, 80256, '', 13, 'Don’t tell me the sky’s the limit when there are footprints on the moon.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10708, 92495, '', 13, 'The man who goes alone can start today; but he who travels with another must wait till that other is ready.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10709, 4214, '', 13, 'No place is ever as bad as they tell you it’s going to be.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:31:59'),
(10710, 83890, '', 13, 'If you reject the food, ignore the customs, fear the religion and avoid the people, you might better stay at home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10711, 60847, '', 13, 'We\'re all travellers, just travelling through this world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10712, 90654, '', 13, 'A wise traveller never despises his own country.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10713, 60945, '', 13, 'A man travels the world over in search of what he needs, and returns home to find it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10714, 58497, '', 13, 'A traveller to distant places should make no enemies. - Nigerian Proverb.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10715, 52644, '', 13, 'Go out into the world. Take trains and planes to places you haven\'t been before.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10716, 69248, '', 13, 'Travel. As much as you can, as far as you can, as long as you can. Life\'s not meant to be fixed in one place.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10717, 83785, '', 13, 'A wise man travels to discover himself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10718, 36684, '', 13, 'Go find yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10719, 6062, '', 13, 'A good traveller has no fixed plans.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10720, 43273, '', 13, 'Travel brings power and love back to your life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10721, 14102, '', 13, 'Some journeys can only be travelled alone.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10722, 25999, '', 13, 'Wander without purpose or reason.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10723, 5925, '', 13, 'Travel is still the intense mode of learning.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10724, 81094, '', 13, 'Life is meant for spectacular adventures. Let your feet wander, your eyes marvel, and your soul ignite.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10725, 97917, '', 13, 'Sometimes, a break from your routine is the very thing you need.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10726, 92734, '', 13, 'Life is not measured by the number of breaths we take, but by the moments and places that take our breath away.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10727, 88844, '', 13, 'If you don\'t get out of the box you were raised in, you won\'t understand how much bigger the world is.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10728, 43038, '', 13, 'In the world through which you travel. You are endlessly creating yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10729, 71220, '', 13, 'It\'s time for a new adventure.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10730, 48292, '', 13, 'Good things come to those who book flights.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10731, 17114, '', 13, 'If happiness is the goal - and it should be, then adventures should be a priority.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10732, 522, '', 13, 'Not until we are lost do we begin to find ourselves.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10733, 80777, '', 13, 'Travelling leaves you speechless, then turns you into a storyteller.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10734, 16799, '', 13, 'To move, to breathe, to fly, to float, to roam the roads of lands remote, to travel is to live.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10735, 75499, '', 13, 'Chase adventures.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10736, 97682, '', 13, 'Don\'t be the person who is too busy when you\'re young and too tired when you\'re old.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10737, 32651, '', 13, 'Solo travel not only pushes you out of your comfort zone. It also pushes you out of the zone of others\' expectations.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10738, 48853, '', 13, 'There\'s no time to be bored in a world as beautiful as this.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10739, 66898, '', 13, 'Life goal: Travel to as many places as possible.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10740, 44254, '', 13, 'A rainy day at the beach is better than a sunny day at the office.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10741, 67017, '', 13, 'The world is big, get a good look at it before it gets dark.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10742, 63852, '', 13, 'What a glorious greeting the sun gives the mountains.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10743, 24729, '', 13, 'Put down the map and get wonderfully lost.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10744, 70487, '', 13, 'Travel is not reward for working, it\'s education for living.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10745, 35212, '', 13, 'Travel is good for the soul; experiences are necessary for growth.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10746, 88112, '', 13, 'Don\'t let them make you walk, when you want to fly.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10747, 96334, '', 13, 'The best view comes after the hardest climb.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10748, 44513, '', 13, 'Somewhere on your journey don\'t forget to turn around and enjoy the view.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10749, 70463, '', 13, 'When one door closes, pack your bags and go where there are no doors.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10750, 20980, '', 13, 'Travel to regroup, reinvent yourself, be the best you can be, find joy in the ordinary and peace in exploring.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10751, 79183, '', 13, 'The human spirit needs places where nature has not been rearranged by the hand of man.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10752, 9663, '', 13, 'Travel. Because money returns, time doesn\'t.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10753, 23568, '', 13, 'If you don\'t go on wild adventures when you\'re young, you\'ll have nothing to smile about when you\'re old.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10754, 79260, '', 13, 'No reason to stay, is a good reason to go.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10755, 86241, '', 13, 'Wander often, wonder always.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10756, 22882, '', 13, 'Travel is not really about leaving our homes, but leaving our habits.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10757, 2682, '', 13, 'To most people, sky is the limit. To those who love aviation, the sky is home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10758, 97055, '', 13, 'You don\'t need magic to disappear, all you need is a destination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10759, 67285, '', 13, 'Travelling solo means getting to know the real you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10760, 45669, '', 13, 'If you are waiting for someone to travel with you... you may end up waiting a life time!', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10761, 29858, '', 13, 'We travel because distance and differences are the secret tonic of creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10762, 84571, '', 13, 'Aspire not to have more, but to be more.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10763, 60669, '', 13, 'If you want to go fast, go alone. If you want to go far, go together.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10764, 96980, '', 13, 'Let\'s travel together and get lost in beautiful places.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10765, 71877, '', 13, 'One day you will be at the place you always wanted to be.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10766, 12463, '', 13, 'Explore and discover.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10767, 43229, '', 13, 'Knowledge is an unending adventure at the edge of uncertainity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10768, 98098, '', 13, 'So much world. So little time.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10769, 88753, '', 13, 'Travel only with the equals or the better, if there are none, travel alone.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10770, 66641, '', 13, 'The sky was never the limit.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10771, 31194, '', 13, 'Difficult roads often leads to beautiful destinations.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10772, 33030, '', 13, 'Let no one keep you from your journey.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10773, 96722, '', 13, 'Exploration is really the essence of the human spirit.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10774, 86942, '', 13, 'Free your mind, surf when the sun goes down.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10775, 67339, '', 13, 'Unplanned moments are always better than planned ones.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10776, 31936, '', 13, 'See the world. It\'s more fantastic than any dream.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10777, 54996, '', 13, 'Time is short. Take time to travel.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10778, 98833, '', 13, 'Be grateful for every day spent in a different country.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10779, 25961, '', 13, 'The best traveller is one without a camera.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10780, 48885, '', 13, 'Wherever you go, go with all your heart.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10781, 83219, '', 13, 'Don\'t be a tourist, be a traveller.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10782, 32829, '', 13, 'To travel is to embrace the unknown.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:00'),
(10783, 22370, '', 13, 'Don\'t just tell your children about the world show them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10784, 42501, '', 13, 'You must go on adventures to find out where you truly belong.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10785, 42031, '', 13, 'Embrace the detours.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10786, 86480, '', 13, 'The best education you will ever receive is through travel.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10787, 3057, '', 13, 'Travel is better with friends.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10788, 69682, '', 13, 'If you never go, you\'ll never know.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10789, 21165, '', 13, 'Travel creates memories that last a lifetime.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10790, 36461, '', 13, 'Unplanned trips are the best.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10791, 93040, '', 13, 'Spend your life arriving each evening in a new city.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10792, 75771, '', 13, 'Happiness is a car, the open road, and best friends.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10793, 66551, '', 13, 'Never let a stumble in the road be the end of the journey.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10794, 9249, '', 13, 'Some beautiful paths can\'t be discovered without getting lost.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10795, 26243, '', 13, 'Let\'s go travel. Plan your trip through the best cities.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10796, 10314, '', 13, 'Do not follow where the path may lead. Go instead where there is no path and leave a trail.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10797, 30812, '', 13, 'Travel in your own backyard.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10798, 29659, '', 13, 'Never stop exploring.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10799, 45339, '', 13, 'Travel is the only way to truly understand and appreciate the world we live in.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10800, 26217, '', 13, 'The beauty of the world lies in the diversity of its people.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10801, 52794, '', 13, 'The journey is the reward. The destination is just the excuse to go.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10802, 13681, '', 13, 'Voyaging is not just about the destination, it\'s about the journey and all the experiences and lessons learned along the way.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10803, 84160, '', 13, 'The purpose of life is to live it, to taste experience to the utmost, to reach out eagerly and without fear for newer and richer experience.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10804, 71467, '', 13, 'Voyaging is about the people you meet and the things you create with them, not the places you go.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10805, 93911, '', 13, 'Aim for the sky, but move slowly, enjoying every step along the way.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10806, 35703, '', 13, 'Stay patient and trust your journey.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10807, 79175, '', 13, 'Let your mind start a journey through a strange new world. Leave all thoughts of the world you knew before and let your soul take you where you long to be.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10808, 78356, '', 13, 'Sometimes the longest journey we make is the sixteen inches from our heads to our hearts.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10809, 60391, '', 13, 'A journey is a person in itself; no two are alike. ', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10810, 88511, '', 13, 'When setting out on a journey do not seek advice from someone who never left home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10811, 49285, '', 13, 'To get through the hardest journey we need take only one step at a time, but we must keep on stepping.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10812, 50242, '', 13, 'The only thing that is ultimately real about your journey is the step that you are taking at this moment. That’s all there ever is.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10813, 11267, '', 13, 'One may walk over the highest mountain one step at a time.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10814, 1552, '', 13, 'Sometimes it’s the journey that teaches you a lot about your destination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10815, 91111, '', 13, 'Life is a journey that has a lot of different paths, but any path you choose use it as your destiny.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10816, 45296, '', 13, 'Life is about waking up. It is a journey of discovery and you’ve already bought the ticket and are sitting on the train.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10817, 25845, '', 13, 'Focus on the journey, not on arriving at a certain destination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10818, 96764, '', 13, 'Our life is an endless journey; it is like a broad highway that extends infinitely into the distance.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10819, 88282, '', 13, 'Simplicity is making the journey of this life with just baggage enough.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10820, 35169, '', 13, 'We are travellers on a cosmic journey, stardust, swirling and dancing in the eddies and whirlpools of infinity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10821, 13219, '', 13, 'No one can decide the road that inspires us to kick-start a journey better than the one embarking on the path.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10822, 33234, '', 13, 'We may find others joining our journey, but we have to take the first step alone to reach our destination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01');
INSERT INTO `quotes` (`id`, `order`, `entry_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `author`, `has_notif`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(10823, 41469, '', 13, 'When you set out on a journey and night covers the road, that\'s when you discover the stars.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10824, 16946, '', 13, 'We advance on our journey only when we face our goal, we are confident and believe we are going to succeed.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10825, 11350, '', 13, 'You must remain focused on your journey to greatness.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10826, 80331, '', 13, 'On a hard jungle journey, nothing is so important as having a team you can trust.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10827, 71016, '', 13, 'If all difficulties were known at the outset of a long journey, most of us would never start out at all.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10828, 86627, '', 13, 'Embrace your life journey with gratitude, so that how you travel your path is more important than reaching your ultimate destination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10829, 89025, '', 13, 'Man’s real home is not a house, but the Road and that life itself is a journey to be walked on foot.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10830, 73423, '', 13, 'The soul of a journey is liberty, perfect liberty, to think, feel, do just as one pleases.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10831, 79816, '', 13, 'Accomplishments will prove to be a journey, not a destination. ', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10832, 12094, '', 13, 'Trust yourself, trust the road, trust the weather, and trust your destination! This quarto-trust can create a miraculously successful journey!', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10833, 39983, '', 13, 'The only impossible journey is the one you never begin.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10834, 4099, '', 13, 'The road of life twists and turns and no two directions are ever the same. Yet our lessons come from the journey, not the destination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10835, 19370, '', 13, 'In this journey of life, you will meet people who will make you feel alive!', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10836, 51034, '', 13, 'Winning and losing isn’t everything; sometimes, the journey is just as important as the outcome.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10837, 81674, '', 13, 'Not everyone will understand your journey. That’s okay. You’re here to live your life, not to make everyone understand.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10838, 47897, '', 13, 'Gotta’ take that adventure, in order to understand your journey.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10839, 41236, '', 13, 'There ain’t no journey what don’t change you some.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10840, 46969, '', 13, 'A fresh start is a journey – a journey that requires a plan.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10841, 68092, '', 13, 'Aim for the sky, but move slowly, enjoying every step along the way. It is all those little steps that make the journey complete.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10842, 35321, '', 13, 'We never know the journey another person has walked, so be kind to everyone.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10843, 75711, '', 13, 'You have learned a lot, but there are still lots of learning for you as you journey through life. Never stop learning.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10844, 68275, '', 13, 'Sometimes, reaching out and taking someone’s hand is the beginning of a journey.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10845, 95418, '', 13, 'Life is a journey and it’s about growing and changing and coming to terms with who and what you are, and loving who and what you are.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10846, 61360, '', 13, 'Learn to trust the journey, even when you do not understand it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10847, 78588, '', 13, 'Sometimes life takes you on a journey that changes everything you thought you wanted.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10848, 13674, '', 13, 'The beautiful journey of today can only begin when we learn to let go of yesterday.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10849, 19056, '', 13, 'The journey is yours. Enjoy each and every step.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10850, 82197, '', 13, 'And at the end of the day, there is nothing but the journey. Because destination is pure illusion.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10851, 44914, '', 13, 'A journey taken in vain is not a wasted journey if you have learnt something.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10852, 68275, '', 13, 'It is more important to go slow and gain the lessons you need along the journey then to rush the process and arrive at your destination empty.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10853, 33392, '', 13, 'The journey of every ignorant and obedient society always ends up in the same place: In the desert!', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:40:30', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10854, 87700, '', 31, 'Imagination is more important than knowledge.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10855, 21444, '', 31, 'Imagination is everything. It is the preview of life\'s coming attractions.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10856, 98359, '', 31, 'Those who dream by day are cognizant of many things that escape those who dream only at night.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10857, 24106, '', 31, 'You can\'t depend on your eyes when your imagination is out of focus.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10858, 138, '', 31, 'The man who has no imagination has no wings.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(10859, 98378, '', 31, 'The lunatic, the lover, and the poet, are of imagination all compact.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10860, 5493, '', 31, 'Imagination will often carry us to worlds that never were. But without it we go nowhere.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10861, 88281, '', 31, 'Our truest life is when we are in dreams awake.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10862, 16337, '', 31, 'To invent, you need a good imagination and a pile of junk.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10863, 70242, '', 31, 'Imagination rules the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10864, 118, '', 31, 'All men who have achieved great things have been great dreamers.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(10865, 81858, '', 31, 'Imagination and fiction make up more than three quarters of our real life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10866, 3606, '', 31, 'Imagine for yourself a character, a model personality, whose example you determine to follow, in private as well as in public.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10867, 59107, '', 31, 'People who lean on logic and philosophy and rational exposition end by starving the best part of the mind.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10868, 3854, '', 31, 'There is a boundary to men\'s passions when they act from feelings but none when they are under the influence of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10869, 773, '', 31, 'Happiness is not an ideal of reason, but of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10870, 53498, '', 31, 'Trust that little voice in your head that says \'Wouldn\'t it be interesting if...\' And then do it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10871, 35090, '', 31, 'Imagination grows by exercise, and contrary to common belief, is more powerful in the mature than in the young.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10872, 2679, '', 31, 'One is never fortunate or as unfortunate as one imagines.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10873, 158, '', 31, 'They are ill discoverers that think there is no land, when they can see nothing but sea.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(10874, 3561, '', 31, 'Fiction reveals truths that reality obscures.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10875, 91091, '', 31, 'Solitude is as needful to the imagination as society is wholesome for the character.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10876, 7523, '', 31, 'Imagination is at the root of much that passes for love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10877, 45601, '', 31, 'The imagination is man\'s power over nature.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10878, 50992, '', 31, 'What we imagine is order is merely the prevailing form of chaos.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10879, 73961, '', 31, 'You need imagination in order to imagine a future that doesn\'t exist.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10880, 25361, '', 31, 'The most imaginative people are the most credulous, for them everything is possible.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10881, 64786, '', 31, 'There are no shortcuts in life - only those we imagine.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10882, 128, '', 31, 'The true sign of intelligence is not knowledge but imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(10883, 23644, '', 31, 'Logic will get you from A to B. Imagination will take you everywhere.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10884, 91676, '', 31, 'To raise new questions, new possibilities, to regard old problems from a new angle, requires creative imagination and marks real advance in science.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10885, 51134, '', 31, 'The moment a person forms a theory, his imagination sees in every object only the traits which favor that theory.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10886, 82073, '', 31, 'Reason is the natural order of truth but imagination is the organ of meaning.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10887, 24181, '', 31, 'This world is but a canvas to our imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10888, 60163, '', 31, 'Imagination was given to man to compensate him for what he is not a sense of humor to console him for what he is.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10889, 1265, '', 31, 'The imagination imitates. It is the critical spirit that creates.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10890, 30335, '', 31, 'There are no great limits to growth because there are no limits of human intelligence, imagination, and wonder.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10891, 96784, '', 31, 'Love is the triumph of imagination over intelligence.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10892, 59711, '', 31, 'Reality leaves a lot to the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10893, 1612, '', 31, 'Science does not know its debt to imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10894, 73358, '', 31, 'Love is a canvas furnished by nature and embroidered by imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10895, 64362, '', 31, 'It is usually the imagination that is wounded first, rather than the heart it being much more sensitive.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10896, 43195, '', 31, 'Generally speaking, a howling wilderness does not howl: it is the imagination of the traveler that does the howling.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:01'),
(10897, 61190, '', 31, 'Imagination is the beginning of creation. You imagine what you desire, you will what you imagine and at last you create what you will.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10898, 69869, '', 31, 'There are lots of people who mistake their imagination for their memory.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10899, 51458, '', 31, 'We are more often frightened than hurt and we suffer more from imagination than from reality.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10900, 22296, '', 31, 'Imagination is the key to my lyrics. The rest is painted with a little science fiction.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10901, 49406, '', 31, 'Disneyland will never be completed. It will continue to grow as long as there is imagination left in the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10902, 48943, '', 31, 'A good teacher can inspire hope, ignite the imagination, and instill a love of learning.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10903, 17128, '', 31, 'There are many ways to be free. One of them is to transcend reality by imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10904, 78909, '', 31, 'Few people have the imagination for reality.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10905, 78034, '', 31, 'We cast away priceless time in dreams, born of imagination, fed upon illusion, and put to death by reality.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10906, 2313, '', 31, 'The only limit to your impact is your imagination and commitment.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10907, 16022, '', 31, 'Cowardice... is almost always simply a lack of ability to suspend functioning of the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10908, 29181, '', 31, 'The nose of a mob is its imagination. By this, at any time, it can be quietly led.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10909, 94850, '', 31, 'Imagination is the true magic carpet.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10910, 78731, '', 31, 'Falling in love consists merely in uncorking the imagination and bottling the common sense.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10911, 90641, '', 31, 'Nothing is more fearful than imagination without taste.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10912, 42040, '', 31, 'All the works of man have their origin in creative fantasy. What right have we then to depreciate imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10913, 2532, '', 31, 'Aptitude found in the understanding and is often inherited. Genius coming from reason and imagination, rarely.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10914, 69472, '', 31, 'The power of imagination makes us infinite.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10915, 96550, '', 31, 'Life is only a dream and we are the imagination of ourselves.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10916, 50918, '', 31, 'The soul without imagination is what an observatory would be without a telescope.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10917, 49448, '', 31, 'Neither a lofty degree of intelligence nor imagination nor both together go to the making of genius. Love, love, love, that is the soul of genius.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10918, 36042, '', 31, 'Do not quench your inspiration and your imagination do not become the slave of your model.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10919, 87267, '', 31, 'I am certain of nothing but the holiness of the heart\'s affections, and the truth of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10920, 963, '', 31, 'Happiness is ideal, it is the work of the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10921, 73727, '', 31, 'The human race is governed by its imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10922, 58076, '', 31, 'Imagination is the real and eternal world of which this vegetable universe is but a faint shadow.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10923, 34290, '', 31, 'A lady\'s imagination is very rapid it jumps from admiration to love, from love to matrimony in a moment.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10924, 44558, '', 31, 'Without this playing with fantasy no creative work has ever yet come to birth. The debt we owe to the play of the imagination is incalculable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10925, 49071, '', 31, 'Imagination was given to man to compensate him for what he isn\'t. A sense of humor was provided to console him for what he is.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10926, 52839, '', 31, 'The use of travelling is to regulate imagination by reality, and instead of thinking how things may be, to see them as they are.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10927, 39090, '', 31, 'Imagination is a poor matter when it has to part company with understanding.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10928, 19535, '', 31, 'Liberty: One of Imagination\'s most precious possessions.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10929, 79704, '', 31, 'Knowledge is a polite word for dead but not buried imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10930, 49007, '', 31, 'Our thoughts and imagination are the only real limits to our possibilities.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10931, 87352, '', 31, 'Imagination is the eye of the soul.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10932, 16287, '', 31, 'Imagination decides everything.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10933, 79209, '', 31, 'You have all the reason in the world to achieve your grandest dreams. Imagination plus innovation equals realization.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10934, 31393, '', 31, 'We especially need imagination in science. It is not all mathematics, nor all logic, but it is somewhat beauty and poetry.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10935, 96041, '', 31, 'Were it not for imagination a man would be as happy in arms of a chambermaid as of a duchess.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10936, 22199, '', 31, 'An idea is salvation by imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10937, 82477, '', 31, 'To treat your facts with imagination is one thing, to imagine your facts is another.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10938, 22904, '', 31, 'The world of reality has its limits the world of imagination is boundless.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10939, 67774, '', 31, 'For strange effects and extraordinary combinations we must go to life itself, which is always far more daring than any effort of the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10940, 75920, '', 31, 'Having imagination it takes you an hour to write a paragraph that if you were unimaginative would take you only a minute.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10941, 46480, '', 31, 'Imagination can picture no fairer happiness than to continue living for art.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10942, 47846, '', 31, 'Fantasy mirrors desire. Imagination reshapes it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10943, 91412, '', 31, 'Imagination is a monastery and you are its monk.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10944, 37455, '', 31, 'What the imagination seizes as beauty must be truth.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10945, 20192, '', 31, 'The scientific imagination always restrains itself within the limits of probability.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10946, 4980, '', 31, 'Memories, imagination, old sentiments, and associations are more readily reached through the sense of smell than through any other channel.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10947, 17639, '', 31, 'The degree in which a poet\'s imagination dominates reality is, in the end, the exact measure of his importance and dignity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10948, 70994, '', 31, 'Every great advance in science has issued from a new audacity of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10949, 90038, '', 31, 'What distinguishes a great artist from a weak one is first their sensibility and tenderness second, their imagination, and third, their industry.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10950, 34990, '', 31, 'He who has imagination without learning has wings but no feet.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10951, 61774, '', 31, 'Taste refers to the past, imagination to the future.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10952, 17836, '', 31, 'Imagination has rules, but we can only guess what they are.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10953, 44461, '', 31, 'Skill without imagination is craftsmanship and gives us many useful objects such as wickerwork picnic baskets. Imagination without skill gives us modern art.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10954, 4837, '', 31, 'No amount of skillful invention can replace the essential element of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10955, 98889, '', 31, 'He is the true enchanter, whose spell operates, not upon the senses, but upon the imagination and the heart.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10956, 15697, '', 31, 'Censorship is never over for those who have experienced it. It is a brand on the imagination that affects the individual who has suffered it, forever.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10957, 63841, '', 31, 'Imagination is the highest kite one can fly.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10958, 11545, '', 31, 'Where there is no imagination there is no horror.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10959, 35074, '', 31, 'The public has an appetite for anything about imagination - anything that is as far away from reality as is creatively possible.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10960, 45070, '', 31, 'True change takes place in the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10961, 69994, '', 31, 'Classical plays require more imagination and more general training to be able to do. ', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10962, 93468, '', 31, 'Belief in the supernatural reflects a failure of the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10963, 51675, '', 31, 'When the imagination and will power are in conflict, are antagonistic, it is always the imagination which wins, without any exception.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10964, 52018, '', 31, 'The level of our success is limited only by our imagination and no act of kindness, however small, is ever wasted.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10965, 39853, '', 31, 'The great instrument of moral good is the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10966, 61487, '', 31, 'Hope lies in dreams, in imagination, and in the courage of those who dare to make dreams into reality.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10967, 35735, '', 31, 'Reason respects the differences, and imagination the similitudes of things.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10968, 13968, '', 31, 'Uttering a word is like striking a note on the keyboard of the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10969, 9239, '', 31, 'Panic is a sudden desertion of us, and a going over to the enemy of our imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10970, 97066, '', 31, 'When you start to develop your powers of empathy and imagination, the whole world opens up to you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10971, 76427, '', 31, 'The realities of the world seldom measure up to the sublime designs of human imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10972, 87243, '', 31, 'My imagination makes me human and makes me a fool it gives me all the world, and exiles me from it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10973, 10378, '', 31, 'What\'s cool is when you\'re able to give your audience imagination and you don\'t have to cage them in like animals.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10974, 31217, '', 31, 'Children do not give up their innate imagination, curiosity, dreaminess easily. You have to love them to get them to do that.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:02'),
(10975, 89697, '', 31, 'Life is possible only by the deficiencies of our imagination and memory.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10976, 10682, '', 31, 'Reason clears and plants the wilderness of the imagination to harvest the wheat of art.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10977, 83296, '', 31, 'Man lives by imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10978, 48429, '', 31, 'Belief is nothing but a more vivid, lively, forcible, firm, steady conception of an object, than what the imagination alone is ever able to attain.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10979, 81555, '', 31, 'Imagination creates reality.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10980, 8230, '', 31, 'In the world of words, the imagination is one of the forces of nature.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10981, 77793, '', 31, 'You will recognize your own path when you come upon it, because you will suddenly have all the energy and imagination you will ever need.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10982, 68919, '', 31, 'Our imagination is the only limit to what we can hope to have in the future.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10983, 960, '', 31, 'Imagination, the supreme delight of the immortal and the immature, should be limited. In order to enjoy life, we should not enjoy it too much.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10984, 13371, '', 31, 'A writer should have the precision of a poet and the imagination of a scientist.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10985, 64472, '', 31, 'Works of imagination should be written in very plain language the more purely imaginative they are the more necessary it is to be plain.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10986, 62241, '', 31, 'Only in men\'s imagination does every truth find an effective and undeniable existence. Imagination, not invention, is the supreme master of art as of life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10987, 62774, '', 31, 'If the reporter has killed our imagination with his truth, he threatens our life with his lies.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10988, 14679, '', 31, 'It takes no imagination to live within your means.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10989, 75977, '', 31, 'One longs for a director with a sense of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10990, 85227, '', 31, 'The opportunities of man are limited only by his imagination. ', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10991, 64828, '', 31, 'Imagination is the wide-open eye which leads us always to see truth more vividly.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10992, 25505, '', 31, 'People write memoirs because they lack the imagination to make things up.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10993, 62785, '', 31, 'Imagination... its limits are only those of the mind itself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10994, 32383, '', 31, 'Fools act on imagination without knowledge, pedants act on knowledge without imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10995, 15098, '', 31, 'One of the virtues of being very young is that you don\'t let the facts get in the way of your imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10996, 33157, '', 31, 'As great scientists have said and as all children know, it is above all by the imagination that we achieve perception, and compassion, and hope.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10997, 93989, '', 31, 'Imagination has a great deal to do with winning.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10998, 2432, '', 31, 'The source and center of all man\'s creative power... is his power of making images, or the power of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(10999, 10998, '', 31, 'You can understand nothing about art, particularly modern art, if you do not understand that imagination is a value in itself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11000, 22205, '', 31, 'The past is really almost as much a work of the imagination as the future.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11001, 47942, '', 31, 'Put off your imagination, as you put off your overcoat, when you enter the laboratory. Put it on again, as you put on your overcoat, when you leave.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11002, 59107, '', 31, 'Today the function of the artist is to bring imagination to science and science to imagination, where they meet, in the myth.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11003, 15127, '', 31, 'The imagination is part of the arsenal that actors draw from.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11004, 31773, '', 31, 'Obviously the imagination is fueled by emotions beyond the control of the conscious mind.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11005, 23242, '', 31, 'The English language is nobody\'s special property. It is the property of the imagination: it is the property of the language itself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11006, 50331, '', 31, 'It would be a bitter cosmic joke if we destroy ourselves due to atrophy of the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11007, 40238, '', 31, 'The most dire disaster in love is the death of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11008, 58962, '', 31, 'There is only one admirable form of the imagination: the imagination that is so intense that it creates a new reality, that it makes things happen.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11009, 39891, '', 31, 'There is hope in dreams, imagination, and in the courage of those who wish to make those dreams a reality.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11010, 17542, '', 31, 'Dr. Einstein was not successful in school, but he found something in the air from his own imagination and his own brain power, and look what he did.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11011, 56736, '', 31, 'One travels to run away from routine, that dreadful routine that kills all imagination and all our capacity for enthusiasm.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11012, 21543, '', 31, 'Without imagination we can go nowhere. And imagination is not restricted to the arts. Every scientist who has been a success has had to imagine.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11013, 75631, '', 31, 'Imagination is the air of mind.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11014, 52774, '', 31, 'It\'s through the small things that we develop our moral imagination, so that we can understand the sufferings of others.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11015, 75842, '', 31, 'Imagination is not the exclusive appanage of artists, but belongs in varying degrees to all men.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11016, 82615, '', 31, 'Our imagination just needs space. It\'s all it needs, that moment where you just sort of stare into the distance where your brain gets to sort of somehow rise up.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11017, 82940, '', 31, 'One way we can enliven the imagination is to push it toward the illogical. We\'re not scientists. We don\'t always have to make the logical, reasonable leap.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11018, 3115, '', 31, 'There must be room for the imagination to exercise its powers we must conceive and apprehend a thousand things which we do not actually witness.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11019, 84655, '', 31, 'There can be no passion, and by consequence no love, where there is not imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11020, 59676, '', 31, 'There\'s just so many great stories in the past that you can know a little bit about, but you can\'t know it all, and that\'s where imagination can work.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11021, 58483, '', 31, 'When something is such a creative medium as the web, the limits to it are our imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11022, 41026, '', 31, 'Use your imagination, and you\'ll see that even the most narrow, humdrum lives are infinite in scope if you examine them with enough care.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11023, 8077, '', 31, 'Vulgarity begins when imagination succumbs to the explicit.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11024, 40125, '', 31, 'Literary imagination is an aesthetic object offered by a writer to a lover of books.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11025, 34360, '', 31, 'We especially need imagination in science.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11026, 84174, '', 31, 'Reality is how we interpret it. Imagination and volition play a part in that interpretation. Which means that all reality is to some extent a fiction.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11027, 31194, '', 31, 'Never forget that the key to the situation lies in the will and not in the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11028, 32404, '', 31, 'Imagination comes of not having things.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11029, 78023, '', 31, 'We forget that what matters begins with the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11030, 42900, '', 31, 'Imagination is as good as many voyages - and how much cheaper!', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11031, 42054, '', 31, 'Only in your imagination can you revise.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11032, 79706, '', 31, 'You have to just go with your imagination, where your instinct takes you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11033, 79096, '', 31, 'A place makes a deep impression on you when you\'re young. It lives with you. It\'s like your childhood. It fertilises the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11034, 90911, '', 31, 'We also maintain - again with perfect truth - that mystery is more than half of beauty, the element of strangeness that stirs the senses through the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11035, 94471, '', 31, 'The thing about imagination is that by the very act of putting it down, there must be some truth in one\'s own imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11036, 33004, '', 31, 'Imagination needs to be fed.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11037, 98682, '', 31, 'The artist must bow to the monster of his own imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11038, 89102, '', 31, 'Sooner or later you must move down an unknown road that leads beyond the range of the imagination, and the only certainty is that the trip has to be made.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11039, 86635, '', 31, 'You never quite know what\'s going to strike your imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11040, 68627, '', 31, 'To think, and to feel, constitute the two grand divisions of men of genius - the men of reasoning and the men of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:03'),
(11041, 99450, '', 31, 'Writing poetry is the hard manual labor of the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11042, 45931, '', 31, 'He brought imagination to the story of the Creation.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11043, 8117, '', 31, 'What\'s in front of you is a whole world of experiences beyond your imagination. Put yourself, and your growth and development, first.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11044, 94219, '', 31, 'Life is not so bad if you have plenty of luck, a good physique, and not too much imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11045, 49861, '', 31, 'Technology, like art, is a soaring exercise of the human imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11046, 67540, '', 31, '\nNothing too long imagined can be perfect in a worldly way.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11047, 23291, '', 31, 'The function of the imagination is not to make strange things settled, so much as to make settled things strange.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11048, 11727, '', 31, 'It\'s not what you look at that matters, it\'s what you see.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11049, 98564, '', 31, 'Imagination continually frustrates tradition, that is its function.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11050, 80032, '', 31, 'These are the gloomy comparisons of a disturbed imagination; the melancholy madness of poetry, without inspiration.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11051, 41846, '', 31, 'Imagination governs the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11052, 26931, '', 31, 'Anyone who lives within their means suffers from a lack of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11053, 34028, '', 31, 'Think left and think right and think low and think high. Oh, the things you can think up if only you try!', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11054, 23282, '', 31, 'Every thing you can imagine is real.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11055, 56151, '', 31, 'Laughter is timeless. Imagination has no age. And dreams are forever.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11056, 63320, '', 31, 'Stories of imagination tend to upset those without one.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11057, 98819, '', 31, 'If you don\'t imagine, nothing ever happens at all.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11058, 7115, '', 31, 'Each generation imagines itself to be more intelligent than the one that went before it, and wiser than the one that comes after it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11059, 5222, '', 31, 'Bring ideas in and entertain them royally, for one of them may be the king.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11060, 36277, '', 31, 'If you can imagine it, you can achieve it. If you can dream it, you can become it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11061, 148, '', 31, 'Visualise this thing you want to, see it, feel, believe in it. Make your mental blueprint and begin to build.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(11062, 15164, '', 31, 'What we wish, we readily believe, and what we ourselves think, we imagine others think also.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11063, 8057, '', 31, 'What is now proved was once only imagined.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11064, 16047, '', 31, 'Everything that is new or uncommon raises a pleasure in the imagination because it fills the soul with an agreeable surprise.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11065, 97384, '', 31, 'The courage to imagine the otherwise is our greatest resource, adding colour and suspense to all our life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11066, 92631, '', 31, 'True originality consists not in a new manner but in a new vision.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11067, 74971, '', 31, 'Go confidently in the direction of your dreams. Live the life you have imagined.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11068, 91570, '', 31, 'Imagination is the highest form of research.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11069, 3495, '', 31, 'When you can imagine you begin to create and when you begin to create you realise that you can create a world that you prefer to live in.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11070, 66882, '', 31, 'Imagine what a harmonious world it could be if every single person, both young and old shared a little of what he/she is good at doing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11071, 83513, '', 31, 'Imagine is every thing, to know is nothing at all.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11072, 88162, '', 31, 'Imagination and fiction make up more than three-quarters of our real life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11073, 57059, '', 31, 'Our imagination flies, we are its shadow on the earth.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11074, 47425, '', 31, 'It\'s time to start living the life you\'ve imagined.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11075, 88712, '', 31, 'Reality can be beaten with enough imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11076, 56049, '', 31, 'Imagination is the voice of daring.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11077, 40365, '', 31, 'Creativity is putting your imagination to work, and it\'s produced the most extraordinary results in human culture.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11078, 40948, '', 31, 'Imagination was given to man to compensate him for what he is not; a sense of humour to console him for what he is.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11079, 61353, '', 31, 'Imagination is like a muscle, I found out that the more I wrote, the bigger it got. - Philip Jose Farmer.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11080, 72916, '', 31, 'Imagination does not become great until human beings, given the courage and strength, use it to create.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11081, 9503, '', 31, 'Imagination is the beginning of creation. You imagine what you desire, you will what you imagine, and at last, you create what you will.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11082, 69261, '', 31, 'Without leaps of imagination, or dreaming, we lose the excitement of possibilities. Dreaming, after all, is a form of planning', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11083, 61042, '', 31, 'A book is a device to ignite the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11084, 21616, '', 31, 'If you fall in love with the imagination, you understand that it is a free spirit. It will go anywhere, and it can do anything.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11085, 48830, '', 31, 'Imagination is the only weapon in the fight against reality.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11086, 99816, '', 31, 'The world of reality has its limits; the world of imagination is boundless.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11087, 54292, '', 31, 'Writing is a job, a talent, but it’s also the place to go in your head. It is the imaginary friend you drink your tea with in the afternoon.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11088, 90001, '', 31, 'Everything in life is writable about if you have the outgoing guts to do it, and the imagination to improvise.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11089, 31297, '', 31, 'Imagination encircles the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11090, 78068, '', 31, 'My imagination makes me human and makes me a fool; it gives me all the world and exiles me from it. - Ursula K. Le Guin', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11091, 10119, '', 31, 'You are lucky to be one of those people who wishes to build sand castles with words, who is willing to create a place where your imagination can wander.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11092, 41246, '', 31, 'Hate is a lack of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11093, 7699, '', 31, 'Imagination is the uniquely human capacity to envision that which is not.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11094, 22097, '', 31, 'Every good writer needs to go into some deep, quiet place to do work that is fully imagined.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11095, 86095, '', 31, 'You need to be a little bit crazy. Crazy is the price you pay for having an imagination. It’s your superpower. Tapping into the dream. It’s a good thing not a bad thing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11096, 89989, '', 31, 'The thinking mind is best controlled by the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11097, 1526, '', 31, 'A man, to be greatly good, must imagine intensely and comprehensively; he must put himself in the place of another and many others.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11098, 42562, '', 31, 'Adults are bad at remembering how powerful they can be because somewhere along the line, they were shamed for their imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11099, 12975, '', 31, 'Imperfection inspires invention, imagination, and creativity. It stimulates. The more you feel imperfect, the more you feel alive.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11100, 15608, '', 31, 'Your imagination, my dear fellow, is worth more than you imagine.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11101, 49992, '', 31, 'Imagination has brought mankind through the Dark Ages to its present state of civilization.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11102, 25937, '', 31, 'Imagination has given us the steam engine, the telephone, the talking-machine and the automobile, for these things had to be dreamed of before they became realities.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11103, 20465, '', 31, 'The imaginative child will become the imaginative man or woman most apt to create, to invent, and therefore to foster civilisation.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11104, 51080, '', 31, 'The writer must have a good imagination, to begin with, but the imagination has to be muscular, which means it must be exercised in a disciplined way, by writing, failing, succeeding and revising.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11105, 4410, '', 31, 'Writing a novel is not merely going on a shopping expedition across the border to an unreal land: it is hours and years spent in the factories, the streets, the cathedrals of the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11106, 70029, '', 31, 'Individuals make the future, and they do it by imagining that things can be different. ', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11107, 60221, '', 31, 'We all have an obligation to daydream. We have an obligation to imagine.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11108, 58839, '', 31, 'Laughter is timeless, imagination has no age, and dreams are forever.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11109, 68433, '', 31, 'The power of imagination created the illusion that my vision went much farther than the naked eye could actually see. - Nelson Mandela', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:04'),
(11110, 739, '', 31, 'Imagination is usually regarded as a synonym for the unreal... Indeed, the power of imagination makes us infinite.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11111, 99364, '', 31, 'It is a blessed thing to have an imagination that can always make you satisfied, no matter how you are fixed.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11112, 40341, '', 31, 'Limitations live only in our minds. But if we use our imaginations, our possibilities become limitless.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05');
INSERT INTO `quotes` (`id`, `order`, `entry_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `author`, `has_notif`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(11113, 78046, '', 31, 'If you can imagine it, you can achieve it, if you can dream it, you can become it!', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11114, 15531, '', 31, 'Every great advance in science has issued from a new audacity of the imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11115, 46844, '', 31, 'Anybody can have common sense, provided that they have no imagination. - Oscar Wilde', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11116, 93819, '', 31, 'While knowledge is limited, imagination is the beginning of our creativity in life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11117, 87100, '', 31, 'Live out of your imagination, not your history.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11118, 3329, '', 31, 'Nothing limits achievement like small thinking; nothing expands possibilities like unleashed imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11119, 58869, '', 31, 'The best use of imagination is creativity. The worst use of imagination is anxiety.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11120, 75828, '', 31, 'Imagination should be the center of your life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11121, 43486, '', 31, 'A book - a well-composed book - is a magic carpet on which we are wafted to a world that we cannot enter in any other way.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11122, 92736, '', 31, 'The visionary starts with a clean sheet of paper, and re-imagines the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11123, 63320, '', 31, 'The mightiest lever known to the moral world, imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11124, 88218, '', 31, 'What I fear most, I think, is the death of the imagination. - Sylvia Plath.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11125, 29311, '', 31, 'It is the marriage of the soul with nature that makes the intellect fruitful, and gives birth to imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11126, 96665, '', 31, 'To bring anything into your life, imagine that it’s already there.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11127, 49543, '', 31, 'I have always imagined that Paradise will be a kind of library. - Jorge Luis Borges.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11128, 8671, '', 31, 'Do not quench your inspiration and your imagination; do not become the slave of your model.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11129, 93518, '', 31, 'Our imagination is stretched to the utmost, not, as in fiction, to imagine things which are not really there, but just to comprehend those things which \'are\' there.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11130, 72195, '', 31, 'Reason can answer questions, but imagination has to ask them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11131, 40640, '', 31, 'Reading\'s the only thing that allows you to use your imagination. When you watch films it\'s someone else\'s vision, isn\'t it?', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11132, 39539, '', 31, 'I am certain of nothing but the holiness of the heart\'s affections and the truth of the Imagination. - John Keats.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11133, 50002, '', 31, 'Imagination is the golden-eyed monster that never sleeps. It must be fed; it cannot be ignored.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11134, 69050, '', 31, 'It is the divine attribute of the imagination, that it is irrepressible, unconfinable; that when the real world is shut out, it can create a world for itself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11135, 47494, '', 31, 'Imagination should be used, not to escape reality, but to create it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11136, 78758, '', 31, 'While the world of reality has its limits, the world of your imagination is without boundaries.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11137, 48535, '', 31, 'The imagination is the golden pathway to everywhere.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11138, 13371, '', 31, 'I have too much imagination to be a housewife. - Marilyn Monroe.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11139, 98454, '', 31, 'Every child is born blessed with a vivid imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11140, 44654, '', 31, 'The best way to enhance a child\'s imagination is to make them read.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11141, 56932, '', 31, 'My children have been all over the world, and I think it\'s so good for them: expanding their horizons and imagination and seeing how other people live. - Keeley Hawes.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11142, 82753, '', 31, 'It is more important to let a child\'s imagination develop than it is to labor to inculcate in him or her some correct ethical point of view.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11143, 75799, '', 31, 'Since childhood, I\'d been suspected of imagination! - Steve Aylett.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11144, 60996, '', 31, 'While childhood, and while dreams, producing childhood, shall be left, imagination shall not have spread her holy wings totally to fly the earth.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11145, 40228, '', 31, 'It is not enough to simply teach children to read; we have to give them something worth reading. Something that will stretch their imaginations.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11146, 95469, '', 31, 'Children see magic because they look for it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11147, 29072, '', 31, 'When the arts are included, children\'s imaginations are allowed to run wild.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11148, 34122, '', 31, 'We don\'t stop playing because we grow old; we grow old because we stop playing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11149, 43810, '', 31, 'I spent my childhood in an imaginary world - probably because I needed an escape. - Rickey Lee Jones', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11150, 66662, '', 31, 'The difference between childhood and adulthood, Vic had come to believe, was the difference between imagination and resignation. You traded one for the other and lost your way.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11151, 58200, '', 31, 'Childhood, catching our imagination when it is fresh and tender, never lets go of us.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11152, 782, '', 31, 'Imagination is enormously valuable, and children should be encouraged in their imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11153, 26446, '', 31, 'There is more treasure in books than in all the pirates\' loot on Treasure Island.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11154, 86946, '', 31, 'I doubt that the imagination can be suppressed. If you truly eradicated it in a child, he would grow up to be an eggplant.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11155, 59068, '', 31, 'Reason is the natural organ of truth; but imagination is the organ of meaning.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11156, 95127, '', 31, 'While modern music expresses both feelings, thought and imagination, old composers expressed pure feeling.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11157, 58237, '', 31, 'Land looms large in our imagination and civilization in history books, only because sea and savagery are to us less interesting.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11158, 99647, '', 31, 'The more imagination the reader has ... the more he will do for himself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11159, 97513, '', 31, 'Imagination, producing new metaphors or revivifying old, is not the cause of truth, but its condition.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11160, 4543, '', 31, 'To raise new questions, new possibilities, to regard old problems from a new angle requires creative imagination and marks real advances in science.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11161, 82667, '', 31, 'Use your imagination to visualize what may be, not what is. Then set your goals, take action and make what you imagined a reality.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11162, 3508, '', 31, 'Imagination is a very powerful tool. It helps you to achieve your need very quickly. It inspires you more when you think about it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11163, 68644, '', 31, 'Imagine what the most motivated and ambitious person in the world would likely be doing right now. . . Now do that!', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11164, 1740, '', 31, 'Start today by imagining the life you want in the future and take one practice step towards it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11165, 44832, '', 31, 'Imagination is a natural resource. It\'s not a plan, strategy, or process that you can follow or implement. Imagination is a raw material that we can use for whatever we want.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11166, 79628, '', 31, 'Only human beings have the power to imagine a future that could be different from the present.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11167, 77097, '', 31, 'One of the most important ways to boost your results is to imagine how you would feel when your desire manifests.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11168, 90732, '', 31, 'Wonder is triggered by beauty, by new discoveries, and by our imaginations. Children live in a constant state of wonder. They’re always learning, exploring, and discovering new things.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11169, 83777, '', 31, 'Wherever you are, whoever you are, whatever you may be following as an occupation, there is room for you to make yourself more useful by developing and using your \'imagination\'.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11170, 97169, '', 31, 'Our imagination is the workshop of the mind. This is the place where dreams are born, ideas are nourished, and plans are made.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11171, 37855, '', 31, 'Our imagination is a very powerful tool. It\'s something that can help us achieve great things, even if it\'s just in our mind. What you think is what you become eventually.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11172, 50373, '', 31, 'As crazy and weird as the imagination of children can be, we need to encourage that type of thinking. Even participate in imaginary events with our kids.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11173, 36037, '', 31, 'Change begins with fresh eyes, in other words. It begins with an awakened imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11174, 39466, '', 31, 'Since it doesn\'t cost a dime to dream, you\'ll never shortchange yourself when you stretch your imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11175, 20200, '', 31, 'Your imagination, just like your body, grows through exercise.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11176, 29470, '', 31, 'Artists often consider the imagination their unique provenance, but the imagination drives everything from engineering, marketing, cosmology, economics, and ethics.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11177, 56745, '', 31, 'Imagination is limitless.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11178, 63054, '', 31, 'Imagination is more important than knowledge. For knowledge is limited, whereas imagination embraces the entire world, stimulating progress, giving birth to evolution.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11179, 56876, '', 31, 'The only limit to our realization of tomorrow will be our doubts of today.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11180, 92119, '', 31, 'Imagination is the catalyst for all human progress and achievement.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11181, 19689, '', 31, 'Imagination is the basis of all creative effort.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11182, 38985, '', 31, 'Imagination is the only key to the future. Without it, we are locked in the present.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11183, 22649, '', 31, 'Imagination is the fuel of the soul.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11184, 84039, '', 31, 'Imagination is the paintbrush of the mind.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11185, 87258, '', 31, 'Imagination is the playground of the mind.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11186, 11045, '', 31, 'Imagination is the bridge between the impossible and the possible.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11187, 62575, '', 31, 'Imagination is the spark that ignites the flame of creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11188, 29997, '', 31, 'Imagination is the catalyst for change and innovation.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:05'),
(11189, 86097, '', 31, 'Imagination is the doorway to the future.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11190, 49282, '', 31, 'Imagination is the currency of the future.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11191, 68088, '', 31, 'Imagination is the catalyst for transformation.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11192, 69424, '', 31, 'Imagination is the catalyst for progress and evolution.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11193, 96701, '', 31, 'The imagination is the beginning of all great art.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11194, 97485, '', 31, 'See yourself where you want to be. Imagine how good it feels to reach that goal. Paint a mental image of yourself succeeding.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11195, 66986, '', 31, 'By imagining experiences in your mind, you can gain reference experiences that translate to your physical reality, but facing your fears in the reality is much more life-changing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11196, 56587, '', 31, 'Imagination is the engine of progress.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11197, 62863, '', 31, 'True imagination is not fanciful daydreaming; it is fire from heaven.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11198, 60955, '', 31, 'Imagination is free and effective.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11199, 93091, '', 31, 'Imagination is the possibility maker. It is the home of hope and regret.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11200, 78279, '', 31, 'Imagination enlarges vision, stretches the mind, challenges the impossible. Without imagination, thought comes to a halt.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11201, 94512, '', 31, 'Be free like a child. Let your imagination fly high. You must make it a point to surround yourself with the people who are like that.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11202, 15509, '', 31, 'Visualization is the act of picturing something in your mind. It utilizes the incredible power of your imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11203, 59256, '', 31, 'Use your imagination not as an escape from reality but as an aid to making your reality the best it could possibly be.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11204, 47482, '', 31, 'Through imagination, visualization, and choosing new thoughts and actions, we can create a new reality in our lives.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11205, 60256, '', 31, 'Truth is not confined by facts but by the intensity of your imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11206, 84677, '', 31, 'Imagination is the foundation of all progress.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11207, 74342, '', 31, 'Adversarial situations tend to narrow vision and imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11208, 5219, '', 31, 'There is no reason not to try as hard as possible and accomplish as much as humanely imaginable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11209, 12249, '', 31, 'Imagine a life where no one tells you that you can\'t do something. Imagine, if you will, a life in which you tell yourself that you can do anything you want - no limits.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11210, 4741, '', 31, 'Management is the power of imagination in action.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11211, 42015, '', 31, 'Creativity is a defining quality of the human spirit, a force of nature, the mainstream of imagination accessible to all.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11212, 15031, '', 31, 'Reason and imagination are twin faculties, both part of human nature.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11213, 66381, '', 31, 'Acquiring new ideas will help you boost your creative imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11214, 56197, '', 31, 'If you change your imagination, you can change your mood.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11215, 94377, '', 31, 'If the winds of fortune are temporarily blowing against you, remember that you can harness them and make them carry you toward your definite purpose, through the use of your imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11216, 18766, '', 31, 'You have an imagination for a reason. Use it!', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11217, 53357, '', 31, 'Worrying = Using your imagination to create something you don\'t want.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11218, 46718, '', 31, 'When your mind is calm, don\'t dwell on your bad habit or its consequences, but instead imagine what your daily life will look like once you adopt your new good habit.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11219, 63182, '', 31, 'Live out of your imagination instead of out of your memory.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11220, 74058, '', 31, 'Usually, the main problem with life conundrums is that we don\'t bring to them enough imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11221, 16535, '', 31, 'To create a new standard, it takes something that\'s not just a little bit different; it takes something that\'s really new and really captures people\'s imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11222, 87733, '', 31, 'Both desire and imagination are stored in the mind of the individual and when stretched, both have the potential to position a person for greatness.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11223, 39921, '', 31, 'Arousing the imagination arouses the creative powers of man.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11224, 7192, '', 31, 'As we get older, we learn to be \"realistic.\" If you want to learn to manifest, you have to regain some of that childlike belief that anything is possible.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11225, 85446, '', 31, 'Things are pretty, graceful, rich, elegant, handsome, but until they speak to the imagination, not yet beautiful.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11226, 21583, '', 31, 'Let your imagination release your imprisoned possibilities.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11227, 84309, '', 31, 'There are moments when a man\'s imagination so easily subdued to what it lives in, suddenly rises above its daily level and surveys the long windings of destiny.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11228, 64478, '', 31, 'Imagination allows you to see things in a non-traditional, non-restrictive manner. Your imagination is your picture of what tomorrow may bring.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11229, 49272, '', 31, 'All the breaks you need in life wait within your imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11230, 74964, '', 31, 'Imagination is the workshop of your mind, capable of turning mind energy into accomplishment and wealth.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11231, 15016, '', 31, 'Imagination gallops; judgment merely walks.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11232, 51029, '', 31, 'The best nation in the world is our imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11233, 87546, '', 31, 'The opportunities of man are limited only by his imagination. But so few have imagination that there are ten thousand fiddlers to one composer.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11234, 13992, '', 31, 'Children have this wonderful gift of imagination, untarnished by life\'s harsh realities. They live and imagine freely.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11235, 90866, '', 31, 'When the mind is quiet and emotions are passive, concentrated creative imagination enables us to transcend thoughts and feelings of limitation.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11236, 31790, '', 31, 'Commitment unlocks the doors of imagination, allows vision, and gives us the \'right stuff\' to turn our dreams into reality.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11237, 9369, '', 31, 'In a world without ego, there would be no originality, no color, no contrast. Variety would cease to exist, and choice would become unnecessary.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11238, 19034, '', 31, 'You can literally close your eyes and place yourself anywhere in the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11239, 31021, '', 31, 'As our knowledge grows, our imagination will lead to extremely exciting advances throughout all areas of life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11240, 87658, '', 31, 'Imagination is the core of desire, it acts at the core of metaphor.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11241, 67033, '', 31, 'Your imagination is the key to your future.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11242, 86885, '', 31, 'The past is only an imaginary time or experience that is used to teach us lessons for the future. The future is where you apply the lessons of the past.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11243, 35119, '', 31, 'One of the things about children is their vivid, unrestrained, and far-reaching imaginations - the depth and breadth of their creativity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11244, 95719, '', 31, 'You need imagination and vision, you need to believe in yourself and your abilities, and you need the determination to succeed despite the obstacles you will inevitably encounter.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11245, 91152, '', 31, 'Remember that sometimes people laugh when something is actually funny, but often they laugh when they lack the imagination to understand the situation.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11246, 94060, '', 31, 'Fortunate is the young man or young woman who learns, early in life, to use imagination, and doubly so in this age of greater opportunity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11247, 48703, '', 31, 'Imagination differentiates between man and other forms of life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11248, 86427, '', 31, 'The greatest things in life - truth, creativity, imagination, love, kindness, compassion -are already inside us, and they\'re all free.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11249, 76556, '', 31, 'First comes thought; then organization of that thought, into ideas and plans; then transformation of those plans into reality. The beginning, as you will observe, is in your imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11250, 97416, '', 31, 'A man to carry on a successful business must have imagination. He must see things as in a vision, a dream of the whole thing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11251, 56614, '', 31, 'We act, or fail to act, not because of \'will,\' as is so commonly believed, but because of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11252, 65230, '', 31, 'Imagination does not work to its full potential when we are lying on the couch doing nothing, but when we are with like-minded people.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11253, 92796, '', 31, 'Adults tend to suppress their imagination, and are too quick to give up their dreams. Don\'t let the child in you disappear - imagine, dream, and believe in yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11254, 46331, '', 31, 'Everything that exists is created first in the imagination, and secondly in reality, through activity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11255, 23950, '', 31, 'Our creative dreams come from imagination and original thinking. Every product we have today, from bagels to blue jeans and violas to vaccines, first existed in somebody\'s imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11256, 22733, '', 31, 'Imagination is a place where all the important answers live.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11257, 33443, '', 31, 'Imagination is the soil that brings dreams to life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11258, 40134, '', 31, 'Imagination has no age and dreams are forever.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11259, 67161, '', 31, 'Books give a soul to the universe, wings to the mind, flight to the imagination, and life to everything.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11260, 39385, '', 31, 'You don\'t need wings to fly, all you need is a wild imagination with wings.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11261, 78430, '', 31, 'Without leaps of imagination, or dreaming, we lose the excitement of possibilities.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11262, 7380, '', 31, 'Let your imagination run wild.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11263, 61867, '', 31, 'Why sleep when wild imagination triggers, bring it out before it explodes, time to hold your pen and let it scribble.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11264, 33562, '', 31, 'Children do not move, think or speak in a straight line, and neither does imagination and creativity. But sadly, our standardised pathways of education do.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11265, 37570, '', 31, 'Never apologise for your wild imaginations.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11266, 46086, '', 31, 'The imagination is a wild and dangerous forest that is impossible to know the full might of.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11267, 47596, '', 31, 'Let your imagination run wild with the possibilities of everything you could explore and experience and begin immediately.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11268, 56546, '', 31, 'Live in the sunshine, swim the sea, and drink the wild air of your imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11269, 6119, '', 31, 'Imagination, like certain wild animals, will not breed in captivity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11270, 93706, '', 31, 'Worry is a waste of imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11271, 74834, '', 31, 'Reading is dreaming with open eyes!', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11272, 75386, '', 31, 'Let your imagination run wild & let your mind be a Sweet Escape.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11273, 88501, '', 31, 'The music had to be rooted, and yet had to branch out, like the wild imagination of a child.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11274, 59973, '', 31, 'Perhaps imagination is not where we go to escape reality but where we go to remember it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11275, 22167, '', 31, 'If you can imagine it, you can do it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11276, 76610, '', 31, 'You need to be a little crazy. Crazy is the price you pay for having an imagination.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:06'),
(11277, 9318, '', 31, 'Be wild enough to imagine you can change the world because then there\'s a greater chance that you will.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11278, 85792, '', 31, 'Be wild and boundless. Why are you crawling when you have wings of imagination?', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11279, 50460, '', 31, 'Real difficulties can be overcome; it is only the imaginary ones that are unconquerable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:41:28', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11280, 50161, '', 14, 'We don’t meet people by accident. Everyone crosses our path for a reason.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11281, 57305, '', 14, 'Your vibe attracts your tribe.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11282, 86247, '', 14, 'Anything is possible when you have the right people there to support you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11283, 14538, '', 14, 'Be genuinely interested in everyone you meet and everyone you meet will be genuinely interested in you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11284, 85633, '', 14, 'Distance means so little, when someone means so much.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11285, 69504, '', 14, 'Two things you will never have to chase: True friends & true love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11286, 5783, '', 14, 'If the feelings are mutual the effort will be equal.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11287, 27731, '', 14, 'Invest on people who invest their time and affection on you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11288, 46215, '', 14, 'It doesn’t matter who hurt you, or broke you down. What matters is who made you smile again.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11289, 93183, '', 14, 'Relationships end too soon because people stop putting in the same effort to keep you, as they did to win you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11290, 71691, '', 14, 'There is no challenge strong enough to destroy your marriage as long as you are both willing to stop fighting against each other, and start fighting for each other.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11291, 54066, '', 14, 'He can’t read your mind. So take a moment to let him know how you really feel.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11292, 32330, '', 14, 'Sometimes you fall in love with the most unexpected person at the most unexpected time.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11293, 37594, '', 14, 'Keep good company, read good books, love good things and cultivate soul and body as faithfully as you can.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11294, 85336, '', 14, 'Whether it is a friendship or a relationship, all bonds are built on trust. Without it, you have nothing.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11295, 56364, '', 14, 'Apologizing does not mean that you’re wrong and the other person is right. It just means that you value your relationship more than your ego.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11296, 65948, '', 14, 'Don’t talk, just act. Don’t say, just show. Don’t promise, just prove.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11297, 53716, '', 14, 'We don’t meet people by accident. They are meant to cross our path for a reason.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11298, 45449, '', 14, 'The greatest relationships are the ones you never expected to be in.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11299, 1520, '', 14, 'Great relationships are not great because they have no problems. They are great because both people care enough about the other person to find a way to make it work.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11300, 95562, '', 14, 'Remember this point, as it is important. The person you are with now, is not anyone you have been with before. Do not hold the crimes of the past against the person in your present.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11301, 64830, '', 14, 'A true relationship is two imperfect people refusing to give up on each other.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11302, 59218, '', 14, 'The best feeling in the world is knowing that you actually mean something to someone.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11303, 40940, '', 14, 'All relationships go through hell, real ones get through it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11304, 83042, '', 14, 'A good relationship is when someone accepts your past, supports your present, and encourages your future.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11305, 72054, '', 14, 'The moment you start to wonder if you deserve better, you do.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11306, 42886, '', 14, 'Don’t let someone change who you are, to become what they need.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11307, 58003, '', 14, 'A perfect relationship is not perfect, it’s just that both people never gave up.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11308, 7783, '', 14, 'No matter how busy a person’s day may be, if they really care, they will always find time for you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11309, 4179, '', 14, 'Far too many people are looking for the right person, instead of trying to be the right person.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11310, 87562, '', 14, 'Assumptions are the termites of relationships.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11311, 94625, '', 14, 'Truth is everybody is going to hurt you: you just gotta find the ones worth suffering for. - Bob Marley.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11312, 35607, '', 14, 'Love is composed of a single soul inhabiting two bodies.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11313, 33691, '', 14, 'When someone loves you, the way they talk about you is different. You feel safe and comfortable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11314, 58743, '', 14, 'True love is your soul’s recognition of its counterpart in another.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11315, 75847, '', 14, 'Cheating and lying aren’t struggles, they’re reasons to break up.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11316, 54705, '', 14, 'We loved with a love that was more than love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11317, 21095, '', 14, 'People are lonely because they build walls instead of bridges.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11318, 32052, '', 14, 'We are afraid to care too much, for fear that the other person does not care at all.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11319, 26951, '', 14, 'They may forget what you said, but they will never forget how you made them feel.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11320, 19815, '', 14, 'The best thing to hold onto in life is each other.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11321, 13701, '', 14, 'When you stop expecting people to be perfect, you can like them for who they are.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11322, 90207, '', 14, 'When you don’t talk, there’s a lot of stuff that ends up not getting said.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11323, 65439, '', 14, 'Being deeply loved by someone gives you strength, while loving someone deeply gives you courage.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11324, 99523, '', 14, 'Forgiveness is the oil of all relationships.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11325, 17267, '', 14, 'The meeting of two personalities is like the contact of two chemical substances: if there is any reaction, both are transformed.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11326, 8172, '', 14, 'The person you’re meant to be with will never have to be chased, begged or given an ultimatum.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11327, 41453, '', 14, 'Be sure it’s your real self you’re showing. Because it is your real self that needs to be loved.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11328, 62704, '', 14, 'Fall in love with someone who makes you glad to be different.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11329, 18675, '', 14, 'If he can’t handle you at your worst then he does not deserve you at your best.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11330, 23920, '', 14, 'Real love means seeing beyond the words spoken out of pain, and instead seeing a person’s soul.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11331, 67269, '', 14, 'No road is long with good company.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11332, 99212, '', 14, 'Constant kindness can accomplish much. As the sun makes ice melt, kindness causes misunderstanding, mistrust and hostility to evaporate.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11333, 53969, '', 14, 'No matter how much you love someone, you still want to have your own way.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11334, 28740, '', 14, 'The true measure of a man is how he treats you when others are not looking.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11335, 66989, '', 14, 'Love looks not with the eyes, but with the mind/And therefore is winged Cupid painted blind.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11336, 11968, '', 14, 'Love is a two-way street constantly under construction.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11337, 80628, '', 14, 'If you look for it, I’ve got a sneaky feeling that love actually is all around.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11338, 61587, '', 14, 'Maybe you don’t need the whole world to love you. Maybe you just need one person.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11339, 129, '', 14, 'Life takes a bit of time and a lot of relationships.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(11340, 97908, '', 14, 'Let us be grateful to the people who make us happy; they are the charming gardeners who make our souls blossom.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11341, 30376, '', 14, 'In any relationship in which two people become one, the end result is two half people.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11342, 82571, '', 14, 'It is better to love wisely, no doubt: but to love foolishly is better than not to be able to love at all.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11343, 93952, '', 14, 'In the end there doesn’t have to be anyone who understands you. There just has to be someone who wants to.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11344, 46756, '', 14, 'You know it’s love when all you want is that person to be happy, even if you’re not part of their happiness.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11345, 74064, '', 14, 'Shared joy is a double joy; shared sorrow is half a sorrow. - Swedish Proverb.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11346, 19753, '', 14, 'Love is when you meet someone who tells you something new about yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11347, 74751, '', 14, 'Someone to tell it to is one of the fundamental needs of human beings.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11348, 4432, '', 14, 'Ultimately the bond of all companionship, whether in marriage or in friendship, is conversation.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11349, 21513, '', 14, 'Having someone wonder where you are when you don’t come home at night is a very old human need.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11350, 1990, '', 14, 'The purpose of a relationship is not to have another who might complete you, but to have another with whom you might share your completeness.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11351, 96337, '', 14, 'A relationship requires a lot of work and commitment.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11352, 15743, '', 14, 'Indifference and neglect often do much more damage than outright dislike.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11353, 51101, '', 14, 'The extent to which two people in a relationship can bring up and resolve issues is a critical marker of the soundness of a relationship.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11354, 77906, '', 14, 'We have to recognize that there cannot be relationships unless there is commitment, unless there is loyalty, unless there is love, patience, persistence.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:07'),
(11355, 4746, '', 14, 'The ultimate test of a relationship is to disagree but to hold hands.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11356, 70435, '', 14, 'A healthy relationship will never require you to sacrifice your friends, your dreams, or your dignity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11357, 32312, '', 14, 'You don’t develop courage by being happy in your relationships everyday. You develop it by surviving difficult times and challenging adversity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11358, 96292, '', 14, 'Trouble is part of your life, and if you don’t share it, you don’t give the person who loves you enough chance to love you enough.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11359, 82332, '', 14, 'Love in such a way that the person you love feels free.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11360, 33012, '', 14, 'The relationship between husband and wife should be one of closest friends.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11361, 70965, '', 14, 'To know when to go away and when to come closer is the key to any lasting relationship.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11362, 31248, '', 14, 'Relationships, marriages are ruined where one person continues to learn, develop and grow and the other person stands still.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11363, 37691, '', 14, 'Don’t walk in front of me; I may not follow. Don’t walk behind me; I may not lead. Just walk beside me and be my friend. - Albert Camus', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11364, 73415, '', 14, 'Do what you did in the beginning of the relationship and there won’t be an end.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11365, 9141, '', 14, 'No relationship is perfect, ever. There are always some ways you have to bend, to compromise, to give something up in order to gain something greater.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11366, 90858, '', 14, 'Souls tend to go back to who feels like home.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11367, 67674, '', 14, 'Each relationship nurtures a strength or weakness within you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11368, 25645, '', 14, 'A woman knows the face of the man she loves as a sailor knows the open sea.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11369, 139, '', 14, 'True friendship comes when the silence between two people is comfortable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(11370, 3153, '', 14, 'The most important ingredient we put into any relationship is not what we say or what we do, but what we are.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11371, 57460, '', 14, 'When you’re in a relationship and it’s good, even if nothing else in your life is right, you feel like your whole world is complete.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11372, 21940, '', 14, 'Love is a game that two can play and both can win.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11373, 149, '', 14, 'It is the things in common that make relationships enjoyable, but it is the little differences that make them interesting.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-26 19:52:08'),
(11374, 67772, '', 14, 'What love we’ve given, we’ll have forever. What love we fail to give, will be lost for all eternity.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11375, 54101, '', 14, 'In relationships, the little things are the big things.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11376, 77791, '', 14, 'Intimacy is the capacity to be rather weird with someone and finding that that’s ok with them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11377, 68682, '', 14, 'Three things I want in a relationship: Eyes that won’t cry, lips that won’t lie, and love that won’t die. - Wiz Khalifa', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11378, 91346, '', 14, 'Every couple needs to argue now and then. Just to prove that the relationship is strong enough to survive.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11379, 44671, '', 14, 'Don’t settle for a relationship that won’t let you be yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11380, 27585, '', 14, 'What greater thing is there for two human souls than to feel that they are joined for life… to strengthen each other… to be at one with each other in silent unspeakable memories.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11381, 42792, '', 14, 'It’s a humbling thing when you find someone to love. Even better if you’ve been waiting your whole life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11382, 58007, '', 14, 'There’s no perfect relationship. All relationships are work. If you put in the work, you’ll reap the rewards.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11383, 1408, '', 14, 'Love is an endless act of forgiveness. Forgiveness is me giving up the right to hurt you for hurting me. - Beyoncé', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11384, 53494, '', 14, 'Stick to the basics: Hold on to your family and friends—they will never go out of fashion.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11385, 87369, '', 14, 'Treasure your relationships, not your possessions.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11386, 92170, '', 14, 'The biggest difference trust makes in any relationship – and not just an intimate one – is that you can relax, be open, be yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11387, 89965, '', 14, 'In true love the smallest distance is too great and the greatest distance can be bridged.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11388, 18366, '', 14, 'Being good to yourself equates to having a positive relationship with yourself and higher self-esteem.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11389, 85716, '', 14, 'When you cultivate quality relationships, not only do you feel better and help your friends feel better, but you contribute to an increase of joy, love, and peace in the world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11390, 42705, '', 14, 'Beyond friendships adding to the list of improving life success and happiness, experts also assert that supportive relationships improve our odds of survival by fifty percent.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11391, 26768, '', 14, 'Don’t give up at the first signs of friction: only through clear communication, flexibility and willingness to adapt can you find a relationship that will weather the storms of life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11392, 44131, '', 14, 'Our lack of attention means we don’t notice or we miss much that is going on and this affects our relationships.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11393, 29919, '', 14, 'Forgiveness is essential for every kind of relationship we have.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08');
INSERT INTO `quotes` (`id`, `order`, `entry_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `author`, `has_notif`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(11394, 56962, '', 14, 'Trust in a relationship is very crucial. Without trust, a relationship cannot last as a healthy and happy bond.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11395, 29871, '', 14, 'If you find someone you love in your life, then hang on to that love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11396, 13268, '', 14, 'When you have once seen the glow of happiness on the face of a beloved person, you know that a man can have no vocation but to awaken that light on the faces surrounding him.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11397, 63779, '', 14, 'To love someone is nothing, to be loved by someone is something, to love someone who loves you is everything.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11398, 90839, '', 14, 'So long as there is a little real friendship and a desire to help each other that is sufficient.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11399, 86785, '', 14, 'Be patient and open-minded in your interactions with others; find the positive attributes that they possess.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11400, 40597, '', 14, 'The most precious gift we can offer anyone is our attention. When mindfulness embraces those we love, they will bloom like flowers.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11401, 60646, '', 14, 'Affection is when you see someone’s strengths; love is when you accept someone’s flaws.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11402, 26528, '', 14, 'The emotion that can break your heart is sometimes the very one that heals it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11403, 8591, '', 14, 'The pain of parting is nothing to the joy of meeting again.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11404, 5760, '', 14, 'You meet thousands of people and none of them really touch you. And then you meet one person and your life is changed forever.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11405, 55801, '', 14, 'A dream you dream alone is only a dream. A dream you dream together is reality.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11406, 30125, '', 14, 'We come to love not by finding a perfect person, but by learning to see an imperfect person perfectly.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11407, 81070, '', 14, 'Remember that the best relationship is one in which your love for each other exceeds your need for each other.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11408, 68036, '', 14, 'If you love yourself you love others, if you hate yourself you hate others, because in relationship with others it is only you mirrored.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11409, 67786, '', 14, 'Treat everyone as if they were a guest in your own house because in reality, they are a guest in your own world.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11410, 65804, '', 14, 'Quit wanting them to be the way you want them to be. Just love them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11411, 45606, '', 14, 'Associate with people who are likely to improve you. Welcome those who you are capable of improving. The process is a mutual one: people learn as they teach.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11412, 84528, '', 14, 'There’s only one thing more precious than our time and that’s who we spend it on.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11413, 99299, '', 14, 'Love cures people—both the ones who give it and the ones who receive it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11414, 93450, '', 14, 'When in a relationship, a real man doesn’t make his woman jealous of others, he makes others jealous of his woman.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11415, 43153, '', 14, 'If we would build on a sure foundation in friendship, we must love friends for their sake rather than for our own.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11416, 64573, '', 14, 'Trust is the fruit of a relationship in which you know you are loved.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11417, 88434, '', 14, 'Be a loving person rather than in a love relationship.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11418, 49034, '', 14, 'Remember to stay away from people who have a problem for every solution.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11419, 7630, '', 14, 'Love is at the root of everything. All learning. All parenting. All relationships. Love, or the lack of it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11420, 58609, '', 14, 'We are so different, yet so much the same.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11421, 67686, '', 14, 'So much of life is being present with the people you love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11422, 30861, '', 14, 'Our soulmate is the one who makes life come to life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11423, 44374, '', 14, 'You come to love not by finding the perfect person, but by seeing an imperfect person perfectly.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11424, 25376, '', 14, 'Forever is a measure of time used by people who share an ordinary love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11425, 54819, '', 14, 'How people treat you is their karma; how you react is yours.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11426, 26034, '', 14, 'Love is never lost. If not reciprocated, it will flow back and soften and purify the heart.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11427, 42346, '', 14, 'If you love someone, set them free. If they come back they’re yours; if they don’t they never were.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11428, 55453, '', 14, 'Nothing is perfect. Life is messy. Relationships are complex. Outcomes are uncertain. People are irrational.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11429, 88829, '', 14, 'Between men and women there is no friendship possible. There is passion, enmity, worship, love, but no friendship. - Oscar Wilde', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11430, 20946, '', 14, 'The beginning of love is to let those we love be perfectly themselves, and not to twist them to fit our own image.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11431, 28182, '', 14, 'It is a curious thought, but it is only when you see people looking ridiculous that you realize just how much you love them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11432, 74899, '', 14, 'Love does not consist in gazing at each other, but in looking outward together in the same direction.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11433, 18622, '', 14, 'When you realize you want to spend the rest of your life with somebody, you want the rest of your life to start as soon as possible.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11434, 17481, '', 14, 'If you work through the tough times, the respect and love that you feel deepens.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11435, 72054, '', 14, 'The greatest happiness of life is the conviction that we are loved; loved for ourselves, or rather, loved in spite of ourselves.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11436, 72475, '', 14, 'You don’t love someone because they’re perfect, you love them in spite of the fact that they’re not.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11437, 91801, '', 14, 'First and foremost, self-love, and then give love away.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11438, 45223, '', 14, 'The one who loves the least, controls the relationship.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:08'),
(11439, 46505, '', 14, 'Love does not claim possession, but gives freedom.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11440, 44576, '', 14, 'Falling in love and having a relationship are two different things.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11441, 15641, '', 14, 'If men and women really suit each other. Perhaps they should live next door and just visit now and then.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11442, 45657, '', 14, 'A person isn’t who they are during the last conversation you had with them – they’re who they’ve been throughout your whole relationship.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11443, 49298, '', 14, 'If civilization is to survive, we must cultivate the science of human relationships – the ability of all peoples, of all kinds, to live together, in the same world at peace.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11444, 22517, '', 14, 'The scariest thing about distance is you don’t know if they’ll miss you or forget about you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11445, 75859, '', 14, 'Any man who can drive safely while kissing a pretty girl is simply not giving the kiss the attention it deserves. - Albert Einstein', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11446, 14720, '', 14, 'We’re all a little weird. And when we find someone whose weirdness is compatible with ours, we join up with them and fall into mutually satisfying weirdness—and call it love—true love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11447, 60373, '', 14, 'Many people will walk in and out of your life, but only true friends will leave footprints in your heart.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11448, 3364, '', 14, 'One of the most beautiful qualities of true friendship is to understand and to be understood.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11449, 9303, '', 14, 'A good relationship is all about balance and chemistry.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11450, 98886, '', 14, 'No partner in a love relationship… should feel that he has to give up an essential part of himself to make it viable.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11451, 74776, '', 14, 'Our greatest joy and our greatest pain comes in our relationships with others.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11452, 90790, '', 14, 'Every relationship is fundamentally a power struggle, and the individual in power is whoever likes the other person less.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11453, 83948, '', 14, 'Work on your relationships… Relationships need renewal or they die.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11454, 36278, '', 14, 'You’ve got to be in a bad relationship to really understand what a great one is.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11455, 4881, '', 14, 'Relationships are the hallmark of the mature person.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11456, 97526, '', 14, 'Everything in your life, every experience, every relationship is a mirror of the mental pattern that is going on inside of you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11457, 48192, '', 14, 'Love is missing someone whenever you’re apart, but somehow feeling warm inside because you’re close in heart.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11458, 91386, '', 14, 'Health is the greatest gift, contentment the greatest wealth, faithfulness the best relationship.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11459, 69495, '', 14, 'Trust and faith bring joy to life and help relationships grow to their maximum potential.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11460, 15069, '', 14, 'A relationship becomes easier when you realize that you don’t have to be the one at fault to be the one who’s sorry.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11461, 12652, '', 14, 'Genuine relationships depend first on a healthy relationship with ourselves.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11462, 78981, '', 14, 'Sooner or later, we must all accept the fact that in a relationship, the only person you are dealing with is yourself.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11463, 7883, '', 14, 'Love … is the honoring of others in a way that grants them the grace of their own autonomy and allows mutual discovery.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11464, 24539, '', 14, 'Treasure each other in the recognition that we do not know how long we shall have each other.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11465, 75244, '', 14, 'People and relationships never stop being a work in progress.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11466, 30915, '', 14, 'To become a better you, you must be positive towards yourself, develop better relationships, embrace the place where you are.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11467, 62267, '', 14, 'That which is created in a relationship can be fixed in a relationship.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11468, 71426, '', 14, 'The three ingredients of a successful union between two … humor, commitment & undying love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11469, 65515, '', 14, 'If we are going to be happy and have any chance at growing then we must learn how to forgive others … and ourselves.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
