(11479, 61767, '', 14, 'Relationships in general make people a bit nervous. It’s about trust. Do I trust you enough to go there?', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11480, 64881, '', 14, 'Be honest, brutally honest. That is what’s going to maintain relationships.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11481, 12271, '', 14, 'The challenge and the energy running requires may be a selfish one, but it actually motivates me to be stronger in my relationships.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11482, 53171, '', 14, 'The deepest principle in human nature is the craving to be appreciated.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11483, 61202, '', 14, 'The place to begin building any relationship is inside ourselves, inside our circle of influence, our own character.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11484, 16686, '', 14, 'Happily ever after is not a fairy tale—it’s a choice.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11485, 28045, '', 14, 'Only when your love for someone exceeds your need for them do you have a shot at a genuine relationship together.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11486, 68917, '', 14, 'In a relationship each person should support the other; they should lift each other up.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11487, 98003, '', 14, 'It is only when we no longer compulsively need someone that we can have a real relationship with them.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11488, 88392, '', 14, 'We can improve our relationships with others by leaps and bounds if we become encouragers instead of critics.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11489, 5940, '', 14, 'Successful relationships start by giving up control, giving up the need to be loved or wanted or right all the time.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11490, 86813, '', 14, 'Your relationship with yourself sets the tone for every other relationship you have.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11491, 5894, '', 14, 'The most important thing in a relationship between a man and a woman is that one of them must be good at taking orders.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11492, 25557, '', 14, 'To maintain good relationships, one must keep checking emotional bank account.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11493, 25909, '', 14, 'A great relationship is about two things: First, appreciating the similarities and second, respecting the differences.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11494, 39983, '', 14, 'A successful relationship requires falling in love multiple times, but always with the same person.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11495, 59491, '', 14, 'Our soul mate is the one who makes life come to life.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11496, 84696, '', 14, 'A relationship where you can be weird together is your best choice.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11497, 86040, '', 14, 'To love is easy, to be in a relationship is extremely difficult.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11498, 98970, '', 14, 'Remember, we all stumble, every one of us. That’s why it’s a comfort to go hand in hand.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11499, 5382, '', 14, 'Love is friendship that has caught fire. It is quiet understanding, mutual confidence, sharing and forgiving. It is loyalty through good and bad times.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11500, 47991, '', 14, 'We must recognize that there cannot be relationships without commitment, loyalty, love, patience, and persistence.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11501, 56835, '', 14, 'Never love anybody that treats you like you’re ordinary.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11502, 98982, '', 14, 'Never love something so much that you can’t let go of it.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11503, 89231, '', 14, 'Take a lover who looks at you like maybe you are magic.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11504, 76064, '', 14, 'Be with someone who won’t stay mad at you, who can’t stand not talking to you, and who’s afraid of losing you.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11505, 11437, '', 14, 'Trust is the fruit on a relationship in which you know you are loved.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
