(11514, 8559, '', 14, 'There is no more lovely, friendly, and charming relationship, communion, or company than a good marriage.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11515, 9433, '', 14, 'Sometimes the heart sees what is invisible to the eye.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11516, 92924, '', 14, 'True love is your soul\'s recognition of its counterpart in another.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11517, 62119, '', 14, 'Love is people caring for people. That is love.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11518, 92980, '', 14, 'There are lots of people who can call you by your name, but there is only one person who can make it sound so special.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11519, 77884, '', 14, 'That\'s why they\'re called crushes. If they were easy, they\'d call them something else.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11520, 51018, '', 14, 'To get the full value of joy, you must have someone to divide it with.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11521, 36102, '', 14, 'We’re often afraid of being vulnerable, but vulnerability creates genuine connection.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11522, 51064, '', 14, 'You can’t have a relationship with someone hoping they’ll change. You have to be willing to commit to them as they are, with no expectations.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:09'),
(11523, 15482, '', 14, 'We can not control a relationship. We can only contribute to a relationship.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11524, 85376, '', 14, 'All relationships, business or personal, are an opportunity to serve another human being.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11525, 24571, '', 14, 'Relationships are like crystals, you don\'t realise how much you love it until it breaks.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11526, 88787, '', 14, 'Man is a knot into which relationships are tied.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11527, 37753, '', 14, 'We have to believe that even the briefest of human connections can heal.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11528, 48256, '', 14, 'Love and respect are the most important aspects of parenting, and of all relationships.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11529, 54073, '', 14, 'Don\'t smother each other. No one can grow in the shade.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11530, 99311, '', 14, 'In human relationships, kindness and lies are worth a thousand truths.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11531, 67848, '', 14, 'We must realise that all life is valuable and that we are united to all life. From this knowledge comes our spiritual relationship with the universe.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11532, 5780, '', 14, 'What is important to a relationship is a harmony of emotional roles and not too great a disparity in the general level of intelligence.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11533, 20074, '', 14, 'People change and forget to tell each other.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11534, 82408, '', 14, 'Death ends a life, not a relationship.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:42', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11535, 21339, '', 14, 'Truth is the glue of life. It\'s the most essential ingredient in effective communication. It\'s the foundational principle that holds all relationships.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:43', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11536, 47464, '', 14, 'Part of growing up is realising you learn to love so many people. It\'s about forming those relationships and finding what will last forever.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:43', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
(11537, 69745, '', 14, 'Be honest, brutally honest. That is what is going to maintain relationships.', '', 0, 2, '2023-01-19 19:42:43', '2023-01-27 00:32:10'),
